INSERT INTO `catalog_product_entity_text` VALUES ('1',75,0,'1','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=JY6RO95],#html-body [data-pb-style=PUMKDCS],#html-body [data-pb-style=VCFG8FT]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=D3UMN4M]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=WT5CHYN]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=BK1IE01],#html-body [data-pb-style=GDKELIJ],#html-body [data-pb-style=IQKM1PL]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"D3UMN4M\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"JY6RO95\"><a href=\"#SMAJ1QC\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"PUMKDCS\"><a href=\"#MU2U9Q4\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"VCFG8FT\"><a href=\"#UUXCMJ9\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"WT5CHYN\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"SMAJ1QC\" data-pb-style=\"IQKM1PL\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Tivi thng minh Xiaomi A Pro 65 inch &nbsp;ni bt vi thit k hin i, khung kim loi cao cp thit k khng vin sang trng cho tri nghim hnh nh khng gii hn. Mn hnh 4K UHD di mu rng cng Dolby Vision mang n  sc nt cc cao, m thanh sng ng nh s h tr ca Dolby Audio, DTS-X v DTS Virtual:X, Google TV cung cp kho gii tr khng l p ng mi nhu cu s dng, iu khin d dng bng ging ni. Xiaomi 65A Pro 65 inch ha hn mang n cho ngi dng nhng pht giy th gin hon ho, nng cao tri nghim cuc sng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thit k hin i vi khung kim loi khng vin cao cp</strong><br>Vi phn vin c thit k siu hp, mang li cho ngi dng tri nghim xem vi hnh nh khng gii hn, to chiu su v  chn tht cho cc thc phim. Tivi 65A Pro 65 inch ni bt vi phn khung kim loi nguyn khi sang trng, p mt khng ch gip bo v cc b phn bn trong m cn gp phn to im nhn cho khng gian sng ca bn thm phn mu sc v hin i.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Hnh nh sc nt, sinh ng</strong><br>Nh c trang b mn hnh 4K Ultra HD  phn gii 3840 x 2160 pixels, sn phm em n cho ngi xem hnh nh c  sc nt cao. Ngoi ra, vi tiu chun gam mu DCI-P3 c p dng trong ngnh cng nghip in nh Hollywood cng cng ngh c tnh chuyn ng b tr MEMC gip hnh nh hin th  tc  cao lun m bo  chn thc v mt m, cho tri nghim xem hon ho nht. Thm vo  l cng ngh Dolby Vision tiu chun ca ngnh in nh gip hnh nh hin th trn tivi Xiaomi 65A Pro 65 inch c  tng phn v mu sc cao hn, a dng chi tit hn, hnh nh hin th sng ng, c khng gian nh c thu vo tm mt bn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>m thanh mnh m, ni bt</strong><br>Hai loa 12W mnh m c trang b trn tivi Xiaomi mang n hiu sut m thanh nh cao, a ngi dng ti gn hn nhng hnh ng. Cng cng ngh DTS-X v Dolby Audio gii m kp to ra m thanh c hiu ng sng ng. Bn cnh , DTS Virtual:X gip to ra m thanh 3 chiu vi chiu trn cao ti to tri nghim nh trong rp phim y n tng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Kho gii tr khng l thng qua Google TV</strong><br>Di s h tr ca Google TV ca smart TV Xiaomi 65A Pro 65 inch, ngi dng s c c tri nghim xem v cng trn vn cc b phim, chng trnh,... hp dn t ng dng. Ngoi ra, bn cn c khm ph nhng ni dung mi thng qua cc  xut hin th da trn ni dung  xem hoc quan tm trc .</p>\r\n<p><strong>iu khin bng ging ni thng minh</strong><br>Tnh nng iu khin bng ging ni ny s gip tivi 65A Pro 65 inch tr ln hu ch hn rt nhiu. Ch bng ging ni ca mnh, ngi dng  c th d dng iu khin mi tc v ca thit b nh: pht trc tuyn ng dng, tm phim, pht nhc,... Hay thm ch c th nhn cu tr li v iu khin cc thit b thng minh trong nh ch vi cu lnh \"Ok Google\" hoc bm nt Tr l Google trn remote.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bluetooth 360 - iu khin t xa mi gc </strong><br>Ngi dng c th d dng kim sot smart tivi 65A Pro Xiaomi 65 inch trong bn knh 10m khng im cht nh c trang b iu khin t xa hin i. Cc nt n cho php bn truy cp ngay tc th vo cc ni dung yu thch.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Truyn pht ni dung trn in thoi ln mn hnh ln</strong><br>Chromecast tch hp v Miracast gip qu trnh truyn ti ni dung yu thch ca bn t cc thit b thng minh ln mn hnh tivi ln d dng hn, em li tri nghim hnh nh th v cho ngi xem.</p>\r\n<p><strong>B x l cht lng cao gip thao tc mt m</strong><br>Nh c trang b GPU Mali G52 cng b x l li t CPU A55 mang n cho tivi Xiaomi 65A Pro 65 inch mt hiu nng cc nh v thut ton tr ln linh hot hn. Bn cnh  b nh ln 2GB + 16GB cho php ngi dng thoi mi ti xung mi ng dng yu thch m khng lo v d liu hay gy git lag, tn hng nhng pht giy th gin vi thao tc mt m nht. Cng ngh Wi-Fi bng tn kp v Bluetooth 5.0 cng m bo thit b truyn d liu nhanh v n nh hn.</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"MU2U9Q4\" data-pb-style=\"BK1IE01\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hng dn mua hng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th mua hng theo mt trong cc cch sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong>1/ Mua hng trc tip:</strong><br>Qu khch c th n trc tip tham quan, tri nghim v mua sm cc sn phm Xiaomi ti tt c cc a ch sau ca MISTORE:</p>\r\n<p>364 Nguyn Tri, Thanh Xun Trung, Thanh Xun, H Ni.<br>Hotline: 03.4567.6666</p>\r\n<p>195, An Dng Vng, Phng 8, Qun 5<br>Hotline: (028)3.888.3456</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>2/ t mua qua website ca Mistore:</strong><br>Bc 1 : Click vo sn phm bn c nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Chn  Thm Vo Gi Hng   thc hin bc tip theo ( lu  bn c th chn nhiu sn phm trong cng 1 gi hng ).</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Kim tra n hng v s lng sau  chn Tin hnh t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 4 : in y  thng tin chnh xc ca qu khch v chn phng thc thanh ton mong mun, sau  kim tra li Ha n mua hng.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu mun thm sn phm khc vo n hng qu khch chn Mua thm.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu Ha n mua hng  chnh xc, qu khch chn t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 5 : Qu khch s nhn c thng bo t hng thnh cng v M n hng t h thng. Thng tin mua hng ca qu khch s c h thng gi qua email ng k, hy lu li m s n hng  tin cho vic theo di n hng ca qu khch.</p>\r\n<p>Chng ti s lin lc vi Qu khch  xc nhn n hng v tin hnh giao hng.</p>\r\n<p>( n hng cha bao gm ph vn chuyn, ph vn chuyn s c bo c th khi nhn vin gi in cht n trc khi giao. n hng ca qu khch s t ng hy nu thng tin t hng khng y  hoc khng r rng m khng cn bo trc. Nu qu khch c nhu cu gi hng ti ca hng vui lng thanh ton trc. )</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>3/ t hng qua in thoi:</strong><br>Bc 1 : in thoi n s in Thoi t Hng ti Hotline:</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Cung cp y  thng tin sn phm , mu sc, chng loi , s lng sn phm m qu khch mong mun.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Cung cp y  thng tin nhn hng ca qu khch mt cch chnh xc nht  Mistore c th giao hng cho qu khch nhanh nht.</p>\r\n<p>Thng tin thanh ton chuyn khon<br>STK: 0461000266789  Vietcombank</p>\r\n<p>Ch TK: Nguyn L Phng</p>\r\n<p>Email: mistore.com.vn@gmail.com</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong> thun tin hn cho qu trnh mua hng, hin ti Mistore.com.vn h tr cc hnh thc thanh ton sau:</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton ti ca hng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tin mt (VND)</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton th ATM</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton bng th tn dng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tr gp. Tm hiu thm ti y</strong><br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton khi nhn hng</strong><br>Hng ho s c vn chuyn qua dch v Chuyn pht nhanh / Shipper n tn nh, thanh ton sau  nhn hng.</p>\r\n<p>(*) Lu : thanh ton khi nhn hng (Cash On Delivery) ch p dng vi n hng c gi tr di 2 triu ng, cha bao gm ph vn chuyn v bo him (nu c), vi n hng ln hn vui lng lin h  c hng dn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton online</strong><br>Chuyn khon qua ti khon cng ty. Xem ti y<br>Thanh ton bng th ATM<br>Thanh ton bng th tn dng<br>Thanh ton tr gp bng th tn dng<br>Th tn dng (Credit Card) l mt loi th ngn hng c tnh nng thanh ton m khng cn tin c sn trong th. Ni cch khc l bn s mn tin ca ngn hng  thanh ton v ti cui k s cn tr li y  cho ngn hng. S tin trong th tn dng c ngn hng cp gi l hn mc th tn dng.<br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Chnh sch bo hnh\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"UUXCMJ9\" data-pb-style=\"GDKELIJ\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p id=\"AMAGAE3\">Cng ty TNHH Dami Vit Nam</p>\r\n<p><strong>QUY NH V BO HNH  I MI</strong><br>Chnh sch bo hnh c p dng i vi sn phm: in thoi; My tnh bng (Tablet); My tnh xch tay (Laptop); Linh kin, Ph kin trong h thng ca hng Xiaomi chnh hng MISTORE trn ton quc.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Lu  quan trng:</strong></p>\r\n<p>K t 3/2015, Mistore p dng chnh sch bo hnh in t thng qua S in thoi/ Series number/ iMei thit b. Theo quy nh bo hnh chnh hng, Qu khch vui lng gi li v/hp thit b  c bo hnh.<br>Thi gian tip nhn &amp; tr bo hnh t: 12h00  21h00 (Tr th 7, ch nht v ngy l)<br><strong>I. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;CHNH SCH BO HNH:</strong><br>Lu : chnh sch bo hnh / i mi ny p dng vi sn phm nhp khu, cc sn phm c phn phi chnh hng bi DGW s c bo hnh / i mi theo chnh sch / quyt nh ca n v tip nhn bo hnh DGW (Dcare)<br>1. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh (tu theo nhm sn phm) v i mi theo chnh sch bo hnh chnh hng ca Xiaomi.</p>\r\n<p>2. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh hoc i mi trong trng hp pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut (tr ngoi hnh).</p>\r\n<p>3. &nbsp; &nbsp;Quy nh v thi gian tip nhn - x l (tnh t thi im tip nhn bo hnh):</p>\r\n<p>Thi gian kim tra: Ti a 48 gi lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Thi gian x l bo hnh: &nbsp;15 - 30 ngy lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Nu c pht sinh vn  khc, CSKH s lin h  thng bo trc t nht 24 gi.</p>\r\n<p>4. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c thay th linh kin hoc sa cha min ph khi b h hng do li k thut t nh sn xut sau thi gian quy nh i mi.</p>\r\n<p>6. &nbsp; &nbsp; Mi loi sn phm c chnh sch bo hnh ring, Qu khch vui lng xem k chnh sch bo hnh theo tng sn phm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>II. &nbsp; &nbsp; IU KIN BO HNH:</strong><br>Sn phm cn trong thi hn bo hnh.<br>Sn phm phi cn nguyn vn, khng sa cha bi cc ni khc ngoi h thng ca hng hoc Mi Store, MiCare v Dcare.<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm phi trng hp vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t v bao b sn phm.<br>Sn phm phi cn hp nguyn vn, khng b rch, khng chp ni, khng b ty xa.<br>III. &nbsp;IU KIN I MI:<br>Sn phm c hng chnh sch 1 i 1 nu pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut.<br>Sn phm i mi l sn phm ngang gi, cng chng loi, cng thng s k thut, cng mu sc. (Trng hp Store khng cn sn phm c cng mu vi sn phm c i mi, chng ti s thay th bng sn phm khc tng ng vi gi tr sn phm ). Nu sn phm khng c li t nh sn xut th s tnh khu tr 30% gi tr sn phm.<br>Thi gian bo hnh v i mi:<br>in thoi, Laptop: Bo hnh 12 Thng phn cng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin | Pin bo hnh 06 thng<br>Xe in, Xe cn bng: Bo hnh 06 Thng phn cng | Pin bo hnh 03 thng<br>Pin d phng: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Tai nghe: Bo hnh 03 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Loa bluetooth: Bo hnh 01 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Camera: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>n trn, n bn: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Sn phm thi trang, ph kin khc: Khng bo hnh, khng i mi.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>IV. &nbsp;TRNG HP T CHI BO HNH (H tr sa cha):</strong><br>Sn phm  ht hn bo hnh.<br>Cc vn  lin quan n ti khon, bo mt (Mt khu, MiCloud)<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm khng trng vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t (hoc ho n mua hng).<br>Sn phm b h hng do thin tai, l lt, st nh, ha hon hay do vn chuyn lm nt, mp, b, try xc, vo nc.<br>Sn phm h hng do s dng khng ng theo hng dn, do ngun in khng ng, khng n nh, do t  cp nht phn mm (up rom) khng ng k thut, Root my dn n h hng thit b.<br>Mn hnh xut hin di 3 im cht, mn hnh b sc, m, bi bn, phn quang hoc cht hn trong qu trnh s dng do tc dng lc, va p, vo nc.<br>Sn phm b r st,  bn do n mn hay do cht lng  vo.<br>Sn phm c du hiu  tho lp, sa cha thay th linh kin  nhng ni khc ngoi h thng Mistore, Micare, Dcare<br>Cc tng phm ph kin km theo sn phm khng phi l sn phm khng c bo hnh. V d: tng phm khuyn mi, mt s ph kin km theo my nh Pin, sc, cable, tai nghe...(nu c)<br>Cc trng hp yu cu v v sinh sn phm, bo tr sn phm khng nm trong hn mc bo hnh.<br>i vi pin tch hp, khng bo hnh cc trng hp ph, chm chy linh kin v cc trng hp chai, hng pin do s dng.<br>i vi loa, tai nghe v cc sn phm c loa, khng bo hnh li r, h.<br>V. Quy nh khc:<br>i vi nhng sn phm nh my tnh, in thoi,  cng lu tr, th nh. Chng ti hon ton khng chu trch nhim v vic mt d liu c nhn ca Qu khch nh: ti liu, danh b, tin nhn  khi thc hin cc yu cu Up Rom, sa cha.<br>Nu qu khch c nhu cu sao lu, backup d liu. Vui lng bo trc  nhn vin k thut thc hin.<br>VI. Chnh sch tr hng<br>Mi Store khng c chnh sch tr hng Qu khch vui lng tm hiu tnh nng hng ha hoc kim tra k sn phm.<br>Mt s trng hp c bit:<br>Qu khch c quyn tr hoc i mi trong trng hp sn phm pht sinh li do nh sn xut khng khc phc c hoc khc phc nhiu ln khng c.<br><strong>GIM C CNG TY</strong></p>\r\n<p> K</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(p dng t 01/01/2023)</p></div></div></div></div>'),('2',76,0,'1','<p> Phn phi chnh hng Xiaomi (Vit Nam)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bo hnh chnh hng 12 thng</strong>, i mi trong 7 ngy u tin.</p>\r\n<p> Mi 100% Fullbox nguyn seal</p>\r\n<p>Lu : sn phm ny<strong>ch bn ONLINE</strong>.Qu khch cn t trc, sau  giao hng hoc t hn nhn ti ca hng.</p>'),('3',85,0,'1','Tivi thng minh Xiaomi A Pro 65 inch'),('4',75,0,'2','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=KDOR3QX],#html-body [data-pb-style=QHIXUFB],#html-body [data-pb-style=UVPDFNI]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=XO2W24J]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=LIDU7GX]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=NVGG3H5],#html-body [data-pb-style=RHD6NSD],#html-body [data-pb-style=SOJRRDP]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"XO2W24J\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"KDOR3QX\"><a href=\"#K680E61\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"UVPDFNI\"><a href=\"#YNJ2FWL\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"QHIXUFB\"><a href=\"#B4W7BL9\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"LIDU7GX\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"K680E61\" data-pb-style=\"NVGG3H5\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Tivi thng minh Xiaomi A Pro 55 inch l dng smart tivi mi nht n t nh Xiaomi, s hu mn hnh vi  sc nt cc cao 4K Ultra UHD. Thit k khung kim loi khng vin, cng ngh MEMC hin i, h thng m thanh Dolby Audio v DTS-X m chm, iu khin thng minh bng ging ni, kho gii tr khng l cng nhiu tnh nng ng kinh ngc chc chn s chiu lng c tt c ngi dng kh tnh nht.</p>\r\n<p><strong>S hu khung kim loi cao cp cng thit k khng vin</strong><br>Vi thit k vin siu hp mang li t l mn hnh trn thn my cao hn, vt xa so vi tivi tiu chun. Khi mn hnh c bt, ngi dng gn nh khng cm nhn c ranh gii ca hnh nh, mang n tri nghim hnh nh sng ng, m chm hn, to chiu su v tng  chn tht cho cc cun phim. Smart TV 55A Pro 55 inch ni bt vi phn khung kim loi tinh xo thit k nguyn khi v cng p mt, m bo s chc chn v an ton cho cc b phn bn trong, khng ch l mt thit b tin ch m cn gip khng gian sng ca bn thm phn hin i v y mu sc.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cht lng hnh nh chi tit, sc nt</strong><br>Bc vo khng gian gii tr vi Xiaomi Google Tivi 4K 55 inch 55A Pro s mang n cho ngi dng hnh nh c  sc nt cc cao 4K Ultra HD  phn gii 3840 x 2160 pixels. p dng tiu chun gam mu DCI-P3 c s dng trong ngnh cng nghip in nh Hollywood nhm m bo mu sc hin th trn mn hnh lun trung thc, kt hp cng cng ngh MEMC c tnh chuyn ng b tr gip hnh nh chuyn ng  tc  cao tr nn mt m hn, mang n tri nghim xem hon ho.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra, cng ngh Dolby Vision tiu chun ca ngnh in nh mang li  sng cng  tng phn v mu sc cao hn, ng thi hin th nhiu chi tit hn, cho hnh nh sng ng, c khng gian nh c thu vo mt bn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>m thanh sng ng, chn thc nh ti rp chiu phim</strong><br>55A Pro 55 inch trang b 2 loa 12W mnh m mang n hiu sut m thanh nng cao, a ngi dng n gn hn vi hnh ng. Kt hp cng cng ngh gii m kp Dolby Audio v DTS-X to hiu ng m thanh sng ng. Ngoi ra, DTS Virtual:X c kh nng to m thanh ba chiu vi chiu trn cao gip ti to tri nghim nh  trong rp phim.</p>\r\n<p><strong>p ng mi nhu cu gii tr vi s h tr t Google TV</strong><br>Thng qua Google TV c tch hp, bn s c c cm gic gii tr v cng trn vn vi cc chng trnh, b phim, hp dn v r nt t ng dng. Ngoi ra, ngi dng cn c khm ph nhng ni dung mi vi cc  xut da trn ni dung bn  xem hoc quan tm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thc hin nhiu tc v cng lc bng ging ni ca bn</strong><br>Tnh nng iu khin bng ging ni s gip tivi Xiaomi 55A Pro 55 inch tr ln hu ch hn, ch bng ging ni, bn c th trc tip iu khin ng dng, tm phim, pht trc tuyn ng dng, pht nhc, mt cch nhanh chng v thun tin. Hay thm ch nhn cu tr li, iu khin cc thit b nh thng minh ch vi cu lnh \"Ok Google\" hoc nhn nt Tr l Google trn iu khin.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Smart tivi 55A Pro 55 inch iu khin t xa mi gc  vi Bluetooth 360</strong><br>Thng qua iu khin t xa, ngi dng c th thc hin mi thao trong phm vi 10m, d dng kim sot hn  mi hng khng im cht. Cc nt n cho php ngi dng truy cp ngay lp tc vo nhng ni dung yu thch ca mnh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Truyn pht ni dung t thit b thng minh ln tivi&nbsp;</strong><br>Chromecast tch hp v Miracast gip vic truyn ti ni dung yu thch ca bn t in thoi thng minh hay my tnh bng ln mn hnh ln hn, mang li tri nghim hnh nh th v cho ngi dng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thao tc mt m vi b x l cao cp</strong><br>Nh c trang b b x l li t CPU A55 cng GPU Mali G52 mang n cho Google tivi 4K 55 inch 55A Pro Xiaomi mt hiu nng cc nh, thut ton linh hot hn. Bn cnh  b nh ln 2GB + 16GB cho php bn ti xung mi ng dng yu thch m khng lo v d liu hay gy git lag, tn hng tri nghim vi thao tc mt m nht. Cng ngh Wi-Fi bng tn kp v Bluetooth 5.0 cng s gip thit b truyn d liu nhanh v n nh hn rt nhiu.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"YNJ2FWL\" data-pb-style=\"RHD6NSD\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hng dn mua hng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th mua hng theo mt trong cc cch sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong>1/ Mua hng trc tip:</strong><br>Qu khch c th n trc tip tham quan, tri nghim v mua sm cc sn phm Xiaomi ti tt c cc a ch sau ca MISTORE:</p>\r\n<p>364 Nguyn Tri, Thanh Xun Trung, Thanh Xun, H Ni.<br>Hotline: 03.4567.6666</p>\r\n<p>195, An Dng Vng, Phng 8, Qun 5<br>Hotline: (028)3.888.3456</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>2/ t mua qua website ca Mistore:</strong><br>Bc 1 : Click vo sn phm bn c nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Chn  Thm Vo Gi Hng   thc hin bc tip theo ( lu  bn c th chn nhiu sn phm trong cng 1 gi hng ).</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Kim tra n hng v s lng sau  chn Tin hnh t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 4 