INSERT INTO `catalog_product_entity_text` VALUES ('7',75,0,'3','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=L0LKHBU],#html-body [data-pb-style=RJ8UV5Y],#html-body [data-pb-style=ROK1JW3]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=N60QB5C]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=L433DL4]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=CXCEJPM],#html-body [data-pb-style=Q4WMEN8],#html-body [data-pb-style=V1GGG1S]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"N60QB5C\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"RJ8UV5Y\"><a href=\"#POSVH00\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"L0LKHBU\"><a href=\"#QQ0EIVE\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"ROK1JW3\"><a href=\"#OEEWSD8\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"L433DL4\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"POSVH00\" data-pb-style=\"Q4WMEN8\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Tivi thng minh Xiaomi A Pro 43 inch &nbsp;thuc dng tivi mi nht ca nh Xiaomi, ni bt vi thit k hin i, khung kim loi khng vin cao cp mang n tri nghim hnh nh khng gii hn. Mn hnh 4K Ultra HD vi  phn gii cc cao, di mu rng cng Dolby Vision cho ra hnh nh cc sc nt, m thanh mnh m n tng bi c h tr t Dolby Audio, DTS-X v DTS Virtual:X, Google TV cung cp kho gii tr v hn, d dng iu khin mi thao tc bng ging ni. 43A Pro 43 inch chc chn s lm hi lng tt c ngi dng d kh tnh nht.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thit k vin mn hnh siu hp, tri nghim hnh nh m chm</strong><br>c thit k vi phn vin siu hp gip t l mn hnh c thn trn cao hn thn di, mang li tri nghim xem vi hnh nh khng gii hn, sng ng, m chm, to chiu su v  chn tht cho cc cun phim. Smart TV Xiaomi 43A Pro 43 inch ni bt vi phn khung ch tc t kim loi nguyn khi cao cp v cng tinh xo, p mt khng ch gip bo v an ton cho cc ph kin bn trong m cn gp phn bin khng gian sng ca bn tr ln hin i, phong cch v y mu sc.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cht lng hnh nh sc nt, sinh ng</strong><br>Hnh nh sc nt, mu sc tuyt p, tc  mt m,...  l nhng in cng rt ln ca tivi 43A Pro 43 inch nh s hu mn hnh 4K UHD vi  phn gii cao 3840 x 2160 pixels cng tiu chun gam mu DCI-P3 v cng ngh c tnh chuyn ng b tr MEMC. Thm vo , p dng cng ngh Dolby Vision tiu chun c s dng trong ngnh cng nghip in nh mang n cho tivi Xiaomi  tng phn cng  sng v mu sc cao hn, hin th a dng chi tit hn, cho hnh nh sng ng, thu ht.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tn hng m thanh ni mnh m, sng ng</strong><br>Nh c trang b 2 loa cng sut 12W, smart tivi 43A Pro Xiaomi 43 inch mang li hiu sut m thanh nng cao cc n tng, a ngi dng tin gn hn vi nhng hnh ng. Bn cnh , cng ngh gii m kp DTS-X v Dolby Audio cho ra hiu ng m thanh sng ng. Ngoi ra, cng ngh DTS Virtual:X tin tin to m thanh ba chiu vi chiu trn cao gip ti to hon ho tri nghim rp chiu phim.</p>\r\n<p><strong>p ng mi nhu cu gii tr vi s tr gip t Google TV</strong><br>Di s h tr ca Google TV, ngi dng s c c tri nghim xem v cng trn vn vi tivi 43A Pro 43 inch khi c thng thc hng lot b phim, chng trnh yu thch v sp xp chng dnh ring cho bn. Bn cnh , bn cn c khm ph nhiu ni dung mi vi cc  xut da trn ni dung  xem hoc quan tm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thc hin nhiu tc v hn ch bng ging ni</strong><br>Xng danh l mt chic Smart TV, tivi Xiaomi 43A Pro 43 inch lm tt nhim v ca mnh khi c th nhn lnh bng ging ni ca ngi dng v iu khin ng dng, tm phim, pht nhc, pht trc tip,... Thm ch, thit b cn c th nhn cu tr li v iu khin cc thit b thng minh trong nh ch vi cu lnh \"Ok Google\" hoc nhn nt Tr l Google trn iu khin t xa  bt u.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bluetooth iu khin t xa 360</strong><br>Vi iu khin t xa, ngi dng c th thc hin mi thao tc trn tivi trong phm vi 10m, d dng kim sot v iu khin  mi hng. Cc nt nhn cho php bn truy cp ngay tc th vo nhng ni dung m bn thn yu thch.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cung cp ch  xem rng hn</strong><br>Chromecast tch hp v Miracast cho php ngi dng tip tc xem ni dung trn thit b di ng thng minh ca mnh bng mn hnh ln hn, nng cao tri nghim hnh nh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tri nghim mt m vi b vi x l hiu sut cao</strong><br>CPU A55 li t, GPU Mali G52 cng b nh ln 2GB + 16GB chnh l gii php chip mnh m cung cp cho tivi Xiaomi 43A Pro 43 inch mt hiu nng cc nh vi thut ton linh hot, mang n khng gian rng ln cho cc ng dng yu thch ca bn v tri nghim gii tr y th v. Bn cnh , cng ngh Wi-Fi bng tn kp 2.4GHz/5GHz v Bluetooth 5.0 s gip thit b truyn ti d liu nhanh chng v n nh hn rt nhiu.</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"QQ0EIVE\" data-pb-style=\"CXCEJPM\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hng dn mua hng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th mua hng theo mt trong cc cch sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong>1/ Mua hng trc tip:</strong><br>Qu khch c th n trc tip tham quan, tri nghim v mua sm cc sn phm Xiaomi ti tt c cc a ch sau ca MISTORE:</p>\r\n<p>364 Nguyn Tri, Thanh Xun Trung, Thanh Xun, H Ni.<br>Hotline: 03.4567.6666</p>\r\n<p>195, An Dng Vng, Phng 8, Qun 5<br>Hotline: (028)3.888.3456</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>2/ t mua qua website ca Mistore:</strong><br>Bc 1 : Click vo sn phm bn c nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Chn  Thm Vo Gi Hng   thc hin bc tip theo ( lu  bn c th chn nhiu sn phm trong cng 1 gi hng ).</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Kim tra n hng v s lng sau  chn Tin hnh t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 4 : in y  thng tin chnh xc ca qu khch v chn phng thc thanh ton mong mun, sau  kim tra li Ha n mua hng.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu mun thm sn phm khc vo n hng qu khch chn Mua thm.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu Ha n mua hng  chnh xc, qu khch chn t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 5 : Qu khch s nhn c thng bo t hng thnh cng v M n hng t h thng. Thng tin mua hng ca qu khch s c h thng gi qua email ng k, hy lu li m s n hng  tin cho vic theo di n hng ca qu khch.</p>\r\n<p>Chng ti s lin lc vi Qu khch  xc nhn n hng v tin hnh giao hng.</p>\r\n<p>( n hng cha bao gm ph vn chuyn, ph vn chuyn s c bo c th khi nhn vin gi in cht n trc khi giao. n hng ca qu khch s t ng hy nu thng tin t hng khng y  hoc khng r rng m khng cn bo trc. Nu qu khch c nhu cu gi hng ti ca hng vui lng thanh ton trc. )</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>3/ t hng qua in thoi:</strong><br>Bc 1 : in thoi n s in Thoi t Hng ti Hotline:</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Cung cp y  thng tin sn phm , mu sc, chng loi , s lng sn phm m qu khch mong mun.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Cung cp y  thng tin nhn hng ca qu khch mt cch chnh xc nht  Mistore c th giao hng cho qu khch nhanh nht.</p>\r\n<p>Thng tin thanh ton chuyn khon<br>STK: 0461000266789  Vietcombank</p>\r\n<p>Ch TK: Nguyn L Phng</p>\r\n<p>Email: mistore.com.vn@gmail.com</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong> thun tin hn cho qu trnh mua hng, hin ti Mistore.com.vn h tr cc hnh thc thanh ton sau:</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton ti ca hng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tin mt (VND)</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton th ATM</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton bng th tn dng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tr gp. Tm hiu thm ti y</strong><br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton khi nhn hng</strong><br>Hng ho s c vn chuyn qua dch v Chuyn pht nhanh / Shipper n tn nh, thanh ton sau  nhn hng.</p>\r\n<p>(*) Lu : thanh ton khi nhn hng (Cash On Delivery) ch p dng vi n hng c gi tr di 2 triu ng, cha bao gm ph vn chuyn v bo him (nu c), vi n hng ln hn vui lng lin h  c hng dn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton online</strong><br>Chuyn khon qua ti khon cng ty. Xem ti y<br>Thanh ton bng th ATM<br>Thanh ton bng th tn dng<br>Thanh ton tr gp bng th tn dng<br>Th tn dng (Credit Card) l mt loi th ngn hng c tnh nng thanh ton m khng cn tin c sn trong th. Ni cch khc l bn s mn tin ca ngn hng  thanh ton v ti cui k s cn tr li y  cho ngn hng. S tin trong th tn dng c ngn hng cp gi l hn mc th tn dng.<br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Chnh sch bo hnh\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"OEEWSD8\" data-pb-style=\"V1GGG1S\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p id=\"AMAGAE3\">Cng ty TNHH Dami Vit Nam</p>\r\n<p><strong>QUY NH V BO HNH  I MI</strong><br>Chnh sch bo hnh c p dng i vi sn phm: in thoi; My tnh bng (Tablet); My tnh xch tay (Laptop); Linh kin, Ph kin trong h thng ca hng Xiaomi chnh hng MISTORE trn ton quc.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Lu  quan trng:</strong></p>\r\n<p>K t 3/2015, Mistore p dng chnh sch bo hnh in t thng qua S in thoi/ Series number/ iMei thit b. Theo quy nh bo hnh chnh hng, Qu khch vui lng gi li v/hp thit b  c bo hnh.<br>Thi gian tip nhn &amp; tr bo hnh t: 12h00  21h00 (Tr th 7, ch nht v ngy l)<br><strong>I. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;CHNH SCH BO HNH:</strong><br>Lu : chnh sch bo hnh / i mi ny p dng vi sn phm nhp khu, cc sn phm c phn phi chnh hng bi DGW s c bo hnh / i mi theo chnh sch / quyt nh ca n v tip nhn bo hnh DGW (Dcare)<br>1. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh (tu theo nhm sn phm) v i mi theo chnh sch bo hnh chnh hng ca Xiaomi.</p>\r\n<p>2. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh hoc i mi trong trng hp pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut (tr ngoi hnh).</p>\r\n<p>3. &nbsp; &nbsp;Quy nh v thi gian tip nhn - x l (tnh t thi im tip nhn bo hnh):</p>\r\n<p>Thi gian kim tra: Ti a 48 gi lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Thi gian x l bo