data-pb-style=R7V3VQC]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=I4I0SA7]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=TDC80AC],#html-body [data-pb-style=VPAN1PE],#html-body [data-pb-style=WL9DBX9]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"R7V3VQC\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"LBDHN1J\"><a href=\"#O4HS7HX\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"EE3FF65\"><a href=\"#PJIIQ9H\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"YKTBVF9\"><a href=\"#Y44YU9A\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"I4I0SA7\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"O4HS7HX\" data-pb-style=\"TDC80AC\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Tivi thng minh Xiaomi A2 58 inch &nbsp;l mu tivi thng minh 4K m Xiaomi mun mang ti cho khch hng. S hu rt nhiu cng ngh thng minh v hin  &nbsp;i cng cht lng v cng sc nt, ngi dng chc chn s c m chm trong nhng hnh nh v cng cun ht.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Vin mn siu mng - Tri nghim hnh nh khng gii hn</strong><br>Tivi thng minh Xiaomi A2 58 inch &nbsp;mang ti cho ngi dng mt tri nghim hnh nh v cng n tng vi khng gian hin th siu ln. y l do thit k vin siu mng gip t l mn hnh so vi thn vt xa so vi t l ca tivi tiu chun. Khi tri nghim hnh nh ngi dng kh cm nhn c ranh gii gip cho mi th c tr nn sng ng hn.</p>\r\n<p>Khung vin ca tivi c lm bng kim loi tinh t. Nh s hu thit k nguyn khi mang n cho ngi dng cm nhn v cng chc chn v bn b vt tri.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mn hnh HD 4K - Hnh nh sc nt&nbsp;</strong><br>Tivi thng minh Xiaomi A2 58 inch s hu  phn gii siu HD 4K cho hnh nh c hin th vi cht lng tt nht chi tit nht v kinh t nht. Mn hnh vi tn s qut 90Hz gip hnh nh chuyn ng mt m, c bit nng cao tri nghim trong nhng game ua xe hay thc phim hnh ng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cng ngh vt tri, dn u cht lng</strong><br>Tivi thng minh Xiaomi A2 58 inch &nbsp;c trang b rt nhiu cng ngh hin i. Trong  ni bt phi k ti nh: Cng ngh Dolby Vision, cng ngh tiu chun gam mu DCI-P3, Gam mu rng (WCG) cng vi hiu chun mu chnh xc, cng ngh c tnh Chuyn ng, cng ngh b tr chuyn ng (MEMC),... Tt c u mang ti hnh nh v cng cht lng tc  chuyn ng mt m  bn c th tn hng nhng khonh khc tuyt vi hn bao gi ht.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra tivi cng c tch hp Chromecast v Miracast  bn c th gip c xy dng trn thit b di ng ca mnh  mt mn hnh ln hn gia tng tri nghim c o hn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>m thanh cht lng chun rp chiu phim</strong><br>Tivi thng minh Xiaomi A2 58 inch &nbsp;c trang b hai loa cng sut 10W vi cng ngh m thanh ni. Nh  tri nghim gii tr ca ngi dng sng ng vi m thanh nh ngoi rp chiu phim.</p>\r\n<p>Bn cnh  thit b cn c trang b b gii m kp Dolby Audio v DTS-HD gip nng cao tri nghim gii tr m thanh ti nh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Kho ng dng a dng cng kh nng kt ni v tn</strong><br>Tivi thng minh Xiaomi A2 58 inch &nbsp;mang li kh nng gii tr v tn vi kh nng truy cp hn 400.000 chng trnh v b phim khc nhau. Thit b cn h tr ti xung ng thi hn 5000 ng dng.</p>\r\n<p>Ngi dng c th iu khin Tivi thng minh Xiaomi A2 58 inch d dng bng nhiu cch. Smart tivi Xiaomi A2 58 inch h tr iu khin t xa thng qua tr l ging ni bng cch nhn nt trn iu khin t xa. Bn cnh  l b iu khin TV thng minh bluetooth 360  gip kim sot mt cch d dng.</p>\r\n<p>Tivi thng minh Xiaomi A2 58 inch cn c th kt ni wifi ng tn kp 2.4G / 5GHz cng Bluetooth 5.0  kt ni khng dy vi cc thit b khc mt cch v cng d dng. Ngi dng cng c th chia s hnh nh t in thoi ln TV thng minh nhanh chng thng qua Chromecast v Miracast.</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"PJIIQ9H\" data-pb-style=\"WL9DBX9\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hng dn mua hng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th mua hng theo mt trong cc cch sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong>1/ Mua hng trc tip:</strong><br>Qu khch c th n trc tip tham quan, tri nghim v mua sm cc sn phm Xiaomi ti tt c cc a ch sau ca MISTORE:</p>\r\n<p>364 Nguyn Tri, Thanh Xun Trung, Thanh Xun, H Ni.<br>Hotline: 03.4567.6666</p>\r\n<p>195, An Dng Vng, Phng 8, Qun 5<br>Hotline: (028)3.888.3456</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>2/ t mua qua website ca Mistore:</strong><br>Bc 1 : Click vo sn phm bn c nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Chn  Thm Vo Gi Hng   thc hin bc tip theo ( lu  bn c th chn nhiu sn phm trong cng 1 gi hng ).</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Kim tra n hng v s lng sau  chn Tin hnh t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 4 : in y  thng tin chnh xc ca qu khch v chn phng thc thanh ton mong mun, sau  kim tra li Ha n mua hng.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu mun thm sn phm khc vo n hng qu khch chn Mua thm.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu Ha n mua hng  chnh xc, qu khch chn t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 5 : Qu khch s nhn c thng bo t hng thnh cng v M n hng t h thng. Thng tin mua hng ca qu khch s c h thng gi qua email ng k, hy lu li m s n hng  tin cho vic theo di n hng ca qu khch.</p>\r\n<p>Chng ti s lin lc vi Qu khch  xc nhn n hng v tin hnh giao hng.</p>\r\n<p>( n hng cha bao gm ph vn chuyn, ph vn chuyn s c bo c th khi nhn vin gi in cht n trc khi giao. n hng ca qu khch s t ng hy nu thng tin t hng khng y  hoc khng r rng m khng cn bo trc. Nu qu khch c nhu cu gi hng ti ca hng vui lng thanh ton trc. )</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>3/ t hng qua in thoi:</strong><b