INSERT INTO `catalog_product_entity_text` VALUES ('13',75,0,'5','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=FQSS89M],#html-body [data-pb-style=KMDU1NP],#html-body [data-pb-style=OUVMRN9]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=U2IMNSI]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=N7YSBUK]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=APPK72I],#html-body [data-pb-style=FUJJGPE],#html-body [data-pb-style=HYDXYWT]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"U2IMNSI\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"KMDU1NP\"><a href=\"#S77YXWX\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"FQSS89M\"><a href=\"#SHPJ2XU\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"OUVMRN9\"><a href=\"#MS1HUUE\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"N7YSBUK\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"S77YXWX\" data-pb-style=\"FUJJGPE\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Nu bn ang tm kim mt chic loa mini h tr tt cho cc chuyn du lch di th Loa Bluetooth mini Xiaomi Outdoor s l s la chn hp l nht. Sn phm s hu kch thc nh gn nhng c cht m v cng n tng cng kh nng chng bi v nc hiu qu, s l ngi bn ng hnh tuyt vi.</p>\r\n<p><strong>u im ca Loa Bluetooth mini Xiaomi Outdoor</strong><br>L mt sn phm loa n t thng hiu Xiaomi, Loa Bluetooth mini Xiaomi Outdoor c u t t thit k, cht m cng nhiu trang b hin i nh micro m thoi, chun khng nc,... nhng li c gi thnh kh r, gip d tip cn nhiu ngi dng hn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>m thanh sng ng, h tr m thoi</strong><br>D c v ngoi kh mini nhng Xiaomi Outdoor c trang b cu trc bn trong vi thit k tinh xo, gm rare earth dual horn cho lc t mnh m,  nhy cao cng cc chi tit sng ng hn. Mn chn gip gim xc, cho m thanh t nhin, r rng. V cui cng l b tn nhit th ng gip tng cng hiu ng m thanh, cho m thanh sng ng hn.</p>\r\n<p>Loa bluetooth mini Xiaomi cn h tr m thoi rnh tay kh tin li. C th loa c tch hp micro c  nhy cao cng cng ngh kh ting vang  m bo cht lng cuc gi r rng, tt nht.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Kt ni bluetooth hin i, thi gian dng lu di</strong><br>Tng t nh cc loa khc trn th trng, loa mini outdoor Xiaomi cng c trang b chun kt ni bluetooth 5.0 hin i, c kh nng tng thch vi nhiu thit b khc nhau, cho tn hiu kt ni nhanh chng, n nh  khong cch 10m. Bn cnh , im c bit l loa Bluetooth Xiaomi cho kh nng kt ni vi loa mini khc  to thnh h thng m thanh ni khng dy kh n tng.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra, loa c trang b dung lng pin kh ln 2000mAh, mi ln c sc y loa cho thi gian pht nhc ln ti 10 gi ( mc m lng 60%). Loa c trang b chun chng bi v chng thm nc IP55 c th ngn chn hiu qu m hi, nc ma v bi bn. Giao din sc Type-C hin i gip qu trnh sc nhanh chng hn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thit k ti gin, thch hp dng ngoi tri</strong><br>Loa bluetooth Xiaomi s hu ngoi hnh nh gn vi kch thc ch 86 x 86 x 45mm. Bn cnh  loa c trng lng l 185g, tng ng 1 chic smartphone, kh nh v vy cho php ngi dng b vo balo, ti xch  di chuyn m khng chim nhiu tch. Nh sn xut cn trang b 1 dy treo mu cam kh ni bt, c lm t vi dt c  bn cao, gip ngi dng d dng treo loa m khng s t, thch hp dng cho cc chuyn leo ni, chy xe p ngoi tri, picnic,...</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thng s k thut</strong><br>Micro: C<br>Kt ni: Bluetooth<br>Phin bn Bluetooth: V5.0<br>Khong cch truyn dn: 10 m<br>Giao thc Bluetooth: HFPIA2DP/AVRCP<br>Tham s u vo: 5 V = 1A<br>Dung lng pin: 2000 mAh<br>Thi gian sc: 12 h<br>Thi gian lm vic: 10 h<br>Giao din: Type C<br>Chng thm nc: IP55<br>Cc chc nng khc: TWS kt ni<br>Cht liu: Cht liu ABS + PC<br>Trng Lng tnh (g): 182g<br>Kch thc (cm/inch): 86 x 86 x 45mm</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"SHPJ2XU\" data-pb-style=\"APPK72I\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hng dn mua hng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th mua hng theo mt trong cc cch sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong>1/ Mua hng trc tip:</strong><br>Qu khch c th n trc tip tham quan, tri nghim v mua sm cc sn phm Xiaomi ti tt c cc a ch sau ca MISTORE:</p>\r\n<p>364 Nguyn Tri, Thanh Xun Trung, Thanh Xun, H Ni.<br>Hotline: 03.4567.6666</p>\r\n<p>195, An Dng Vng, Phng 8, Qun 5<br>Hotline: (028)3.888.3456</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>2/ t mua qua website ca Mistore:</strong><br>Bc 1 : Click vo sn phm bn c nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Chn  Thm Vo Gi Hng   thc hin bc tip theo ( lu  bn c th chn nhiu sn phm trong cng 1 gi hng ).</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Kim tra n hng v s lng sau  chn Tin hnh t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 4 : in y  thng tin chnh xc ca qu khch v chn phng thc thanh ton mong mun, sau  kim tra li Ha n mua hng.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu mun thm sn phm khc vo n hng qu khch chn Mua thm.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu Ha n mua hng  chnh xc, qu khch chn t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 5 : Qu khch s nhn c thng bo t hng thnh cng v M n hng t h thng. Thng tin mua hng ca qu khch s c h thng gi qua email ng k, hy lu li m s n hng  tin cho vic theo di n hng ca qu khch.</p>\r\n<p>Chng ti s lin lc vi Qu khch  xc nhn n hng v tin hnh giao hng.</p>\r\n<p>( n hng cha bao gm ph vn chuyn, ph vn chuyn s c bo c th khi nhn vin gi in cht n trc khi giao. n hng ca qu khch s t ng hy nu thng tin t hng khng y  hoc khng r rng m khng cn bo trc. Nu qu khch c nhu cu gi hng ti ca hng vui lng thanh ton trc. )</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>3/ t hng qua in thoi:</strong><br>Bc 1 : in thoi n s in Thoi t Hng ti Hotline:</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Cung cp y  thng tin sn phm , mu sc, chng loi , s lng sn phm m qu khch mong mun.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Cung cp y  thng tin nhn hng ca qu khch mt cch chnh xc nht  Mistore c th giao hng cho qu khch nhanh nht.</p>\r\n<p>Thng tin thanh ton chuyn khon<br>STK: 0461000266789  Vietcombank</p>\r\n<p>Ch TK: Nguyn L Phng</p>\r\n<p>Email: mistore.com.vn@gmail.com</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong> thun tin hn cho qu trnh mua hng, hin ti Mistore.com.vn h tr cc hnh thc thanh ton sau:</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton ti ca hng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tin mt (VND)</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton th ATM</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton bng th tn dng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tr gp. Tm hiu thm ti y</strong><br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton khi nhn hng</strong><br>Hng ho s c vn chuyn qua dch v Chuyn pht nhanh / Shipper n tn nh, thanh ton sau  nhn hng.</p>\r\n<p>(*) Lu : thanh ton khi nhn hng (Cash On Delivery) ch p dng vi n hng c gi tr di 2 triu ng, cha bao gm ph vn chuyn v bo him (nu c), vi n hng ln hn vui lng lin h  c hng dn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton online</strong><br>Chuyn khon qua ti khon cng ty. Xem ti y<br>Thanh ton bng th ATM<br>Thanh ton bng th tn dng<br>Thanh ton tr gp bng th tn dng<br>Th tn dng (Credit Card) l mt loi th ngn hng c tnh nng thanh ton m khng cn tin c sn trong th. Ni cch khc l bn s mn tin ca ngn hng  thanh ton v ti cui k s cn tr li y  cho ngn hng. S tin trong th tn dng c ngn hng cp gi l hn mc th tn dng.<br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Chnh sch bo hnh\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"MS1HUUE\" data-pb-style=\"HYDXYWT\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p id=\"AMAGAE3\">Cng ty TNHH Dami Vit Nam</p>\r\n<p><strong>QUY NH V BO HNH  I MI</strong><br>Chnh sch bo hnh c p dng i vi sn phm: in thoi; My tnh bng (Tablet); My tnh xch tay (Laptop); Linh kin, Ph kin trong h thng ca hng Xiaomi chnh hng MISTORE trn ton quc.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Lu  quan trng:</strong></p>\r\n<p>K t 3/2015, Mistore p dng chnh sch bo hnh in t thng qua S in thoi/ Series number/ iMei thit b. Theo quy nh bo hnh chnh hng, Qu khch vui lng gi li v/hp thit b  c bo hnh.<br>Thi gian tip nhn &amp; tr bo hnh t: 12h00  21h00 (Tr th 7, ch nht v ngy l)<br><strong>I. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;CHNH SCH BO HNH:</strong><br>Lu : chnh sch bo hnh / i mi ny p dng vi sn phm nhp khu, cc sn phm c phn phi chnh hng bi DGW s c bo hnh / i mi theo chnh sch / quyt nh ca n v tip nhn bo hnh DGW (Dcare)<br>1. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh (tu theo nhm sn phm) v i mi theo chnh sch bo hnh chnh hng ca Xiaomi.</p>\r\n<p>2. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh hoc i mi trong trng hp pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut (tr ngoi hnh).</p>\r\n<p>3. &nbsp; &nbsp;Quy nh v thi gian tip nhn - x l (tnh t thi im tip nhn bo hnh):</p>\r\n<p>Thi gian kim tra: Ti a 48 gi lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Thi gian x l bo hnh: &nbsp;15 - 30 ngy lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Nu c pht sinh vn  khc, CSKH s lin h  thng bo trc t nht 24 gi.</p>\r\n<p>4. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c thay th linh kin hoc sa cha min ph khi b h hng do li k thut t nh sn xut sau thi gian quy nh i mi.</p>\r\n<p>6. &nbsp; &nbsp; Mi loi sn phm c chnh sch bo hnh ring, Qu khch vui lng xem k chnh sch bo hnh theo tng sn phm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>II. &nbsp; &nbsp; IU KIN BO HNH:</strong><br>Sn phm cn trong thi hn bo hnh.<br>Sn phm phi cn nguyn vn, khng sa cha bi cc ni khc ngoi h thng ca hng hoc Mi Store, MiCare v Dcare.<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm phi trng hp vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t v bao b sn phm.<br>Sn phm phi cn hp nguyn vn, khng b rch, khng chp ni, khng b ty xa.<br>III. &nbsp;IU KIN I MI:<br>Sn phm c hng chnh sc