 Mi loi sn phm c chnh sch bo hnh ring, Qu khch vui lng xem k chnh sch bo hnh theo tng sn phm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>II. &nbsp; &nbsp; IU KIN BO HNH:</strong><br>Sn phm cn trong thi hn bo hnh.<br>Sn phm phi cn nguyn vn, khng sa cha bi cc ni khc ngoi h thng ca hng hoc Mi Store, MiCare v Dcare.<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm phi trng hp vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t v bao b sn phm.<br>Sn phm phi cn hp nguyn vn, khng b rch, khng chp ni, khng b ty xa.<br>III. &nbsp;IU KIN I MI:<br>Sn phm c hng chnh sch 1 i 1 nu pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut.<br>Sn phm i mi l sn phm ngang gi, cng chng loi, cng thng s k thut, cng mu sc. (Trng hp Store khng cn sn phm c cng mu vi sn phm c i mi, chng ti s thay th bng sn phm khc tng ng vi gi tr sn phm ). Nu sn phm khng c li t nh sn xut th s tnh khu tr 30% gi tr sn phm.<br>Thi gian bo hnh v i mi:<br>in thoi, Laptop: Bo hnh 12 Thng phn cng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin | Pin bo hnh 06 thng<br>Xe in, Xe cn bng: Bo hnh 06 Thng phn cng | Pin bo hnh 03 thng<br>Pin d phng: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Tai nghe: Bo hnh 03 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Loa bluetooth: Bo hnh 01 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Camera: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>n trn, n bn: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Sn phm thi trang, ph kin khc: Khng bo hnh, khng i mi.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>IV. &nbsp;TRNG HP T CHI BO HNH (H tr sa cha):</strong><br>Sn phm  ht hn bo hnh.<br>Cc vn  lin quan n ti khon, bo mt (Mt khu, MiCloud)<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm khng trng vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t (hoc ho n mua hng).<br>Sn phm b h hng do thin tai, l lt, st nh, ha hon hay do vn chuyn lm nt, mp, b, try xc, vo nc.<br>Sn phm h hng do s dng khng ng theo hng dn, do ngun in khng ng, khng n nh, do t  cp nht phn mm (up rom) khng ng k thut, Root my dn n h hng thit b.<br>Mn hnh xut hin di 3 im cht, mn hnh b sc, m, bi bn, phn quang hoc cht hn trong qu trnh s dng do tc dng lc, va p, vo nc.<br>Sn phm b r st,  bn do n mn hay do cht lng  vo.<br>Sn phm c du hiu  tho lp, sa cha thay th linh kin  nhng ni khc ngoi h thng Mistore, Micare, Dcare<br>Cc tng phm ph kin km theo sn phm khng phi l sn phm khng c bo hnh. V d: tng phm khuyn mi, mt s ph kin km theo my nh Pin, sc, cable, tai nghe...(nu c)<br>Cc trng hp yu cu v v sinh sn phm, bo tr sn phm khng nm trong hn mc bo hnh.<br>i vi pin tch hp, khng bo hnh cc trng hp ph, chm chy linh kin v cc trng hp chai, hng pin do s dng.<br>i vi loa, tai nghe v cc sn phm c loa, khng bo hnh li r, h.<br>V. Quy nh khc:<br>i vi nhng sn phm nh my tnh, in thoi,  cng lu tr, th nh. Chng ti hon ton khng chu trch nhim v vic mt d liu c nhn ca Qu khch nh: ti liu, danh b, tin nhn  khi thc hin cc yu cu Up Rom, sa cha.<br>Nu qu khch c nhu cu sao lu, backup d liu. Vui lng bo trc  nhn vin k thut thc hin.<br>VI. Chnh sch tr hng<br>Mi Store khng c chnh sch tr hng Qu khch vui lng tm hiu tnh nng hng ha hoc kim tra k sn phm.<br>Mt s trng hp c bit:<br>Qu khch c quyn tr hoc i mi trong trng hp sn phm pht sinh li do nh sn xut khng khc phc c hoc khc phc nhiu ln khng c.<br><strong>GIM C CNG TY</strong></p>\r\n<p> K</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(p dng t 01/01/2023)</p></div></div></div></div>'),('29',76,0,'10','<p> Nhp khu chnh hng Xiaomi (Bc Kinh)</p>\r\n<p> Bo hnh chnh hng 3 thng, i mi trong 7 ngy u tin.</p>\r\n<p> Mi 100% Fullbox nguyn seal</p>'),('30',85,0,'10','Tai nghe Gaming Xiaomi Black Shark JoyBuds Pro');
INSERT INTO `catalog_product_entity_text` VALUES ('31',75,0,'11','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=ESSQ3MF],#html-body [data-pb-style=US5HDOE],#html-body [data-pb-style=XEADQV5]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=E07UT36]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=JW6FRGA]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=LOHGLPT],#html-body [data-pb-style=TC71P57],#html-body [data-pb-style=XR9V3LM]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"E07UT36\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"US5HDOE\"><a href=\"#QQMB8SQ\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"XEADQV5\"><a href=\"#HQDJ4KO\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"ESSQ3MF\"><a href=\"#OIJW583\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"JW6FRGA\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"QQMB8SQ\" data-pb-style=\"TC71P57\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Tai nghe Gaming Xiaomi Black Shark JoyBuds Pro - Dng tai nghe Bluetooth chng n dnh ring cho game th. Vi thit k m cht Gaming, h tr chng n ch ng 40dB, mang n m thanh sng ng,  tr cc thp cng thi lng pin ko di n 30 ting Ha hn s l la chn hon ho m cc tn  cng ngh khng nn b l.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thit k gn nh, linh hot</strong><br>Tng t nh nhng mu tai nghe Gaming khc trn th trng, Black Shark JoyBuds Pro cng s hu thit k mini nh nhn, vi cc chi tit c cch iu gc cnh, i cng vi Housing bo trn mm mi, mang n mt chic tai nghe hi ha, trung tnh c th dng cho mi mc ch. V l dng tai nghe chng n, nn tai nghe la chn kiu thit k in-ear vi tip silicone, mang li cho ngi dng cm gic eo khc chc chn v m i.</p>\r\n<p>Sn phm i km vi 3 nt tai silicone thay th vi cc kch thc S, M v L gip ngi dng d dng la chn kch c ph hp vi cu trc tai ca mnh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Chng n ch ng ANC - 4 ch </strong><br>Tai nghe chng n ch ng Black Shark JoyBuds Pro c trang b cng ngh chng n ch ng ANC tng t nh trn Airpods Pro, h tr gim thiu nhng ting n khng mong mun t mi trng ln n 40dB. Gip bn nhn bit c nhng m thanh nh ting bc chn, ting sng trong tr chi mt cch r nt. D ang  ni n o hay trong tu in ngm, bn vn c th tn hng th gii gaming ca ring mnh m khng s b lm phin.</p>\r\n<p>Tai nghe cn c tch hp sn 4 ch  chng n khc nhau, ng vi tng nhu cu s dng  ngi dng la chn. C th, ch  chng n cn bng, thch hp s dng  qun c ph, trung tm mua sm; ch  chng n nng thng c dng  th vin hay vn phng; ch  chng n su, ph hp vi nhng ni n o nh sn bay, bn xe, tu in ngm, v cui cng l ch  chng n gi, thch hp s dng khi luyn tp th thao.</p>\r\n<p><strong>m thoi r rng vi 3 micro</strong><br>Tai nghe c trang b 3 micro tch hp trn mi tai nghe, bao gm micro m thoi, micro phn hi v micro chuyn tip. To ra cc sng m thanh ngc pha c cng tn s v bin ,  kh ting n xung quanh, ng thi gim nhiu m thanh, cho php ngi dng m thoi r rng ngay c  nhng ni c nhiu ting n.</p>\r\n<p>c bit, cng ngh kh ting n CVC ca Qualcomm cn c th t ng gim ting n t mi trng v gim ting vng trong cuc gi. T  mi li bn ni trong cuc gi u c u dy bn kia nghe r rng vi m thanh n nh hn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Kt ni Bluetooth 5.2 -  tr cc thp</strong><br>Cng ngh Bluetooth 5.2 mi gip truyn ti m thanh nhanh v n nh hn. Bn cnh , tai nghe cng c h tr codec m thanh thch ng aptX Adaptive vi  tr thp n 85ms, mang n tri nghim xem video v chi tr chi nhp vai khp hn, th v hn.</p>\r\n<p>Tai nghe Bluetooth ANC JoyBuds Pro c trang b cun dy chuyn ng siu ln 12mm. Nh , tai nghe mang n kh nng ti to m thanh ph hp vi xu hng th trng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Pin 30 gi, chng nc IPX4</strong><br>Ngoi ra, tai nghe bluetooth Xiaomi cng c trang b mt vin pin dung lng ln 420mAh, c th p ng nhu cu gii tr nhiu gi ch trong mt ln sc. Khi kt hp vi dock sc, tai nghe Bluetooth gi r Black Shark c th cho thi gian s dng n 30 gi hoc ti a 10 gi vi 1 ln sc khi  tt ANC (chng n ch ng). Black Shark JoyBuds Pro cn h tr sc nhanh trong 15 pht  p ng nhu cu s dng trong 3 gi.</p>\r\n<p>Tnh nng m ca s bt ln cng c tch hp trn chic tai nghe Xiaomi ny. C th, ch cn m hp sc gn in thoi v sau khi giao din bt ln, bn c th nhanh chng ghp ni bng 1 ln nhn.</p>\r\n<p>Phin bn tai nghe khng dy Black Shark ny ca Xiaomi cn c tch hp chun chng nc IPX4, h tr chng nc nh khi tip xc vi m hi, gip ngi dng an tm hn trong qu trnh luyn tp th thao.</p>\r\n<p>(*) thi lng pin cng b theo quy chun phng Lab, th nghim nghe nhc AAC, m lng 50%, nhit  25  C, thc th c th khc th nghim do nhiu yu t khc.</p>\r\n<p><strong>iu khin cm ng, d s dng</strong><br>Tng t nh cc dng tai nghe Bluetooth cao cp khc, Black Shark JoyBuds Pro cng h tr thao tc iu khin thng minh thng qua nt bm cm ng.</p>\r\n<p>c bit, thit k tch hp n RGB trn thn hp sc, tng ng vi tng tnh trng pin khc nhau, gip ngi dng d dng theo di v np nng lng cho tai nghe kp thi.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thng s k thut</strong><br>Model &nbsp; &nbsp;JoyBuds Pro&nbsp;<br>Bluetooth &nbsp; &nbsp;5.2&nbsp;<br>Khong cch kt ni &nbsp; &nbsp;10m&nbsp;<br>Codec m thanh &nbsp; &nbsp;SBC, AAC, aptX Adaptive&nbsp;<br>Chng nc &nbsp; &nbsp;IPX4&nbsp;<br>Dung lng pin &nbsp; &nbsp;58mAh (Tai nghe n) / 420mAh (Hp sc)&nbsp;<br>u vo hp sc &nbsp; &nbsp;5V<br>Mua Tai nghe Gaming Xiaomi Black Shark JoyBuds Pro chnh hng  u?<br>a ch ca hng Xiaomi Store chnh hng:</p>\r\n<p>TPHCM: 195 An Dng Vng, Phng 8 Qun 5</p>\r\n<p>H Ni: 364 Nguyn Tri, Th