 07 ngy u tin.<br>n trn, n bn: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Sn phm thi trang, ph kin khc: Khng bo hnh, khng i mi.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>IV. &nbsp;TRNG HP T CHI BO HNH (H tr sa cha):</strong><br>Sn phm  ht hn bo hnh.<br>Cc vn  lin quan n ti khon, bo mt (Mt khu, MiCloud)<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm khng trng vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t (hoc ho n mua hng).<br>Sn phm b h hng do thin tai, l lt, st nh, ha hon hay do vn chuyn lm nt, mp, b, try xc, vo nc.<br>Sn phm h hng do s dng khng ng theo hng dn, do ngun in khng ng, khng n nh, do t  cp nht phn mm (up rom) khng ng k thut, Root my dn n h hng thit b.<br>Mn hnh xut hin di 3 im cht, mn hnh b sc, m, bi bn, phn quang hoc cht hn trong qu trnh s dng do tc dng lc, va p, vo nc.<br>Sn phm b r st,  bn do n mn hay do cht lng  vo.<br>Sn phm c du hiu  tho lp, sa cha thay th linh kin  nhng ni khc ngoi h thng Mistore, Micare, Dcare<br>Cc tng phm ph kin km theo sn phm khng phi l sn phm khng c bo hnh. V d: tng phm khuyn mi, mt s ph kin km theo my nh Pin, sc, cable, tai nghe...(nu c)<br>Cc trng hp yu cu v v sinh sn phm, bo tr sn phm khng nm trong hn mc bo hnh.<br>i vi pin tch hp, khng bo hnh cc trng hp ph, chm chy linh kin v cc trng hp chai, hng pin do s dng.<br>i vi loa, tai nghe v cc sn phm c loa, khng bo hnh li r, h.<br>V. Quy nh khc:<br>i vi nhng sn phm nh my tnh, in thoi,  cng lu tr, th nh. Chng ti hon ton khng chu trch nhim v vic mt d liu c nhn ca Qu khch nh: ti liu, danh b, tin nhn  khi thc hin cc yu cu Up Rom, sa cha.<br>Nu qu khch c nhu cu sao lu, backup d liu. Vui lng bo trc  nhn vin k thut thc hin.<br>VI. Chnh sch tr hng<br>Mi Store khng c chnh sch tr hng Qu khch vui lng tm hiu tnh nng hng ha hoc kim tra k sn phm.<br>Mt s trng hp c bit:<br>Qu khch c quyn tr hoc i mi trong trng hp sn phm pht sinh li do nh sn xut khng khc phc c hoc khc phc nhiu ln khng c.<br><strong>GIM C CNG TY</strong></p>\r\n<p> K</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(p dng t 01/01/2023)</p></div></div></div></div>'),('38',76,0,'13','<p> Nhp khu chnh hng Xiaomi (Bc Kinh)</p>\r\n<p> Bo hnh chnh hng 3 thng, i mi trong 7 ngy u tin.</p>\r\n<p> Mi 100% Fullbox nguyn seal</p>'),('39',85,0,'13','Tai nghe TWS Redmi AirDots 3 Pro WSEJ01ZM'),('40',75,0,'14','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=AU0JEAN],#html-body [data-pb-style=B0DS224],#html-body [data-pb-style=V6KNDNE]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=CQ469VP]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=XOAU324]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=M9HAOST],#html-body [data-pb-style=O4O8QTW],#html-body [data-pb-style=QYSEMHK]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"CQ469VP\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"V6KNDNE\"><a href=\"#T90SEKE\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"AU0JEAN\"><a href=\"#E53OQR4\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"B0DS224\"><a href=\"#YAWPA9M\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"XOAU324\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"T90SEKE\" data-pb-style=\"M9HAOST\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Nu nh Redmi AirDots 3 bn tiu chun c thit k tng i ph thng v ging vi a s cc mu tai nghe khng dy TWS trn th trng th bn Pro i theo mt phong cch ring kh mi m. Phin bn Pro ln ny mang ti mt s thay i hon ton v thit k.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thit k</strong><br>Ngoi hnh ca Redmi AirDots 3 Pro kh ging vi mu tai nghe khng dy TWS Pixel Buds ti t Google. Chic tai nghe ny i km driver m thanh 9mm cng 3 microphone thu m h tr ti u ho cht ging ca ngi ni cng nh h tr cho kh nng chng n ch ng ANC. Theo Redmi qung co, AirDots 3 Pro cho kh nng kh n ti 35dB.</p>\r\n<p>Redmi AirDots 3 Pro h tr cng ngh Bluetooth 5.2 mi cho php kt ni ti nhiu thit b cng lc, c ti u ho khi s dng cng vi cc thit b smartphone chy MIUI, gim thiu  tr khi s dng vi cc thit b ca Xiaomi.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thi lng pin</strong><br>Redmi AirDots 3 Pro trang b vin pin dung lng 35mAh cho mi tai, cho php ngi dng c th nghe nhc lin tc trong vng 6 gi lin tc, hoc 3 gi lin tc nu c bt chng n ANC. y l mt thi lng pin  mc trung bnh kh. Ngoi ra, case sc ca tai nghe c vin pin 470mAh c th cung cp tng cng 28 gi nghe nhc lin tc. Sn phm s dng cng sc USB-C v c h tr sc khng dy chun Qi, tng thch vi cng ngh sc ngc khng dy hin c trn nhiu smartphone hin nay.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thng s k thut</strong><br>Model: WSEJ01ZM<br>Chun kt ni: BT 5.2<br>Trng lng 1 tai: ~4.9g<br>Kch thc tai nghe: 25.4*20.3*21.3mm<br>Tng trng lng: ~ 55g<br>Kch thc hp sc: 65*48*26mm<br>Thi gian sc tai nghe: ~ 1 ting<br>Thi gian sc hp: ~2,5 ting<br>Thi gian m thoi: ~3 ting (tt noise reduction, 50% volume, AAC encoding)<br>Thi gian nghe nhc: ~6 ting (tt noise reduction, 50% volume, AAC encoding)<br>Thi gian ch: ~28 ting (tt noise reduction, 50% volume, AAC encoding), s dng km hp<br>Input hp sc: 5V=0.5A MAX (wired)<br>Dung lng tai nghe (n): 35mAh/0.13Wh<br>Dung lng pin hp: 470mAh/1.78Wh<br>Tr khng: 32</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"E53OQR4\" data-pb-style=\"QYSEMHK\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><s