INSERT INTO `catalog_product_entity_text` VALUES ('43',75,0,'15','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=SV9CIG3],#html-body [data-pb-style=U990FBX],#html-body [data-pb-style=W9238DQ]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=FSKTA2E]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=QCTYXC5]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=AXNKCXV],#html-body [data-pb-style=FNEK12N],#html-body [data-pb-style=J3SRP4W]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"FSKTA2E\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"U990FBX\"><a href=\"#M3VS6QH\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"W9238DQ\"><a href=\"#UER7BYS\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"SV9CIG3\"><a href=\"#GLM5PPU\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"QCTYXC5\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"M3VS6QH\" data-pb-style=\"AXNKCXV\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Robot ht bi lau nh Ecovacs Deebot X2 Omni l phin bn nng cp mi v ton din nht ca nh Ecovacs t trc n nay. Ni bt vi thit k hnh vung c o cng kch thc nh gn d dng di chuyn v lm sch mi ngc ngch, trang b AI nh cao AIVI 3D 2.0, lc ht nng cp 8000Pa, dock sc ton nng t ng lm sch, lm trng hp bi, sy kh bng kh nng, t  y nc,... cng nhiu tnh nng nng cp ni bt cho kh nng lm sch siu mnh m, ti u qu trnh dn dp, n gin ha, mang ti tri nghim v sinh nh ca hiu qu cao trong thi gian ngn m khng cn chm tay.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thit k t ph mi dn dp nh ca siu sch&nbsp;</strong><br>X2 Omni ni bt vi thit k hnh vung c o, p mt, v cng nh gn khi kch thc ch 394 x 527.5 x 443.73mm nn d dng gii quyt mi thch thc trong vic dn sch ti cc khu vc kh tip cn. Vi ng knh ch 32cm cng chiu cao 9.5cm v kt cu siu mng linh hot, n c th lt nh nhng di tt c cc  ni tht v i su vo nhng khu vc c bi bn gip quy trnh v sinh tr nn hiu qu hn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Bn cnh , robot ht bi lau nh t ng git gi Ecovacs Deebot X2 Omni c tch hp cm bin pht hin cnh v thm lau tri di  lm sch t cnh ny sang cnh khc. T l bao ph cnh ln ti 99.77% v ci thin hiu sut &nbsp;lm sch 19%, m bo lm sch su cc hiu qu.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Vi cu trc dng vung, tng chiu rng ca bn chi con ln pha trc, cho php thm lau di chuyn n cc gc gn hn 30mm, gim 45% khong cch so vi bn X1. Ngoi ra, sn phm cn c trang b thm bn chi con ln chnh c kch thc ln nht do Ecovacs sn xut v cc thut ton iu khin chuyn ng c quyn c nng cao, gia tng hiu qu dn dp mt cch u vit.</p>\r\n<p><strong>S hu kh nng lm sch vt tri</strong><br>Deebot X2 Omni t ho c ng hm gi v lc ht n tng ln n 8000Pa, c thit k ring  ht bi v lm sch thm ton din vi hiu sut mnh m, gii quyt hiu qu bi bn, mng bm ln. Di s h tr ca cng ngh sng m cng tnh nng nng t ng thng minh, robot s ngn nga  nhim cho khi di chuyn v gi lau khng lm dnh bn cc khu vc  lau trong qu trnh git ngc, m bo tri nghim lm sch lin mch, v sinh v ti u ha.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cng sut lau n nh</strong><br>S hu chi lau bng vi chenille c quyn, robot ht bi lau nh Ecovacs X2 Omni c th d dng loi b nhng vt bn cng u cng cng ngh lau xoay OZMO Turbo 2.0 cung cp p lc nht qun ln sn gip lm sch su. Khi pht hin thm hoc i qua khu vc  c lm sch, cng ngh ny s ti u lc ht chuyn t ch  lau sang ht bi, m bo ngi nh lun sch trn mi b mt.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Kh nng di chuyn cc linh hot</strong><br>Ni bt vi kh nng vt chng ngi vt 22mm, robot ht bi X2 Omni c th iu hng trn tru qua cc ngng ri v nh ra, c bit l cc ngng trn b mt cao hoc khng bng phng. Do , ngi dng c th tn hng tri nghim dn dp rnh tay v thit b d dng iu hng ti cc khu vc khc nhau trong nh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cng ngh dn dp thng minh, lm sch chnh xc v hiu qu</strong><br>Cng ngh TrueMapping 3.0 hng u trong ngnh cng cm bin LiDAR c ng dng trong nhiu phng tin iu khin t ng cho php Ecovacs X2 Omni qut gc 210 , iu hng vt tri v khong cch pht hin l 10m. Sn phm c kh nng thch ng tt vi nhng kt cu thay i trong ngi nh, m bo an ton cho  c v c robot, em li tri nghim dn dp tinh t hn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Trang b cng ngh AI nhn din thng minh</strong><br>Cng ngh AIVI 3D 2.0 c tch hp trn robot ht bi lau nh Ecovacs Deebot X2 Omni nhm ci thin kh nng nhn din khng gian. Cm bin RGBD c nng cp nhn dng v thch ng trong tng mi trng nht nh. Tnh nng mi ny  c ci thin kh nng nhn dng cc vt th trn b mt sn v ch nh  ni tht  lm sch, tit kim ng k thi gian iu chnh ca ngi dng. Cng ngh AI tn tin tng kh nng nhn bit v thch nghi ca robot vi nhiu iu kin mi trng lm sch khc nhau.</p>\r\n<p><strong>ng dng thut ton hin i hng u</strong><br>Robot ht bi lau nh Deebot X2 Omni s dng cc thut ton thng minh nhm thch ng hon ho  nhiu mi trng khc nhau, m bo hiu qu lm sch cho gia nh. N t ch tinh chnh cc quyt nh v hiu sut lm sch, ng thi  xut cc gii php lm sch ti u theo thi gian, c chc nng trnh tr em trong qu trnh vn hnh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dn dp d dng cho cc h gia nh bn rn</strong><br>Trm Omni a chc nng thit lp mt tiu chun mi trong t ng ha, cung cp gii php ton din bao gm: lm sch, lm trng hp bi, sy kh bng kh nng v t ng  y nc. Vi chc nng git gi lau nh bng nc nng 55C c o, trm Omni m bo ming lau ca robot ht bi lau nh Ecovacs X2 Omni lun sch vt bn, sch vt du m, an ton cho ln s dng tip theo, tit kim thi gian v cng sc cho ngi dng, gii phng khi cc kh khn trong vic v sinh nh ca.</p>\r\n<p><strong>D dng bo tr cc b phn</strong><br>Vi thit k bn ra lm sch c th tho ri v cc b phn tm y gip tit kim ng k thi gian bo tr, mang n kh nng hot ng ti u, bn b v t xy ra tnh trng hng hc.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thi gian chy di hn</strong><br>Nh c trang b vin pin Lithium dung lng ln n 6400mAh m hiu sut lm sch ca Ecovacs Deebot X2 Omni tng ln ng k ngay c trong khng gian ln m khng phi sc li thng xuyn. Vin pin c tui th di gip robot hot ng m khng b gin on, ngi dng s tn t cng sc hn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tri nghim dn dp - tng tc chn thc thi i mi</strong><br>Vi bn  3D mi c nng cp, robot ht bi Ecovacs X2 Omni s xc nh v lm sch cc khu vc c th nh: vt bn di bn phng khch hoc vt bn  hnh lang. Ngi dng ch cn chm nh vo khu vc cn lm sch ngay trn ng dng v thit b s tin hnh nhim v, mang li tri nghim dn dp ti u. Kt hp cng tr l ging ni YIKO 2.0 tin tin cho php ngi dng thc hin: iu khin t xa, iu chnh tc v, ln lch lm sch,...gip robot ng vai tr nh mt qun gia thng minh.</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"UER7BYS\" data-pb-style=\"FNEK12N\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hng dn mua hng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th mua hng theo mt trong cc cch sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong>1/ Mua hng trc tip:</strong><br>Qu khch c th n trc tip tham quan, tri nghim v mua sm cc sn phm Xiaomi ti tt c cc a ch sau ca MISTORE:</p>\r\n<p>364 Nguyn Tri, Thanh Xun Trung, Thanh Xun, H Ni.<br>Hotline: 03.4567.6666</p>\r\n<p>195, An Dng Vng, Phng 8, Qun 5<br>Hotline: (028)3.888.3456</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>2/ t mua qua website ca Mistore:</strong><br>Bc 1 : Click vo sn phm bn c nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Chn  Thm Vo Gi Hng   thc hin bc tip theo ( lu  bn c th chn nhiu sn phm trong cng 1 gi hng ).</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Kim tra n hng v s lng sau  chn Tin hnh t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 4 : in y  thng tin chnh xc ca qu khch v chn phng thc thanh ton mong mun, sau  kim tra li Ha n mua hng.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu mun thm sn phm khc vo n hng qu khch chn Mua thm.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu Ha n mua hng  chnh xc, qu khch chn t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 5 : Qu khch s nhn c thng bo t hng thnh cng v M n hng t h thng. Thng tin mua hng ca qu khch s c h thng gi qua email ng k, hy lu li m s n hng  tin cho vic theo di n hng ca qu khch.</p>\r\n<p>Chng ti s lin lc vi Qu khch  xc nhn n hng v tin hnh giao hng.</p>\r\n<p>( n hng cha bao gm ph vn chuyn, ph vn chuyn s c bo c th khi nhn vin gi in cht n trc khi giao. n hng ca qu khch s t ng hy nu thng tin t hng khng y  hoc khng r rng m khng cn bo trc. Nu qu khch c nhu cu gi hng ti ca hng vui lng thanh ton trc. )</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>3/ t hng qua in thoi:</strong><br>Bc 1 : in thoi n s in Thoi t Hng ti Hotline:</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Cung cp y  thng tin sn phm , mu sc, chng loi , s lng sn phm m qu khch mong mun.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Cung cp y  thng tin nhn hng ca qu khch mt cch chnh xc nht  Mistore c th giao hng cho qu khch nhanh nht.</p>\r\n<p>Thng tin thanh ton chuyn khon<br>STK: 0461000266789  Vietcombank</p>\r\n<p>Ch TK: Nguyn L Phng</p>\r\n<p>Email: mistore.com.vn@gmail.com</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong> thun tin hn cho qu trnh mua hng, hin ti Mistore.com.vn h tr cc hnh thc thanh ton sau:</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton ti ca hng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tin mt (VND)</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton th ATM</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton bng th tn dng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tr gp. Tm hiu thm ti y</strong><br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton khi nhn hng</strong><br>Hng ho s c vn chuyn qua dch v Chuyn pht nhanh / Shipper n tn nh, thanh ton sau  nhn hng.</p>\r\n<p>(*) Lu : thanh ton khi nhn hng (Cash On Delivery) ch p dng vi n hng c gi tr di 2 triu ng, cha bao gm ph vn chuyn v bo him (nu c), vi n hng ln hn vui lng lin h  c hng dn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton online</strong><br>Chuyn khon qua ti khon cng ty. Xem ti y<br>Thanh ton bng th ATM<br>Thanh ton bng th tn dng<br>Thanh ton tr gp bng th tn dng<br>Th tn dng (Credit Card) l mt loi th ngn hng c tnh nng thanh ton m khng cn tin c sn trong th. Ni cch khc l bn s mn tin ca ngn hng  thanh ton v ti cui k s cn tr li y  cho ngn hng. S tin trong th tn dng c ngn hng cp gi l hn mc th tn dng.<br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Chnh sch bo hnh\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"GLM5PPU\" data-pb-style=\"J3SRP4W\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p id=\"AMAGAE3\">Cng ty TNHH Dami Vit Nam</p>\r\n<p><strong>QUY NH V BO HNH  I MI</strong><br>Chnh sch bo hnh c p dng i vi sn phm: in thoi; My tnh bng (Tablet); My tnh xch tay (Laptop); Linh kin, Ph kin trong h thng ca hng Xiaomi chnh hng MISTORE trn ton quc.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Lu  quan trng:</strong></p>\r\n<p>K t 3/2015, Mistore p dng chnh sch bo hnh in t thng qua S in thoi/ Series number/ iMei thit b. Theo quy nh bo hnh chnh hng, Qu khch vui lng gi li v/hp thit b  c bo hnh.<br>Thi gian tip nhn &amp; tr bo hnh t: 12h00  21h00 (Tr th 7, ch nht v ngy l)<br><strong>I. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;CHNH SCH BO HNH:</strong><br>Lu : chnh sch bo hnh / i mi ny p dng vi sn phm nhp khu, cc sn phm c phn phi chnh hng bi DGW s c bo hnh / i mi theo chnh sch / quyt nh ca n v tip nhn bo hnh DGW (Dcare)<br>1. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh (tu theo nhm sn phm) v i mi theo chnh sch bo hnh chnh hng ca Xiaomi.</p>\r\n<p>2. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh hoc i mi trong trng hp pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut (tr ngoi hnh).</p>\r\n<p>3. &nbsp; &nbsp;Quy nh v thi gian tip nhn - x l (tnh t thi im tip nhn bo hnh):</p>\r\n<p>Thi gian kim tra: Ti a 48 gi lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Thi gian x l bo hnh: &nbsp;15 - 30 ngy lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Nu c pht sinh vn  khc, CSKH s lin h  thng bo trc t nht 24 gi.</p>\r\n<p>4. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c thay th linh kin hoc sa cha min ph khi b h hng do li k thut t nh sn xut sau thi gian quy nh i mi.</p>\r\n<p>6. &nbsp; &nbsp; Mi loi sn phm c chnh sch bo hnh ring, Qu khch vui lng xem k chnh sch bo hnh theo tng sn phm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>II. &nbsp; &nbsp; IU KIN BO HNH:</strong><br>Sn phm cn trong thi hn bo hnh.<br>Sn phm phi cn nguyn vn, khng sa cha bi cc ni khc ngoi h thng ca hng hoc Mi Store, MiCare v Dcare.<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm phi trng hp vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t v bao b sn phm.<br>Sn phm phi cn hp nguyn vn, khng b rch, khng chp ni, khng b ty xa.<br>III. &nbsp;IU KIN I MI:<br>Sn phm c hng chnh sch 1 i 1 nu pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut.<br>Sn phm i mi l sn phm ngang gi, cng chng loi, cng thng s k thut, cng mu sc. (Trng hp Store khng cn sn phm c cng mu vi sn phm c i mi, chng ti s thay th bng sn phm khc tng ng vi gi tr sn phm ). Nu sn phm khng c li t nh sn xut th s tnh khu tr 30% gi tr sn phm.<br>Thi gian bo hnh v i mi:<br>in thoi, Laptop: Bo hnh 12 Thng phn cng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin | Pin bo hnh 06 thng<br>Xe in, Xe cn bng: Bo hnh 06 Thng phn cng | Pin bo hnh 03 thng<br>Pin d phng: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Tai nghe: Bo hnh 03 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Loa bluetooth: Bo hnh 01 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Camera: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>n trn, n bn: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Sn phm thi trang, ph kin khc: Khng bo hnh, khng i mi.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>IV. &nbsp;TRNG HP T CHI BO HNH (H tr sa cha):</strong><br>Sn phm  ht hn bo hnh.<br>Cc vn  lin quan n ti khon, bo mt (Mt khu, MiCloud)<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm khng trng vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t (hoc ho n mua hng).<br>Sn phm b h hng do thin tai, l lt, st nh, ha hon hay do vn chuyn lm nt, mp, b, try xc, vo nc.<br>Sn phm h hng do s dng khng ng theo hng dn, do ngun in khng ng, khng n nh, do t  cp nht phn mm (up rom) khng ng k thut, Root my dn n h hng thit b.<br>Mn hnh xut hin di 3 im cht, mn hnh b sc, m, 