nd-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"IPLKYJ7\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"C8AO070\"><a href=\"#URQ8OI6\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"WJUGHOW\"><a href=\"#MYQO25S\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"FQAOY17\"><a href=\"#W2N8RXN\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"XVC6D9D\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"URQ8OI6\" data-pb-style=\"E0WDN98\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Dreame L10s Ultra l mt trong nhng model bn chy nht trong phn khc cao cp ca Dreame ti th trng Vit Nam. Tip ni thnh cng , hng tip tc trnh lng mu Dreame 10s Ultra SE hi t  cng ngh hin i, mang n cho khch hng ngi nh sch s thm tho. Sau mt ngy di bn rn tr v bn c th ngh ngi thoi mi trong t m ca mnh m khng cn bn tm n vic dn dp.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Hot ng thng minh, dn dp hiu qu</strong><br>H thng iu hng h tr Ai m bo ton b ngi nh ca bn s c lm sch hiu qu, khng b qua bt c khu vc no trn sn, hn ch vic phi lm sch nhiu ln, khng th xc nh phng hng hoc b mc kt.<br>&nbsp;<br>Tr tu nhn to Al nng cao c tch hp, kt hp vi cm bin RGB v h thng iu hng LiDAR gip robol nhanh chng nm r ngi nh ca bn v ln k hoch lm sch ph hp. Ngoi ra, trang b ny cn gip robot t ng lao ng dn  trnh chng ngi vt trn sn hiu qu.<br>Lc ht mnh m, t ng iu chnh, lm sch su<br>Tc, bi bn v cc mnh vn khc s khng b b st vi thit k bn chi c bit ca Dreame L10s Ultra SE. Thit b s kho lo nh bt cc loi bi mn, lng, tc trn nn nh.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>Tt c l nh vo lc ht 5,300Pa mnh m, tnh nng t ng pht hin v tng cng lc ht trn thm. Bn chi cao su mi, gip nh bt cc mnh vn, bi bn ra khi b mt thm mt cc nh nhng.<br>Quy trnh t lm sch khp kn<br>L10s Ultra SE s t v sinh hp cha bi v khay nc bn mt cch hon ton t ng. Nh vy, bn s khng phi lo lng chuyn v sinh robof trong sut 60 ngy tip theo. Tt c nhng g bn phi lm l b ti rc v nc thi ti trm sc sau mt khong thi gian nht nh.</p>\r\n<p>Nh quy trnh t ng lm sch khay cha c quyn ca Dreame mang tn DualBoost 2.0, h thng s thi khng khi vo hp ng bi ca robot v a lng bi ny vo ti ng c thit k trong thn trm sc.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thit k xoay to lc xoy</strong><br>Gi lau ca L10s Ulfra SE c thit k  xoay 360 , vi tn s 180 ln/pht, kt hp vi lc nn t thn my, to lc xoy cun mi vt bn khi sn mt cch hiu qu v nhanh chng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Dreame L10s Ultra SE s t ng iu tit thm nc sch v nc lau sn xung gi lau trong lc hot ng vi t l thch hp  lm cho sn nh ca bn khng ch sch m cn thm v sng bng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>T git v sy kh gi lau, ngn nm mc v mi hi</strong><br>L10s Ultra SE c trang b h thng tun hon nc t ng, cho php git sch cp gi lau sau khi hon thnh chu trnh lm sch nh ca. Hn th na, qui trnh khp kn ny cn t sy kh gi lau (thi gian d kin 2 gi *| bang khi nng  ngn mi hi, nm mc sinh si bn trong gi. m bo nh ca lun sch, thong, khng mi hi v vi khun gy hi.<br><strong>Cm bin thm</strong><br>Dreame L10s Ulfra SE c trang b tnh nng ht bi bn trn thm. Mi khi cm bin pht hin thm, robot s t ng iu chnh lc ht sao cho ph hp  loi b bi bn, vy da, bi, v cc mnh vn trong thm. Thit b cng s t ng nng gi lau ln  gi thm kh ro trong sut qu trnh ht bi trn thm, ngn mi hi v nm mc c c hi pht trin.</p>\r\n<p><strong>C nhn ha mi thit lp</strong><br>Vic kim sot thit b thng qua ng dng cha bao gi n gin n th. Ngi dng d dng iu chnh vic dn dp ca robot ph hp vi nhu cu v lch trnh lm vic ca gia nh mt cch khoa hc. Hn na, ngi dng cn c th kim sot lng nc,  m t ca gi lau hay lc ht, thm ch l s kt hp ca ht &amp; lau, ch ht hoc ch lau.  lm c iu ny, sau khi khi ng, L10s Ultra SE s bt u chu trnh qut v lp k hoch lau dn vi bn  3D, kt hp vi tr tu nhn to Al, thit b s to bn  cho tng lng/ phng v to lch trnh dn dp thch hp. Ngoi ra, ngi dng cng c th to cc bc tng o, t vng cm cho phng hay khng vc khng lau dn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>iu khin t xa thng minh</strong><br>iu khin Dreame tr nn d dng hn bao gi ht, khi m gi y ngi dng c th ra lnh qua ging ni  thay i trng thi hot ng ca L10s Ultra SE. Cn g tuyt vi hn khi bn khng cn chm tay vo thit b m vn c th ra lnh cho robot i dn nh!</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"MYQO25S\" data-pb-style=\"KO7ECP6\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hng dn mua hng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th mua hng theo mt trong cc cch sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong>1/ Mua hng trc tip:</strong><br>Qu khch c th n trc tip tham quan, tri nghim v mua sm cc sn phm Xiaomi ti tt c cc a ch sau ca MISTORE:</p>\r\n<p>364 Nguyn Tri, Thanh Xun Trung, Thanh Xun, H Ni.<br>Hotline: 03.4567.6666</p>\r\n<p>195, An Dng Vng, Phng 8, Qun 5<br>Hotline: (028)3.888.3456</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>2/ t mua qua website ca Mistore:</strong><br>Bc 1 : Click vo sn phm bn c nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Chn  Thm Vo Gi Hng   thc hin bc tip theo ( lu  bn c th chn nhiu sn phm trong cng 1 gi hng ).</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Kim tra n hng v s lng sau  chn Tin hnh t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 4 : in y  thng tin chnh xc ca qu khch v chn phng thc thanh ton mong mun, sau  kim tra li Ha n mua hng.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu mun thm sn phm khc vo n hng qu khch chn Mua thm.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu Ha n mua hng  chnh xc, qu khch chn t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 5 : Qu khch s nhn c thng bo t hng thnh cng v M n hng t h thng. Thng tin mua hng ca qu khch s c h thng gi qua email ng k, hy lu li m s n hng  tin cho vic theo di n hng ca qu khch.</p>\r\n<p>Chng ti s lin lc vi Qu khch  xc nhn n hng v tin hnh giao hng.</p>\r\n<p>( n hng cha bao gm ph vn chuyn, ph vn chuyn s c bo c th khi nhn vin gi in cht n trc khi giao. n hng ca qu khch s t ng hy nu thng tin t hng khng y  hoc khng r rng m khng cn bo trc. Nu qu khch c nhu cu gi hng ti ca hng vui lng thanh ton trc. )</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>3/ t hng qua in thoi:</strong><br>Bc 1 : in thoi n s in Thoi t Hng ti Hotline:</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Cung cp y  thng tin sn phm , mu sc, chng loi , s lng sn phm m qu khch mong mun.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Cung cp y  thng tin nhn hng ca qu khch mt cch chnh xc nht  Mistore c th giao hng cho qu khch nhanh nht.</p>\r\n<p>Thng tin thanh ton chuyn khon<br>STK: 0461000266789  Vietcombank</p>\r\n<p>Ch TK: Nguyn L Phng</p>\r\n<p>Email: mistore.com.vn@gmail.com</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong> thun tin hn cho qu trnh mua hng, hin ti Mistore.com.vn h tr cc hnh thc thanh ton sau:</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton ti ca hng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tin mt (VND)</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton th ATM</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton bng th tn dng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tr gp. Tm hiu thm ti y</strong><br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton khi nhn hng</strong><br>Hng ho s c vn chuyn qua dch v Chuyn pht nhanh / Shipper n tn nh, thanh ton sau  nhn hng.</p>\r\n<p>(*) Lu : thanh ton khi nhn hng (Cash On Delivery) ch p dng vi n hng c gi tr di 2 triu ng, cha bao gm ph vn chuyn v bo him (nu c), vi n hng ln hn vui lng lin h  c hng dn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton online</strong><br>Chuyn khon qua ti khon cng ty. Xem ti y<br>Thanh ton bng th ATM<br>Thanh ton bng th tn dng<br>Thanh ton tr gp bng th tn dng<br>Th tn dng (Credit Card) l mt loi th ngn hng c tnh nng thanh ton m khng cn tin c sn trong th. Ni cch khc l bn s mn tin ca ngn hng  thanh ton v ti cui k s cn tr li y  cho ngn hng. S tin trong th tn dng c ngn hng cp gi l hn mc th tn dng.<br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Chnh sch bo hnh\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"W2N8RXN\" data-pb-style=\"N8KAFS4\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p id=\"AMAGAE3\">Cng ty TNHH Dami Vit Nam</p>\r\n<p><strong>QUY NH V BO HNH  I MI</strong><br>Chnh sch bo hnh c p dng i vi sn phm: in thoi; My tnh bng (Tablet); My tnh xch tay (Laptop); Linh kin, Ph kin trong h thng ca hng Xiaomi chnh hng MISTORE trn ton quc.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Lu  quan trng:</strong></p>\r\n<p>K t 3/2015, Mistore p dng chnh sch bo hnh in t thng qua S in thoi/ Series number/ iMei thit b. Theo quy nh bo hnh chnh hng, Qu khch vui lng gi li v/hp thit b  c bo hnh.<br>Thi gian tip nhn &amp; tr bo hnh t: 12h00  21h00 (Tr th 7, ch nht v ngy l)<br><strong>I. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;CHNH SCH BO HNH:</strong><br>Lu : chnh sch bo hnh / i mi ny p dng vi sn phm nhp khu, cc sn phm c phn phi chnh hng bi DGW s c bo hnh / i mi theo chnh sch / quyt nh ca n v tip nhn bo hnh DGW (Dcare)<br>1. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh (tu theo nhm sn phm) v i mi theo chnh sch bo hnh chnh hng ca Xiaomi.</p>\r\n<p>2. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh hoc i mi trong trng hp pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut (tr ngoi hnh).</p>\r\n<p>3. &nbsp; &nbsp;Quy nh v thi gian tip nhn - x l (tnh t thi im tip nhn bo hnh):</p>\r\n<p>Thi gian kim tra: Ti a 48 gi lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Thi gian x l bo hnh: &nbsp;15 - 30 ngy lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Nu c pht sinh vn  khc, CSKH s lin h  thng bo trc t nht 24 gi.</p>\r\n<p>4. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c thay th linh kin hoc sa cha min ph khi b h hng do li k thut t nh sn xut sau thi gian quy nh i mi.</p>\r\n<p>6. &nbsp; &nbsp; Mi loi sn phm c chnh sch bo hnh ring, Qu khch vui lng xem k chnh sch bo hnh theo tng sn phm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>II.