INSERT INTO `catalog_product_entity_text` VALUES ('49',75,0,'17','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=GOGOBAF],#html-body [data-pb-style=IWJUN08],#html-body [data-pb-style=T9GRJRV]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=OCM6EV3]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=XE96EM7]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=LMU7XK7],#html-body [data-pb-style=NA5T3SK],#html-body [data-pb-style=WQCOT43]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"OCM6EV3\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"IWJUN08\"><a href=\"#GKM60UB\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"GOGOBAF\"><a href=\"#F76OPBM\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"T9GRJRV\"><a href=\"#ETY2U6U\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"XE96EM7\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"GKM60UB\" data-pb-style=\"WQCOT43\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Khng ngng chinh phc th trng Vit Nam vi hng lot thit b gia dng nh r-bt ht bi thng minh, Dreame va a ra th trng chic my ht bi khng dy Dreame R10 Pro, ang c lng ngi tiu dng ti nhiu quc gia trn th gii v nay  chnh thc c mt ti Vit Nam. L s kt hp hon ho gia cht lng v gi c , chic Dreame R10 khng ch em n kh nng lm sch vt tri m cn th hin s tin ch vi thit k khng dy, gip ngi dng d dng di chuyn v lm sch mi gc khut trong ngi nh ca mnh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Lm sch mnah m v n nh bng n</strong><br>My ht bi tch in Dreame R10 Pro t ho c ng c khng chi than tc  cao , m bo lc ht n nh trong sut qu trnh lm sch. c trang b n LED v u bn chi c th hon i cho nhau, to iu kin lm sch ton din vi lc ht n tng 150AW.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Lm sch mnh m v thi gian chy n nh</strong><br>Tri nghim lc ht mnh m v lin tc trong ti a 65 pht lm sch khng dy. Vi ng c khng chi than tc  cao, chy  tc  120.000 vng/pht v b pin 7x 3.000mAh, my ht bi ny mang li lc ht mnh m  x l tc, bi bn v mnh vn mt cch hiu qu, m bo dn dp nh ca k lng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Chiu sng lm sch vi mi ngc ngch</strong><br>Vi s h tr ca n LED, mi ngc ngch v k h ti tm u c th c chiu sng r rng, m bo s sch s ton din trong ton b ngi nh ca bn. Cp n LED pha trc lm sng ton b khu vc nh rng mt cch hiu qu, loi b mi bng ti hoc nhng im n m bi bn, mnh vn hoc tc c th n giu.</p>\r\n<p><strong>u ht chi ch V a nng</strong><br>Lc chi nhiu b mt c lng hnh ch V gip ht tc nhanh chng, cun tc theo thit k ging nh rng lc. Thit k ging nh chic lc ci tin gip g ri tc v gip tc  c nht di chuyn thng vo bn trong. cc cha bi, gi cho vic v sinh n gin v nhanh chng</p>\r\n<p>u bn chi c th hon i cho nhau tng cng s tin li khi lm sch.<br>u chi ln mm c kh nng thch ng gip bn d dng lm sch bi bn v tc trn bt k loi sn no khc. Tnh linh hot to iu kin lm sch xung quanh cc ng vin v gc hp hn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>H thng lc nhiu lp</strong><br>H thng lc nm lp tin tin gip thu gi bi v cc ht mn v gi chng cch xa khng kh vi hiu sut lc ln ti 99,9%.Gip bo v sc khe c gia nh. Ngoi ra, b lc bi cn c th v sinh v ti s dng d dng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Ht lng th cc d</strong><br>Vi  ln hn trn bn chi a b mt hnh ch V, bn chi mini c ng c tin tin c ti u ha  loi b tc, lng th, mt v vy trn vi v  ni tht.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>B pin lp tp linh hot</strong><br>B pin c th thay th cho php bn hon i pin mt cch lin mch  tng gp i thi gian v sinh. Gi treo lu tr trn tng gip d dng tip cn v ct gi thun tin cho my ht bi ca bn v tt c cc ph kin i km.</p>\r\n<p><strong>D dng v sinh v bo tr&nbsp;</strong><br>S tin li ca vic lm sch b lc ch bng mt ln nhn, cng vi lc xoy a hnh nn, b lc, chi ln v b lc trc c th git c, gip n gin ha ng k qu trnh lm sch</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thng s k Thut</strong><br>Cng sut nh mc: 425W<br>Thi gian chy: 65 pht<br>Cng sut ht: &nbsp;150AW<br>Lc ht: 20.000 Pa<br>Tc  quay ca ng c: &nbsp;120.000<br>Gi pin: &nbsp;7 x 3.000mAh<br>Khi lng thng rc: 0.6 L<br>Trng lng: 1.65kg<br>Thi gian sc: Khong 4 Ting&nbsp;<br>Thi gian hot ng ti a: 65 Pht&nbsp;</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"F76OPBM\" data-pb-style=\"NA5T3SK\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hng dn mua hng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th mua hng theo mt trong cc cch sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong>1/ Mua hng trc tip:</strong><br>Qu khch c th n trc tip tham quan, tri nghim v mua sm cc sn phm Xiaomi ti tt c cc a ch sau ca MISTORE:</p>\r\n<p>364 Nguyn Tri, Thanh Xun Trung, Thanh Xun, H Ni.<br>Hotline: 03.4567.6666</p>\r\n<p>195, An Dng Vng, Phng 8, Qun 5<br>Hotline: (028)3.888.3456</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>2/ t mua qua website ca Mistore:</strong><br>Bc 1 : Click vo sn phm bn c nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Chn  Thm Vo Gi Hng   thc hin bc tip theo ( lu  bn c th chn nhiu sn phm trong cng 1 gi hng ).</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Kim tra n hng v s lng sau  chn Tin hnh t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 4 : in y  thng tin chnh xc ca qu khch v chn phng thc thanh ton mong mun, sau  kim tra li Ha n mua hng.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu mun thm sn phm khc vo n hng qu khch chn Mua thm.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu Ha n mua hng  chnh xc, qu khch chn t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 5 : Qu khch s nhn c thng bo t hng thnh cng v M n hng t h thng. Thng tin mua hng ca qu khch s c h thng gi qua email ng k, hy lu li m s n hng  tin cho vic theo di n hng ca qu khch.</p>\r\n<p>Chng ti s lin lc vi Qu khch  xc nhn n hng v tin hnh giao hng.</p>\r\n<p>( n hng cha bao gm ph vn chuyn, ph vn chuyn s c bo c th khi nhn vin gi in cht n trc khi giao. n hng ca qu khch s t ng hy nu thng tin t hng khng y  hoc khng r rng m khng cn bo trc. Nu qu khch c nhu cu gi hng ti ca hng vui lng thanh ton trc. )</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>3/ t hng qua in thoi:</strong><br>Bc 1 : in thoi n s in Thoi t Hng ti Hotline:</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Cung cp y  thng tin sn phm , mu sc, chng loi , s lng sn phm m qu khch mong mun.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Cung cp y  thng tin nhn hng ca qu khch mt cch chnh xc nht  Mistore c th giao hng cho qu khch nhanh nht.</p>\r\n<p>Thng tin thanh ton chuyn khon<br>STK: 0461000266789  Vietcombank</p>\r\n<p>Ch TK: Nguyn L Phng</p>\r\n<p>Email: mistore.com.vn@gmail.com</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong> thun tin hn cho qu trnh mua hng, hin ti Mistore.com.vn h tr cc hnh thc thanh ton sau:</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton ti ca hng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tin mt (VND)</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton th ATM</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton bng th tn dng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tr gp. Tm hiu thm ti y</strong><br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton khi nhn hng</strong><br>Hng ho s c vn chuyn qua dch v Chuyn pht nhanh / Shipper n tn nh, thanh ton sau  nhn hng.</p>\r\n<p>(*) Lu : thanh ton khi nhn hng (Cash On Delivery) ch p dng vi n hng c gi tr di 2 triu ng, cha bao gm ph vn chuyn v bo him (nu c), vi n hng ln hn vui lng lin h  c hng dn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton online</strong><br>Chuyn khon qua ti khon cng ty. Xem ti y<br>Thanh ton bng th ATM<br>Thanh ton bng th tn dng<br>Thanh ton tr gp bng th tn dng<br>Th tn dng (Credit Card) l mt loi th ngn hng c tnh nng thanh ton m khng cn tin c sn trong th. Ni cch khc l bn s mn tin ca ngn hng  thanh ton v ti cui k s cn tr li y  cho ngn hng. S tin trong th tn dng c ngn hng cp gi l hn mc th tn dng.<br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Chnh sch bo hnh\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"ETY2U6U\" data-pb-style=\"LMU7XK7\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p id=\"AMAGAE3\">Cng ty TNHH Dami Vit Nam</p>\r\n<p><strong>QUY NH V BO HNH  I MI</strong><br>Chnh sch bo hnh c p dng i vi sn phm: in thoi; My tnh bng (Tablet); My tnh xch tay (Laptop); Linh kin, Ph kin trong h thng ca hng Xiaomi chnh hng MISTORE trn ton quc.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Lu  quan trng:</strong></p>\r\n<p>K t 3/2015, Mistore p dng chnh sch bo hnh in t thng qua S in thoi/ Series number/ iMei thit b. Theo quy nh bo hnh chnh hng, Qu khch vui lng gi li v/hp thit b  c bo hnh.<br>Thi gian tip nhn &amp; tr bo hnh t: 12h00  21h00 (Tr th 7, ch nht v ngy l)<br><strong>I. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;CHNH SCH BO HNH:</strong><br>Lu : chnh sch bo hnh / i mi ny p dng vi sn phm nhp khu, cc sn phm c phn phi chnh hng bi DGW s c bo hnh / i mi theo chnh sch / quyt nh ca n v tip nhn bo hnh DGW (Dcare)<br>1. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh (tu theo nhm sn phm) v i mi theo chnh sch bo hnh chnh hng ca Xiaomi.</p>\r\n<p>2. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh hoc i mi trong trng hp pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut (tr ngoi hnh).</p>\r\n<p>3. &nbsp; &nbsp;Quy nh v thi gian tip nhn - x l (tnh t thi im tip nhn bo hnh):</p>\r\n<p>Thi gian kim tra: Ti a 48 gi lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Thi gian x l bo hnh: &nbsp;15 - 30 ngy lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Nu c pht sinh vn  khc, CSKH s lin h  thng bo trc t nht 24 gi.</p>\r\n<p>4. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c thay th linh kin hoc sa cha min ph khi b h hng do li k thut t nh sn xut sau thi gian quy nh i mi.</p>\r\n<p>6. &nbsp; &nbsp; Mi loi sn phm c chnh sch bo hnh ring, Qu khch vui lng xem k chnh sch bo hnh theo tng sn phm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>II. &nbsp