" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"A6I73C7\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"L7GMCPE\"><a href=\"#XPIQFN6\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"B9QG6HQ\"><a href=\"#B5J37XB\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"N4MX6PX\"><a href=\"#M5LAWEG\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"LTSWJOQ\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"XPIQFN6\" data-pb-style=\"HT44VEX\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Qun cy lau nh thng thng i - gi y bn c th ht bi v lau sn nh bng mt thit b! My ht bi Dreame H12 Dual c tch hp ng c khng chi than mnh m, nh  n loi b bi, vn, lng th cng v cc cht thi khc mt cch nhanh chng v hiu qu. N c th d dng x l cc vt bn cng u v  ung b . B ny cng bao gm mt con ln d phng, v vy nu cn, bn c th thay th n mt cch n gin - khng cn phi mua thm ph kin ngay lp tc.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thit k nh gn, tin dng</strong><br>Dn dp c th rt th v vi Dreame. My ht bi Dreame H12 Dual rt d s dng v nh thit k gn nh, tin dng, n m bo s thoi mi khi s dng trong thi gian di. Ngn cha nc sch ca my c dung tch ln n 900 ml nn bn khng cn phi  y nc thng xuyn. Ngoi ra, trm sc i km ng vai tr nh mt gi  v cung cp gi  thit thc cho cc ph kin, h tr rt nhiu cho vic bo qun my ht bi.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tnh nang va ht va lau thun tin</strong><br>My ht bi lau sn Dreame H12 Dual pht hin thng minh mc  nhim bn b mt v t ng iu chnh lc ht cho ph hp . Nh , n c th nhanh chng loi b cc loi tp cht, ng thi tit kim nng lng. Tn hng hiu sut ti u v ni li tm bit vi bi bn cng u!</p>\r\n<p>Gi y, bn thm ch c th iu chnh tt hn cng vic ca my ht bi theo nhu cu ca mnh. Dreame H12 Dual cho php bn chn t mt s ch  lm sch. Ch  T ng rt ph hp  s dng hng ngy v ch  Ht rt ph hp  loi b vt bn. Nu bn chn s dng my ht bi cm tay, ch  Tiu chun s c kch hot theo mc nh. Ngoi ra cn c mt ch  Turbo c bit theo  ca bn.</p>\r\n<p>Hy t mnh thy rng vic lm sch sn nh k lng khng cn phi tn nhiu cng sc. My ht bi cung cp mt bn chi ci tin cho php bn lm sch hiu qu dc theo cc cnh v  nhng ni nh gc phng. B ny cng bao gm cc ph kin b sung s gip bn lm sch cc gc kh tip cn. Trong gi, bn s tm thy, chng hn nh bn chi in mini v bn chi k h 2 trong 1. m st chn tng v lm sch su vo cc cnh v gc nh 2 cnh thit k lm sch m rng bn chi n tn mp my ca bn  cch vn chn tng trong vng 6 mm nhm gip m bo ton b sn nh ca bn c lm sch k lng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Hot ng ln n 60 pht ht bi trong mt ln sc y</strong><br>Bn khng cn phi lo lng my ht bi ht in t ngt v phi dng cng vic v sinh  sc li. Dreame H12 Dual c trang b vin pin 4000 mAh, tng ng vi khong 60 pht ht bi hoc khong 35 pht lau sn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>D dnh s dng, hot ng d dng hn</strong><br>Tn hng hot ng thun tin hn na ca my ht bi. Mu H12 Dual  c trang b mt mn hnh LED nh cho php bn kim tra nhanh cc thng tin nh trng thi hot ng ca thit b v mc sc pin. Sn phm cng h tr tin nhn thoi - n s nhc nh bn, trong s nhng th khc, v s cn thit phi  y nc vo bnh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tnh nng t ng lm sch</strong><br>Dreame H12 Dual cng c th t ng lm sch v lm kh con ln. Bn khng cn phi lng ph thi gian ca bn! Sy kh bng khng kh nng, vi nhit  55C (131F) gip m bo bn chi c lm sch ch trong vng 30 pht, do , bn chi khng c c hi b nm mc hoc c mi kh chu v nhanh chng sn sng cho ln s dng tip theo ca bn. Ch cn t my ht bi vo trm sc v nhn nt thch hp. &nbsp;iu ny ngn chn s hnh thnh ca nm mc v mi kh chu, ng thi ngn chn s sinh si ca vi khun.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thng s k thut</strong><br>Lc ht: 16.000Pa<br>Cng sut nh mc: 300W<br>ng c: khng chi than<br>Trng lng my: 5,1kg<br>Bn nc sch: 900mL<br>Bn nc  qua s dng: 700mL<br>Dung lng pin: 6x4000mAh<br>Thi gian sc: 4,5 gi<br>Thi gian chy ti a: 35 pht (My ht kh v t)<br>60 pht (My ht cm tay)<br>Loi bn chi: Lm sch t cnh ny sang cnh khc<br>Pht hin bi bn: C<br>Ch  lm vic: Ch  t ng/Ht (Chn khng kh v t)<br>Ch  tiu chun/Turbo (Ht chn khng cm tay v dng que)<br>T lm sch: C<br>T sy kh: Hi nng<br>Mn hnh: LED<br>Li nhc: C</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"B5J37XB\" data-pb-style=\"Q6BMWUE\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hng dn mua hng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th mua hng theo mt trong cc cch sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong>1/ Mua hng trc tip:</strong><br>Qu khch c th n trc tip tham quan, tri nghim v mua sm cc sn phm Xiaomi ti tt c cc a ch sau ca MISTORE:</p>\r\n<p>364 Nguyn Tri, Thanh Xun Trung, Thanh Xun, H Ni.<br>Hotline: 03.4567.6666</p>\r\n<p>195, An Dng Vng, Phng 8, Qun 5<br>Hotline: (028)3.888.3456</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>2/ t mua qua website ca Mistore:</strong><br>Bc 1 : Click vo sn phm bn c nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Chn  Thm Vo Gi Hng   thc hin bc tip theo ( lu  bn c th chn nhiu sn phm trong cng 1 gi hng ).</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Kim tra n hng v s lng sau  chn Tin hnh t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 4 : in y  thng tin chnh xc ca qu khch v chn phng thc thanh ton mong mun, sau  kim tra li Ha n mua hng.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu mun thm sn phm khc vo n hng qu khch chn Mua thm.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu Ha n mua hng  chnh xc, qu khch chn t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 5 : Qu khch s nhn c thng bo t hng thnh cng v M n hng t h thng. Thng tin mua hng ca qu khch s c h thng gi qua email ng k, hy lu li m s n hng  tin cho vic theo di n hng ca qu khch.</p>\r\n<p>Chng ti s lin lc vi Qu khch  xc nhn n hng v tin hnh giao hng.</p>\r\n<p>( n hng cha bao gm ph vn chuyn, ph vn chuyn s c bo c th khi nhn vin gi in cht n trc khi giao. n hng ca qu khch s t ng hy nu thng tin t hng khng y  hoc khng r rng m khng cn bo trc. Nu qu khch c nhu cu gi hng ti ca hng vui lng thanh ton trc. )</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>3/ t hng qua in thoi:</strong><br>Bc 1 : in thoi n s in Thoi t Hng ti Hotline:</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Cung cp y  thng tin sn phm , mu sc, chng loi , s lng sn phm m qu khch mong mun.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Cung cp y  thng tin nhn hng ca qu khch mt cch chnh xc nht  Mistore c th giao hng cho qu khch nhanh nht.</p>\r\n<p>Thng tin thanh ton chuyn khon<br>STK: 0461000266789  Vietcombank</p>\r\n<p>Ch TK: Nguyn L Phng</p>\r\n<p>Email: mistore.com.vn@gmail.com</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong> thun tin hn cho qu trnh mua hng, hin ti Mistore.com.vn h tr cc hnh thc thanh ton sau:</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton ti ca hng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tin mt (VND)</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton th ATM</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton bng th tn dng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tr gp. Tm hiu thm ti y</strong><br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton khi nhn hng</strong><br>Hng ho s c vn chuyn qua dch v Chuyn pht nhanh / Shipper n tn nh, thanh ton sau  nhn hng.</p>\r\n<p>(*) Lu : thanh ton khi nhn hng (Cash On Delivery) ch p dng vi n hng c gi tr di 2 triu ng, cha bao gm ph vn chuyn v bo him (nu c), vi n hng ln hn vui lng lin h  c hng dn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton online</strong><br>Chuyn khon qua ti khon cng ty. Xem ti y<br>Thanh ton bng th ATM<br>Thanh ton bng th tn dng<br>Thanh ton tr gp bng th tn dng<br>Th tn dng (Credit Card) l mt loi th ngn hng c tnh nng thanh ton m khng cn tin c sn trong th. Ni cch khc l bn s mn tin ca ngn hng  thanh ton v ti cui k s cn tr li y  cho ngn hng. S tin trong th tn dng c ngn hng cp gi l hn mc th tn dng.<br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Chnh sch bo hnh\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"M5LAWEG\" data-pb-style=\"