i/ Series number/ iMei thit b. Theo quy nh bo hnh chnh hng, Qu khch vui lng gi li v/hp thit b  c bo hnh.<br>Thi gian tip nhn &amp; tr bo hnh t: 12h00  21h00 (Tr th 7, ch nht v ngy l)<br><strong>I. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;CHNH SCH BO HNH:</strong><br>Lu : chnh sch bo hnh / i mi ny p dng vi sn phm nhp khu, cc sn phm c phn phi chnh hng bi DGW s c bo hnh / i mi theo chnh sch / quyt nh ca n v tip nhn bo hnh DGW (Dcare)<br>1. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh (tu theo nhm sn phm) v i mi theo chnh sch bo hnh chnh hng ca Xiaomi.</p>\r\n<p>2. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh hoc i mi trong trng hp pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut (tr ngoi hnh).</p>\r\n<p>3. &nbsp; &nbsp;Quy nh v thi gian tip nhn - x l (tnh t thi im tip nhn bo hnh):</p>\r\n<p>Thi gian kim tra: Ti a 48 gi lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Thi gian x l bo hnh: &nbsp;15 - 30 ngy lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Nu c pht sinh vn  khc, CSKH s lin h  thng bo trc t nht 24 gi.</p>\r\n<p>4. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c thay th linh kin hoc sa cha min ph khi b h hng do li k thut t nh sn xut sau thi gian quy nh i mi.</p>\r\n<p>6. &nbsp; &nbsp; Mi loi sn phm c chnh sch bo hnh ring, Qu khch vui lng xem k chnh sch bo hnh theo tng sn phm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>II. &nbsp; &nbsp; IU KIN BO HNH:</strong><br>Sn phm cn trong thi hn bo hnh.<br>Sn phm phi cn nguyn vn, khng sa cha bi cc ni khc ngoi h thng ca hng hoc Mi Store, MiCare v Dcare.<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm phi trng hp vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t v bao b sn phm.<br>Sn phm phi cn hp nguyn vn, khng b rch, khng chp ni, khng b ty xa.<br>III. &nbsp;IU KIN I MI:<br>Sn phm c hng chnh sch 1 i 1 nu pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut.<br>Sn phm i mi l sn phm ngang gi, cng chng loi, cng thng s k thut, cng mu sc. (Trng hp Store khng cn sn phm c cng mu vi sn phm c i mi, chng ti s thay th bng sn phm khc tng ng vi gi tr sn phm ). Nu sn phm khng c li t nh sn xut th s tnh khu tr 30% gi tr sn phm.<br>Thi gian bo hnh v i mi:<br>in thoi, Laptop: Bo hnh 12 Thng phn cng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin | Pin bo hnh 06 thng<br>Xe in, Xe cn bng: Bo hnh 06 Thng phn cng | Pin bo hnh 03 thng<br>Pin d phng: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Tai nghe: Bo hnh 03 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Loa bluetooth: Bo hnh 01 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Camera: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>n trn, n bn: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Sn phm thi trang, ph kin khc: Khng bo hnh, khng i mi.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>IV. &nbsp;TRNG HP T CHI BO HNH (H tr sa cha):</strong><br>Sn phm  ht hn bo hnh.<br>Cc vn  lin quan n ti khon, bo mt (Mt khu, MiCloud)<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm khng trng vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t (hoc ho n mua hng).<br>Sn phm b h hng do thin tai, l lt, st nh, ha hon hay do vn chuyn lm nt, mp, b, try xc, vo nc.<br>Sn phm h hng do s dng khng ng theo hng dn, do ngun in khng ng, khng n nh, do t  cp nht phn mm (up rom) khng ng k thut, Root my dn n h hng thit b.<br>Mn hnh xut hin di 3 im cht, mn hnh b sc, m, bi bn, phn quang hoc cht hn trong qu trnh s dng do tc dng lc, va p, vo nc.<br>Sn phm b r st,  bn do n mn hay do cht lng  vo.<br>Sn phm c du hiu  tho lp, sa cha thay th linh kin  nhng ni khc ngoi h thng Mistore, Micare, Dcare<br>Cc tng phm ph kin km theo sn phm khng phi l sn phm khng c bo hnh. V d: tng phm khuyn mi, mt s ph kin km theo my nh Pin, sc, cable, tai nghe...(nu c)<br>Cc trng hp yu cu v v sinh sn phm, bo tr sn phm khng nm trong hn mc bo hnh.<br>i vi pin tch hp, khng bo hnh cc trng hp ph, chm chy linh kin v cc trng hp chai, hng pin do s dng.<br>i vi loa, tai nghe v cc sn phm c loa, khng bo hnh li r, h.<br>V. Quy nh khc:<br>i vi nhng sn phm nh my tnh, in thoi,  cng lu tr, th nh. Chng ti hon ton khng chu trch nhim v vic mt d liu c nhn ca Qu khch nh: ti liu, danh b, tin nhn  khi thc hin cc yu cu Up Rom, sa cha.<br>Nu qu khch c nhu cu sao lu, backup d liu. Vui lng bo trc  nhn vin k thut thc hin.<br>VI. Chnh sch tr hng<br>Mi Store khng c chnh sch tr hng Qu khch vui lng tm hiu tnh nng hng ha hoc kim tra k sn phm.<br>Mt s trng hp c bit:<br>Qu khch c quyn tr hoc i mi trong trng hp sn phm pht sinh li do nh sn xut khng khc phc c hoc khc phc nhiu ln khng c.<br><strong>GIM C CNG TY</strong></p>\r\n<p> K</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(p dng t 01/01/2023)</p></div></div></div></div>'),('131',76,0,'46','<p> Phn phi chnh hng Xiaomi (Vit Nam)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bo hnh chnh hng 12 thng</strong>,i mi trong 7 ngy u tin.</p>\r\n<p> Mi 100% Fullbox nguyn seal</p>'),('132',85,0,'46','ng h thng minh Kieslect Lady Watch Lora 2');
INSERT INTO `catalog_product_entity_text` VALUES ('133',75,0,'47','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=ASE6PSJ],#html-body [data-pb-style=AVIE267],#html-body [data-pb-style=L43DS27]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=I8VQKYX]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=KDLO2L3]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=L6K6X5M],#html-body [data-pb-style=OIG0PBW],#html-body [data-pb-style=TUEI86K]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"I8VQKYX\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"L43DS27\"><a href=\"#CR4TKM7\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"ASE6PSJ\"><a href=\"#HLS1Q65\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"AVIE267\"><a href=\"#E42903O\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"KDLO2L3\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"CR4TKM7\" data-pb-style=\"OIG0PBW\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>ng h thng minh Kieslect Lora 2 l sn phm ng h thng minh n t thng hiu Kieslect s hu mt thit k thi trang v cng bt mt. Bn cnh  th ng h thng minh Kieslect ny cn c trang b nhiu tnh nng theo di sc khe thng minh cng vin pin s dng bn b.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thit k cao cp vi khung hp kim nhm</strong><br>Kieslect Lora 2 c hon thin vi phn khung t hp kim nhm v cng cao cp, bn mu. Khung kim loi mang li v thi trang cao cng vi  l bn b trong qu trnh s dng. ng h vi mn hnh AMOLED kch thc 1.3 inch mang li khng gian hin th rng cng kh nng hin th r nt.</p>\r\n<p><strong>H tr nhiu tnh nng qun l sc khe thng minh</strong><br>Kieslect Lora 2 c trang b kh nng theo di nng  oxy trong mu ngi dng lin tc trong 24 gi. Bn cnh  l cc ch s nhp tim, ch s gic ng cng c thit b ghi li v a ra nh gi tng qua cho ngi dng. Vi ngi dng na, Lora 2 cn h tr ghi li chu l kinh nguyt cng nh d on chu k tng lai.</p>\r\n<p>Bn cnh , ng h cng h tr theo di ch  tp luyn ca ngi dng vi hn 100 mn th thao khc nhau.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Trng lng gn nh</strong><br>&nbsp;Trng lng ng h l mt yu t quan trng gip ngi dng cm nhn c s thoi mi khi eo trong thi gian di. ng h thng minh Kieslect Lora 2 c trng lng 42.9gr, chic ng h ny va  nh  bn cm thy thoi mi m khng gy cm gic nng n hay g b.</p>\r\n<p>Thit k mt trn lun l s la chn tinh t v truyn thng trong ngnh thit k ng h. Vi mt trn, to ra v ngoi thanh lch, d dng phi  v ph hp vi nhiu phong cch khc nhau, t th thao n thanh lch.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Chng nc chun IP68</strong><br>ng h thng minh Kieslect Lora 2 cng c trang b tnh nng chng nc IP68, gip bo v thit b khi nc v bi bn, cho php ngi dng s dng trong mi trng m v nhiu hot ng ngoi tri.</p>\r\n<p>Sn phm s khin ngi dng hi lng bi mu sc d dng la chn, dy eo va vn vi tay ca ngi dng nh s iu chnh nhanh chng. Khi s dng lu, bn c th thay th dy eo qua vi bc n gin l  tip tc s dng ngay.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Kt ni Bluetooth nhanh chng</strong><br>Cho d bn ang tp th dc, li xe hay nu nng, bn c th thc hin cuc gi r rng v mt m vi Lora 2 bt c lc no v  bt c u. Nh kt ni BT5.2 n nh, ng h thng minh Kieslect Lora 2 cho php bn nhn hay t chi v thc hin cuc gi mt cch d dng.</p>\r\n<p>Sn phm c thit k tinh t, hin i, mu sc ph hp vi nhiu ngi dng khc nhau, Lora 2 thch hp cho c vic s dng trong nh hay i tp gym. T , to phong cch sng thi thng hng ngy ca ngi dng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thao tc nghe nhc n gin</strong><br>Hy thng thc nhng bi ht thng qua ng h thng minh Kieslect Lora 2, ng h thng minh ny s hu b loa pht nhc n tng, cho php bn pht nhc qua kt ni Bluetooth qua vi chm n gin. Bn c th play, pause nhc v iu chnh m lng trc tip ngay trn c tay ca mnh.</p>\r\n<p>Khng ch dng li  , sn phm trang b tr l ging ni vi tr tu nhn to cho php ngi dng tng tc thng qua ging ni mt cch tin li, h tr cc tr l o nh Siri, Google Assistant v nhiu tr l o khc.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dung lng pin ln</strong><br>ng h thng minh Kieslect Lora 2 c thi lng pin n tng vi 5 ngy s dng lin tc trong ch  thng minh v ln n 3 ngy nu thng xuyn. Thi gian sc nhanh chng, ch khong 2 gi  y pin.</p>\r\n<p>Bn cnh , cng sc nam chm cng l mt tnh nng tin li, gip d dng sc ng h mt cch nhanh chng v n nh. Vi nhng thng s n tng nh vy, ngi dng c th yn tm s dng ng h thng minh Kieslect Lora 2 trong thi gian di m khng cn lo lng v vic sc pin qu thng xuyn</p>\r\n<p>y l mt sn phm thch hp cho nhng ngi c li sng bn rn, mun duy tr s kt ni v qun l sc khe hiu qu m khng cn phi lo lng v thi gian sc pin nhiu ln trong ngy nh mt s sn phm thng thng hin nay.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tnh nng ni tri</strong><br>ng h cng tch hp cc tr chi gii tr  phc v ngi dng th gin v gii tr trong thi gian rnh. Chc nng \"Tm in thoi/ng h ca ti\" gip ngi dng d dng tm thit b ca mnh khi b mt hoc  li  ni khc.</p>\r\n<p>Mc d c gi thnh kh r nhng Lora 2 vn c trang b loa v micro, cho php ngi dng nghe v nhn cuc gi trc tip trn ng h m khng cn phi s dng in thoi. Tnh nng ng b danh b v nht k cuc gi cng l im mnh ca Lora 2, gip ngi dng lun nm bt mi thng tin quan trng t in thoi thng qua ng dng i km.</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"HLS1Q65\" data-pb-style=\"L6K6X5M\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hng dn mua hng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th mua hng theo mt 