i/ Series number/ iMei thit b. Theo quy nh bo hnh chnh hng, Qu khch vui lng gi li v/hp thit b  c bo hnh.<br>Thi gian tip nhn &amp; tr bo hnh t: 12h00  21h00 (Tr th 7, ch nht v ngy l)<br><strong>I. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;CHNH SCH BO HNH:</strong><br>Lu : chnh sch bo hnh / i mi ny p dng vi sn phm nhp khu, cc sn phm c phn phi chnh hng bi DGW s c bo hnh / i mi theo chnh sch / quyt nh ca n v tip nhn bo hnh DGW (Dcare)<br>1. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh (tu theo nhm sn phm) v i mi theo chnh sch bo hnh chnh hng ca Xiaomi.</p>\r\n<p>2. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh hoc i mi trong trng hp pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut (tr ngoi hnh).</p>\r\n<p>3. &nbsp; &nbsp;Quy nh v thi gian tip nhn - x l (tnh t thi im tip nhn bo hnh):</p>\r\n<p>Thi gian kim tra: Ti a 48 gi lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Thi gian x l bo hnh: &nbsp;15 - 30 ngy lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Nu c pht sinh vn  khc, CSKH s lin h  thng bo trc t nht 24 gi.</p>\r\n<p>4. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c thay th linh kin hoc sa cha min ph khi b h hng do li k thut t nh sn xut sau thi gian quy nh i mi.</p>\r\n<p>6. &nbsp; &nbsp; Mi loi sn phm c chnh sch bo hnh ring, Qu khch vui lng xem k chnh sch bo hnh theo tng sn phm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>II. &nbsp; &nbsp; IU KIN BO HNH:</strong><br>Sn phm cn trong thi hn bo hnh.<br>Sn phm phi cn nguyn vn, khng sa cha bi cc ni khc ngoi h thng ca hng hoc Mi Store, MiCare v Dcare.<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm phi trng hp vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t v bao b sn phm.<br>Sn phm phi cn hp nguyn vn, khng b rch, khng chp ni, khng b ty xa.<br>III. &nbsp;IU KIN I MI:<br>Sn phm c hng chnh sch 1 i 1 nu pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut.<br>Sn phm i mi l sn phm ngang gi, cng chng loi, cng thng s k thut, cng mu sc. (Trng hp Store khng cn sn phm c cng mu vi sn phm c i mi, chng ti s thay th bng sn phm khc tng ng vi gi tr sn phm ). Nu sn phm khng c li t nh sn xut th s tnh khu tr 30% gi tr sn phm.<br>Thi gian bo hnh v i mi:<br>in thoi, Laptop: Bo hnh 12 Thng phn cng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin | Pin bo hnh 06 thng<br>Xe in, Xe cn bng: Bo hnh 06 Thng phn cng | Pin bo hnh 03 thng<br>Pin d phng: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Tai nghe: Bo hnh 03 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Loa bluetooth: Bo hnh 01 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Camera: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>n trn, n bn: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Sn phm thi trang, ph kin khc: Khng bo hnh, khng i mi.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>IV. &nbsp;TRNG HP T CHI BO HNH (H tr sa cha):</strong><br>Sn phm  ht hn bo hnh.<br>Cc vn  lin quan n ti khon, bo mt (Mt khu, MiCloud)<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm khng trng vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t (hoc ho n mua hng).<br>Sn phm b h hng do thin tai, l lt, st nh, ha hon hay do vn chuyn lm nt, mp, b, try xc, vo nc.<br>Sn phm h hng do s dng khng ng theo hng dn, do ngun in khng ng, khng n nh, do t  cp nht phn mm (up rom) khng ng k thut, Root my dn n h hng thit b.<br>Mn hnh xut hin di 3 im cht, mn hnh b sc, m, bi bn, phn quang hoc cht hn trong qu trnh s dng do tc dng lc, va p, vo nc.<br>Sn phm b r st,  bn do n mn hay do cht lng  vo.<br>Sn phm c du hiu  tho lp, sa cha thay th linh kin  nhng ni khc ngoi h thng Mistore, Micare, Dcare<br>Cc tng phm ph kin km theo sn phm khng phi l sn phm khng c bo hnh. V d: tng phm khuyn mi, mt s ph kin km theo my nh Pin, sc, cable, tai nghe...(nu c)<br>Cc trng hp yu cu v v sinh sn phm, bo tr sn phm khng nm trong hn mc bo hnh.<br>i vi pin tch hp, khng bo hnh cc trng hp ph, chm chy linh kin v cc trng hp chai, hng pin do s dng.<br>i vi loa, tai nghe v cc sn phm c loa, khng bo hnh li r, h.<br>V. Quy nh khc:<br>i vi nhng sn phm nh my tnh, in thoi,  cng lu tr, th nh. Chng ti hon ton khng chu trch nhim v vic mt d liu c nhn ca Qu khch nh: ti liu, danh b, tin nhn  khi thc hin cc yu cu Up Rom, sa cha.<br>Nu qu khch c nhu cu sao lu, backup d liu. Vui lng bo trc  nhn vin k thut thc hin.<br>VI. Chnh sch tr hng<br>Mi Store khng c chnh sch tr hng Qu khch vui lng tm hiu tnh nng hng ha hoc kim tra k sn phm.<br>Mt s trng hp c bit:<br>Qu khch c quyn tr hoc i mi trong trng hp sn phm pht sinh li do nh sn xut khng khc phc c hoc khc phc nhiu ln khng c.<br><strong>GIM C CNG TY</strong></p>\r\n<p> K</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(p dng t 01/01/2023)</p></div></div></div></div>'),('137',76,0,'48','<p> Phn phi chnh hng Xiaomi (Vit Nam)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bo hnh chnh hng 12 thng</strong>,i mi trong 7 ngy u tin.</p>\r\n<p> Mi 100% Fullbox nguyn seal</p>'),('138',85,0,'48','ng h thng minh Kieslect Lady Watch Lora 2');
INSERT INTO `catalog_product_entity_text` VALUES ('139',75,0,'49','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=LK0MM97],#html-body [data-pb-style=LNDCXBB],#html-body [data-pb-style=WVKWLFA]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=CLIGGQ7]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=OVG4PWX]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=BDTJKWD],#html-body [data-pb-style=OEMS5EY],#html-body [data-pb-style=OHFFTAV]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"CLIGGQ7\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"LK0MM97\"><a href=\"#VB1A4PT\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"WVKWLFA\"><a href=\"#DGUL8SC\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"LNDCXBB\"><a href=\"#K6AB7HK\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"OVG4PWX\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"VB1A4PT\" data-pb-style=\"OEMS5EY\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Flagship Xiaomi 13 ra mt vi mc ch ph o doanh s cui nm ch vi 3 nng cp ch mng so vi th h tin nhim. u tin l nng cp v chip, sau  l nng cp tc  c ghi b nh trong ln nhanh gp i, th 3 l thit k quyt nh ln khin ngi dng khng ngi \"xung tin\"  \"rc\" Xiaomi 13 v i ca mnh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thit k vung vc, ti gin, sang trng</strong><br>Thy c cc mu in thoi tm trung co thit k vung vc ca mnh c xu hng bn chy hn, Xiaomi  mang ln mu in thoi cao cp kiu dnh kinh in ny. Ton b chic in thoi gn nh c to nn t nhng mt phng cho dng v vung vc thanh thot, ti gin nhng v cng sang trng gip ngi s hu chic my c nng ln mt tm cao mi.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mn hnh siu p,  sng cc cao</strong><br>Khc vi cc mu my tin nhim, chic in thoi Xiaomi cao cp mi c mn hnh 6.36 inch ln hn, vi tm nn OLED kt hp vi cc cng ngh h tr hin th cao cp gip kh nng ti to hnh nh v cng trung thc v sng ng. Bn ngoi c bo v bng knh cng lc Gorilla Glass Victus chc chn. c bit, vi  sng ti a 1900nits khin bn s sng thoi mi ngoi tri.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Chip siu mnh tr thnh qui vt hiu nng</strong><br>Nh   cp  phn trn, Xiaomi trang b cho chic smartphone cao cp mi ca mnh b x l Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 siu mnh, mi nht ca Qualcomm. Chip c sn xut trn tin trnh 4nm vi cng ngh tin tin nn cho kh nng ti u v tit kim in tt hn th h trc.</p>\r\n<p><strong>H thng camera chp nh tuyt nh</strong><br>Vi cm bin chnh 50MP OIS cng mt ng knh tele 10MP v cm bin gc siu rng 12MP c sp xp hp l trong m-un hnh vung to nn cm camera sau c o. Cho kh nng quay phim 8K siu nt v chp nh nh cao. Pha trc l cm bin 32MP cho php chp nh selfie v gi in video.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Pin ln cng sc siu nhanh n tng</strong><br>Vi kch thc nh gn nhng Xiaomi Mi 13 c dung lng pin 4500mAh, y l mt k tch bi nhiu chic my c mn hnh hn hn m vin pin cn nh hn mu in thoi ny. Bn ch mt khong 38ph  sc u vin pin k trn vi c sc 67W. L thit b cao cp Xiaomi 13 cng c trang sc khng dy 50W v sc ngc khng dy 10W v cng tin li.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thng s k thut</strong><br>Mn hnh : AMOLED 6.36 + 120Hz<br>H iu hnh : MIUI 14<br>Chipset : Snapdragon 8 GEN 2<br>GPU: Adreno 740<br>Camera trc : 32 MP, f/2.0, 20mm (gc rng) | Quay phim: 1080p@30fps<br>Camera sau : 50 MP, f/1.8, 23mm (gc rng), PDAF, OIS<br>10 MP, f/2.0 75mm (tele), 1/3.94\", 1.0m, PDAF, OIS, 3.2x optical zoom<br>12 MP, f/2.2, 15mm, 120 (gc siu rng)<br>Quay phim: 8K@24fps (HDR), 4K@24/30/60fps (HDR10+), 1080p@30/120/240/960fps, 1080p@1920fps, gyro-EIS<br>Pin : 4500mAh<br>Sc nhanh: C dy 67W, khng dy 50W, sc ngc 10W<br>Khng nc: IP68<br>Cng kt ni: Type-C</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"DGUL8SC\" data-pb-style=\"OHFFTAV\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hng dn mua hng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th mua hng theo mt trong cc cch sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong>1/ Mua hng trc tip:</strong><br>Qu khch c th n trc tip tham quan, tri nghim v mua sm cc sn phm Xiaomi ti tt c cc a ch sau ca MISTORE:</p>\r\n<p>364 Nguyn Tri, Thanh Xun Trung, Thanh Xun, H Ni.<br>Hotline: 03.4567.6666</p>\r\n<p>195, An Dng Vng, Phng 8, Qun 5<br>Hotline: (028)3.888.3456</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>2/ t mua qua website ca Mistore:</strong><br>Bc 1 : Click vo sn phm bn c nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Chn  Thm Vo Gi Hng   thc hin bc tip theo ( lu  bn c th chn nhiu sn phm trong cng 1 gi hng ).</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Kim tra n hng v s lng sau  chn Tin hnh t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 4 : in y  thng tin chnh xc ca qu khch v chn phng thc thanh ton mong mun, sau  kim tra li Ha n mua hng.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu mun thm sn phm khc vo n hng qu khch chn Mua thm.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu Ha n mua hng  chnh xc, qu khch chn t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 5 : Qu khch s nhn c thng bo t hng thnh cng v M n hng t h thng. Thng tin mua hng ca qu khch s c h thng gi qua email ng k, hy lu li m s n hng  tin cho vic theo di n hng ca qu khch.</p>\r\n<p>Chng ti s lin lc vi Qu khch  xc nhn n hng v tin hnh giao hng.</p>\r\n<p>( n hng cha bao gm ph vn chuyn, ph vn chuyn s c bo c th khi nhn vin gi in cht n trc khi giao. n hng ca qu khch s t ng hy nu thng tin t hng khng y  hoc khng r rng m khng cn bo trc. Nu qu khch c nhu cu gi hng ti ca hng vui lng thanh ton trc. )</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>3/ t hng qua in thoi:</strong><br>Bc 1