21h00 (Tr th 7, ch nht v ngy l)<br><strong>I. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;CHNH SCH BO HNH:</strong><br>Lu : chnh sch bo hnh / i mi ny p dng vi sn phm nhp khu, cc sn phm c phn phi chnh hng bi DGW s c bo hnh / i mi theo chnh sch / quyt nh ca n v tip nhn bo hnh DGW (Dcare)<br>1. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh (tu theo nhm sn phm) v i mi theo chnh sch bo hnh chnh hng ca Xiaomi.</p>\r\n<p>2. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh hoc i mi trong trng hp pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut (tr ngoi hnh).</p>\r\n<p>3. &nbsp; &nbsp;Quy nh v thi gian tip nhn - x l (tnh t thi im tip nhn bo hnh):</p>\r\n<p>Thi gian kim tra: Ti a 48 gi lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Thi gian x l bo hnh: &nbsp;15 - 30 ngy lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Nu c pht sinh vn  khc, CSKH s lin h  thng bo trc t nht 24 gi.</p>\r\n<p>4. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c thay th linh kin hoc sa cha min ph khi b h hng do li k thut t nh sn xut sau thi gian quy nh i mi.</p>\r\n<p>6. &nbsp; &nbsp; Mi loi sn phm c chnh sch bo hnh ring, Qu khch vui lng xem k chnh sch bo hnh theo tng sn phm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>II. &nbsp; &nbsp; IU KIN BO HNH:</strong><br>Sn phm cn trong thi hn bo hnh.<br>Sn phm phi cn nguyn vn, khng sa cha bi cc ni khc ngoi h thng ca hng hoc Mi Store, MiCare v Dcare.<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm phi trng hp vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t v bao b sn phm.<br>Sn phm phi cn hp nguyn vn, khng b rch, khng chp ni, khng b ty xa.<br>III. &nbsp;IU KIN I MI:<br>Sn phm c hng chnh sch 1 i 1 nu pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut.<br>Sn phm i mi l sn phm ngang gi, cng chng loi, cng thng s k thut, cng mu sc. (Trng hp Store khng cn sn phm c cng mu vi sn phm c i mi, chng ti s thay th bng sn phm khc tng ng vi gi tr sn phm ). Nu sn phm khng c li t nh sn xut th s tnh khu tr 30% gi tr sn phm.<br>Thi gian bo hnh v i mi:<br>in thoi, Laptop: Bo hnh 12 Thng phn cng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin | Pin bo hnh 06 thng<br>Xe in, Xe cn bng: Bo hnh 06 Thng phn cng | Pin bo hnh 03 thng<br>Pin d phng: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Tai nghe: Bo hnh 03 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Loa bluetooth: Bo hnh 01 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Camera: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>n trn, n bn: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Sn phm thi trang, ph kin khc: Khng bo hnh, khng i mi.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>IV. &nbsp;TRNG HP T CHI BO HNH (H tr sa cha):</strong><br>Sn phm  ht hn bo hnh.<br>Cc vn  lin quan n ti khon, bo mt (Mt khu, MiCloud)<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm khng trng vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t (hoc ho n mua hng).<br>Sn phm b h hng do thin tai, l lt, st nh, ha hon hay do vn chuyn lm nt, mp, b, try xc, vo nc.<br>Sn phm h hng do s dng khng ng theo hng dn, do ngun in khng ng, khng n nh, do t  cp nht phn mm (up rom) khng ng k thut, Root my dn n h hng thit b.<br>Mn hnh xut hin di 3 im cht, mn hnh b sc, m, bi bn, phn quang hoc cht hn trong qu trnh s dng do tc dng lc, va p, vo nc.<br>Sn phm b r st,  bn do n mn hay do cht lng  vo.<br>Sn phm c du hiu  tho lp, sa cha thay th linh kin  nhng ni khc ngoi h thng Mistore, Micare, Dcare<br>Cc tng phm ph kin km theo sn phm khng phi l sn phm khng c bo hnh. V d: tng phm khuyn mi, mt s ph kin km theo my nh Pin, sc, cable, tai nghe...(nu c)<br>Cc trng hp yu cu v v sinh sn phm, bo tr sn phm khng nm trong hn mc bo hnh.<br>i vi pin tch hp, khng bo hnh cc trng hp ph, chm chy linh kin v cc trng hp chai, hng pin do s dng.<br>i vi loa, tai nghe v cc sn phm c loa, khng bo hnh li r, h.<br>V. Quy nh khc:<br>i vi nhng sn phm nh my tnh, in thoi,  cng lu tr, th nh. Chng ti hon ton khng chu trch nhim v vic mt d liu c nhn ca Qu khch nh: ti liu, danh b, tin nhn  khi thc hin cc yu cu Up Rom, sa cha.<br>Nu qu khch c nhu cu sao lu, backup d liu. Vui lng bo trc  nhn vin k thut thc hin.<br>VI. Chnh sch tr hng<br>Mi Store khng c chnh sch tr hng Qu khch vui lng tm hiu tnh nng hng ha hoc kim tra k sn phm.<br>Mt s trng hp c bit:<br>Qu khch c quyn tr hoc i mi trong trng hp sn phm pht sinh li do nh sn xut khng khc phc c hoc khc phc nhiu ln khng c.<br><strong>GIM C CNG TY</strong></p>\r\n<p> K</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(p dng t 01/01/2023)</p></div></div></div></div>'),('146',76,0,'51','<p><strong></strong>Nhp khu chnh hng Xiaomi (Bc Kinh)</p>\r\n<p><strong> Bo hnh chnh hng 12 thng, i mi trong 7 ngy u tin.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong></strong>H tr, ci t phn mm<strong>min ph trn i</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Gim thm 30%</strong>ph sa cha dch v (sau bo hnh)</p>\r\n<p><strong></strong>Mi 100% Fullbox nguyn seal</p>'),('147',85,0,'51','in thoi Xiaomi 13 Ultra'),('148',75,0,'52','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=OV5WJAY],#html-body [data-pb-style=TS60IKJ],#html-body [data-pb-style=VOJ0VHU]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=T5YEBQY]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=VSA2BDB]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=GVCPHEW],#html-body [data-pb-style=RS8QKWW],#html-body [data-pb-style=USW7XNA]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"T5YEBQY\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"TS60IKJ\"><a href=\"#TRUXQT5\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"VOJ0VHU\"><a href=\"#SFSG4K2\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"OV5WJAY\"><a href=\"#ITNS44R\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"VSA2BDB\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"TRUXQT5\" data-pb-style=\"RS8QKWW\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Xiaomi 13 Ultra chnh thc xut chinh vi x mnh ni tip s thnh cng ca 12S Ultra nhm cnh tranh vi sng phng vi nhng flagship u bng ca cc hng ln khc. Thit b s vn s hu h thng camera khng nht th gii, cm bin ln 1\", mn hnh OLED 2K cng ngh LTPO3, thit k hm h sang trng, sc siu nhanh. c bit vi mc gi cnh tranh Xiaomi 13 Ultra ha hn s to cn st ln c nhiu Youtuber, TikToker, ... sn tm v s hu.</p>\r\n<p>Khng ch c trang b h thng camera siu nh IMX989 ca Sony, cm bin 1\" siu ln m 13 Ultra cn c trang b nhiu phn cng v tnh nng nh cao nht ti thi im ra mt, nh chip Snapdragon 8 Gen 2, mn hnh OLED 2K c tn s qut tng thch, b nh trong UFS 4.0 siu nhanh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thit k sang trng, mn hnh LTPO OLED 2k</strong><br>Mn hnh OLED 2K, h tr 1 t mu, tn s qut 120Hz siu mt m. Cng ngh hin th Dolby Vision v HDR10+ mang n cht lng hi th tuyt ho. Cc mu my ny cng u c mn hnh cong c l trn vin 6,73 inch, QHD+ siu nt v u c bo v bng knh cng lc Gorilla Glass Victus chc chn, chng try v chu lc tt.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Nng cp chip v b nh</strong><br>Tt nhin, 13 Ultra s c hiu nng mnh m hn bn tin nhim, bi my c tch hp b x l cao cp nht ca Qualcomm  l Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 trong khi Xiaomi 12S Ultra l Snapdragon 8+ Gen 1 c hn.</p>\r\n<p>RAM LPDDR5X c dung lng 12GB, 16GB ca Xiaomi 13 bn Ultra cho php x l nhanh hn v kh nng lu tr thng tin cao hn so vi RAM LPDDR5 dung lng 8-12GB ca bn tin nhim, ng thi gip nng cao tri nghim vi cc ng dng, game hoc cc tc v i hi s phc tp cao trn in thoi.</p>\r\n<p>B nh trong UFS 4.0 ca 13 Ultra c tc  truy xut v ghi d liu nhanh hn UFS 3.1 ca Xiaomi 12S Ultra nh vo vic s dng cng ngh mi nht.</p>\r\n<p>Dung lng lu tr 256GB v 512GB ca c hai sn phm u p ng nhu cu lu tr ti liu, hnh nh v video ca ngi dng. Ngoi ra, 13 Ultra cn c thm bn 1TB gip ngi dng thoi mi lu tr hn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>t ph v camera</strong><br>Hai smartphone cao cp nht hin nay c thit k camera ng cp vi nhiu ng knh, cm bin 1 inck cc ln v cc tnh nng cao cp. H thng 5 camera sau trn 13 Ultra bao gm cm bin chnh 50.3MP (rng), 50MP (tim vng tele), 50MP (tele), 50MP (siu rng) v TOF 3D ( su). Trong khi , Xiaomi 12S Ultra s hu 4 ng knh vi cm bin chnh 50.3MP (rng), 48MP (tim vng tele), 48MP (siu rng) v TOF 3D ( su).</p>\r\n<p>V s lng camera, 13 Ultra c nhiu hn vi 5 ng knh, h tr cho vic chp nh t nhng khong cch khc nhau. Trong khi , Xiaomi 12S Ultra ch c 4 ng knh, tuy nhin  phn gii ca camera tim vng tele v gc siu rng ca 12S Ultra thp hn vi 48MP. C hai my u s hu cm bin chnh vi  phn gii 50.3MP, gip chp nh sc nt v chi tit.</p>\r\n<p>Tc  chp nh cng l mt yu t quan trng, 13 Ultra c tc  ly nt cc nhanh, h tr chp nh chuyn nghip. Xiaomi 12S Ultra cng c kh nng chp nh tt v h tr autofocus nh bn k nhim ca n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dung lng pin ln, h tr sc nhanh 90W</strong><br>Xiaomi Mi 13 Ultra c trang b pin 5000mAh, chip v mn hnh tit kim pin gip ci thin thi lng s dng pin so vi Xiaomi 12S Ultra vi pin 4860mAh. Do , thi gian s dng pin ca 13 Ultra s lu hn rt nhiu so vi Xiaomi 12S Ultra.</p>\r\n<p>Sc nhanh 90W trn Mi 13 Ultra nhanh hn 33W so vi sc 67W trn Xiaomi 12S Ultra, cho php ngi dng sc thit b nhanh hn v tit kim thi gian hn. C th, vi 35 pht bn  c th sc y pin cho Xiaomi 13 Ultra, trong khi ngi dng Xiaomi 12S Ultra cn ti 41 pht  sc y vin pin dung lng thp hn.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thng s k thut</strong><br>Mn hnh : &nbsp;LTPO &nbsp;OLED 6.73 &nbsp;2K + 120Hz<br>H iu hnh : MIUI 14<br>Chipset : Snapdragon 8 GEN 2<br>GPU: Adreno GPU<br>Camera trc : 32 MP, f/2.0, 22mm (gc rng) HDR, Panorama Quay phim: 1080p@30fps<br>Camera sau : 50.3 MP, f/1.9 hoc f/4.0, 23mm (gc rng), kch thc 1\", multi-directional PDAF, Laser AF, OIS<br>50 MP, f/3.0, 120mm (knh tim vong tele), Dual-Pixel PDAF, OIS, zoom quang 5x<br>50 MP, f/1.8, 75mm (tele), Dual-Pixel PDAF, OIS, zoom quang 3.2x<br>50 