i mi lu tr hn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>t ph v camera</strong><br>Hai smartphone cao cp nht hin nay c thit k camera ng cp vi nhiu ng knh, cm bin 1 inck cc ln v cc tnh nng cao cp. H thng 5 camera sau trn 13 Ultra bao gm cm bin chnh 50.3MP (rng), 50MP (tim vng tele), 50MP (tele), 50MP (siu rng) v TOF 3D ( su). Trong khi , Xiaomi 12S Ultra s hu 4 ng knh vi cm bin chnh 50.3MP (rng), 48MP (tim vng tele), 48MP (siu rng) v TOF 3D ( su).</p>\r\n<p>V s lng camera, 13 Ultra c nhiu hn vi 5 ng knh, h tr cho vic chp nh t nhng khong cch khc nhau. Trong khi , Xiaomi 12S Ultra ch c 4 ng knh, tuy nhin  phn gii ca camera tim vng tele v gc siu rng ca 12S Ultra thp hn vi 48MP. C hai my u s hu cm bin chnh vi  phn gii 50.3MP, gip chp nh sc nt v chi tit.</p>\r\n<p>Tc  chp nh cng l mt yu t quan trng, 13 Ultra c tc  ly nt cc nhanh, h tr chp nh chuyn nghip. Xiaomi 12S Ultra cng c kh nng chp nh tt v h tr autofocus nh bn k nhim ca n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dung lng pin ln, h tr sc nhanh 90W</strong><br>Xiaomi Mi 13 Ultra c trang b pin 5000mAh, chip v mn hnh tit kim pin gip ci thin thi lng s dng pin so vi Xiaomi 12S Ultra vi pin 4860mAh. Do , thi gian s dng pin ca 13 Ultra s lu hn rt nhiu so vi Xiaomi 12S Ultra.</p>\r\n<p>Sc nhanh 90W trn Mi 13 Ultra nhanh hn 33W so vi sc 67W trn Xiaomi 12S Ultra, cho php ngi dng sc thit b nhanh hn v tit kim thi gian hn. C th, vi 35 pht bn  c th sc y pin cho Xiaomi 13 Ultra, trong khi ngi dng Xiaomi 12S Ultra cn ti 41 pht  sc y vin pin dung lng thp hn.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thng s k thut</strong><br>Mn hnh : &nbsp;LTPO &nbsp;OLED 6.73 &nbsp;2K + 120Hz<br>H iu hnh : MIUI 14<br>Chipset : Snapdragon 8 GEN 2<br>GPU: Adreno GPU<br>Camera trc : 32 MP, f/2.0, 22mm (gc rng) HDR, Panorama Quay phim: 1080p@30fps<br>Camera sau : 50.3 MP, f/1.9 hoc f/4.0, 23mm (gc rng), kch thc 1\", multi-directional PDAF, Laser AF, OIS<br>50 MP, f/3.0, 120mm (knh tim vong tele), Dual-Pixel PDAF, OIS, zoom quang 5x<br>50 MP, f/1.8, 75mm (tele), Dual-Pixel PDAF, OIS, zoom quang 3.2x<br>50 