hnh tam gic cng di n flash nm ngang. Phn mt trc ca c hai vn s dng thit k c l cha camera selfie  chnh gia.</p>\r\n<p><br><strong>Thng s, cu hnh Redmi Note 12 Pro 5G</strong><br>Mn hnh<br>6,67 inch OLED, 900 nits, 1 t mu<br> phn gii: 1080 x 2400 pixels<br>Tn s qut: 120Hz<br>Hiu nng<br>Mediatek Dimensity 1080 (6nm)<br>H iu hnh<br>MIUI 13 (da trn Android 12)<br>RAM/ROM<br>6GB / 128GB, 8GB / 128GB<br>8GB / 256GB, 12GB/256GB<br>Dung lng pin<br>5.000mAh Li-Po<br>Sc<br>Sc nhanh 67W<br>Camera<br>Camera sau: 50MP + 8MP + 2MP<br>Camera trc: 16MP<br>H tr quay video 4K 30fps<br>Thit k<br>Kch thc: 162,9 x 67 x 7,9 mm<br>Khi lng: 187 gram</p>\r\n<p><br><strong>Mn hnh</strong><br>V kh nng hin th th Redmi Note 12 Pro c trang b mn hnh OLED kch thc 6.67 inch,  phn gii 1.5K (2.400 * 1.080 pixels). Vi thng s ny, Redmi Note 12 Pro s mang n cho ngi dng tri nghim xem cc ni dung vi  chi tit cao, mu sc sng ng v khng gian tri nghim rng ri.<br>im sng gi nht trn Redmi Note 12 Pro chnh l mn hnh 1 t mu.<br><strong>Pin v sc nhanh</strong><br>Redmi Note 12 Pro c trang b vin pin 5000mAh cng kh nng sc nhanh 67W. Cng ging nh cc mu my gi r khc, Xiaomi vn s tng km c sc cho ngi dng trong hp sn phm m khng cn mua thm bn ngoi.&nbsp;<br><strong>Camera</strong><br>Redmi Note 12 Pro c camera chnh 50MP vi cm bin Sony IMX766 v OIS. Hai cm bin cn li trn c hai in thoi l cm bin siu rng 8MP v cm bin  su 2MP. Cc camera selfie pha trc c  phn gii 16MP.<br><strong>Tc  x l</strong><br>V hiu nng, my c trang b con chip Mediatek Dimensity 1080 c sn xut trn tin trnh 6nm hon ton mi. V mt l thuyt, Dimensity 1080 ch l mt phin bn nng cp nh ca Dimensity 920 5G. Tuy nhin, b vi x l mi  c nng cp  ti u v AI v phn mm cho Redmi Note 12 Pro.</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"RPT38G7\" data-pb-style=\"S7OX9N6\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hn