ch, khng chp ni, khng b ty xa.<br>III. &nbsp;IU KIN I MI:<br>Sn phm c hng chnh sch 1 i 1 nu pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut.<br>Sn phm i mi l sn phm ngang gi, cng chng loi, cng thng s k thut, cng mu sc. (Trng hp Store khng cn sn phm c cng mu vi sn phm c i mi, chng ti s thay th bng sn phm khc tng ng vi gi tr sn phm ). Nu sn phm khng c li t nh sn xut th s tnh khu tr 30% gi tr sn phm.<br>Thi gian bo hnh v i mi:<br>in thoi, Laptop: Bo hnh 12 Thng phn cng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin | Pin bo hnh 06 thng<br>Xe in, Xe cn bng: Bo hnh 06 Thng phn cng | Pin bo hnh 03 thng<br>Pin d phng: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Tai nghe: Bo hnh 03 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Loa bluetooth: Bo hnh 01 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Camera: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>n trn, n bn: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Sn phm thi trang, ph kin khc: Khng bo hnh, khng i mi.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>IV. &nbsp;TRNG HP T CHI BO HNH (H tr sa cha):</strong><br>Sn phm  ht hn bo hnh.<br>Cc vn  lin quan n ti khon, bo mt (Mt khu, MiCloud)<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm khng trng vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t (hoc ho n mua hng).<br>Sn phm b h hng do thin tai, l lt, st nh, ha hon hay do vn chuyn lm nt, mp, b, try xc, vo nc.<br>Sn phm h hng do s dng khng ng theo hng dn, do ngun in khng ng, khng n nh, do t  cp nht phn mm (up rom) khng ng k thut, Root my dn n h hng thit b.<br>Mn hnh xut hin di 3 im cht, mn hnh b sc, m, bi bn, phn quang hoc cht hn trong qu trnh s dng do tc dng lc, va p, vo nc.<br>Sn phm b r st,  bn do n mn hay do cht lng  vo.<br>Sn phm c du hiu  tho lp, sa cha thay th linh kin  nhng ni khc ngoi h thng Mistore, Micare, Dcare<br>Cc tng phm ph kin km theo sn phm khng phi l sn phm khng c bo hnh. V d: tng phm khuyn mi, mt s ph kin km theo my nh Pin, sc, cable, tai nghe...(nu c)<br>Cc trng hp yu cu v v sinh sn phm, bo tr sn phm khng nm trong hn mc bo hnh.<br>i vi pin tch hp, khng bo hnh cc trng hp ph, chm chy linh kin v cc trng hp chai, hng pin do s dng.<br>i vi loa, tai nghe v cc sn phm c loa, khng bo hnh li r, h.<br>V. Quy nh khc:<br>i vi nhng sn phm nh my tnh, in thoi,  cng lu tr, th nh. Chng ti hon ton khng chu trch nhim v vic mt d liu c nhn ca Qu khch nh: ti liu, danh b, tin nhn  khi thc hin cc yu cu Up Rom, sa cha.<br>Nu qu khch c nhu cu sao lu, backup d liu. Vui lng bo trc  nhn vin k thut thc hin.<br>VI. Chnh sch tr hng<br>Mi Store khng c chnh sch tr hng Qu khch vui lng tm hiu tnh nng hng ha hoc kim tra k sn phm.<br>Mt s trng hp c bit:<br>Qu khch c quyn tr hoc i mi trong trng hp sn phm pht sinh li do nh sn xut khng khc phc c hoc khc phc nhiu ln khng c.<br><strong>GIM C CNG TY</strong></p>\r\n<p> K</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(p dng t 01/01/2023)</p></div></div></div></div>'),('167',76,0,'58','<p><strong></strong>Nhp khu chnh hng Xiaomi (Bc Kinh)</p>\r\n<p><strong> Bo hnh chnh hng 12 thng, i mi trong 7 ngy u tin.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong></strong>H tr, ci t phn mm<strong>min ph trn i</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Gim thm 30%</strong>ph sa cha dch v (sau bo hnh)</p>\r\n<p><strong></strong>Mi 100% Fullbox nguyn seal</p>\r\n<p><strong>Gim gi khi mua km in thoi</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Tai nghe Xiaomi Capsule DDQ01WM<strong>299K</strong>ch cn<strong>149k</strong></li>\r\n</ul>'),('168',85,0,'58','in thoi Redmi Note 12 Pro 5G');
INSERT INTO `catalog_product_entity_text` VALUES ('169',75,0,'59','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=EAXUYAF],#html-body [data-pb-style=FCFD0PR],#html-body [data-pb-style=KU9KBIH]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=H7WCU4A]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=EPFPSUD]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=NKENLLN],#html-body [data-pb-style=S7OX9N6],#html-body [data-pb-style=WI3UI1H]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"H7WCU4A\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"EAXUYAF\"><a href=\"#ESCADXR\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"KU9KBIH\"><a href=\"#RPT38G7\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"FCFD0PR\"><a href=\"#NVRI9NO\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"EPFPSUD\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"ESCADXR\" data-pb-style=\"NKENLLN\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Redmi Note 12 Pro 5G c thit k vung vt thi trang, s hu mn hnh 120Hz bo v mt 1 t mu, pin dung lng ln n 5.000 mah v cng ngh sc nhanh 67w.Thit k Redmi Note 12 Pro 5G<br>Redmi Note 12 Pro c hon thin bng cht liu nha vi phn khung vung vc. Cm camera sau  c thay i vi 3 ng knh xp theo hnh tam gic cng di n flash nm ngang. Phn mt trc ca c hai vn s dng thit k c l cha camera selfie  chnh gia.</p>\r\n<p><br><strong>Thng s, cu hnh Redmi Note 12 Pro 5G</strong><br>Mn hnh<br>6,67 inch OLED, 900 nits, 1 t mu<br> phn gii: 1080 x 2400 pixels<br>Tn s qut: 120Hz<br>Hiu nng<br>Mediatek Dimensity 1080 (6nm)<br>H iu hnh<br>MIUI 13 (da trn Android 12)<br>RAM/ROM<br>6GB / 128GB, 8GB / 128GB<br>8GB / 256GB, 12GB/256GB<br>Dung lng pin<br>5.000mAh Li-Po<br>Sc<br>Sc nhanh 67W<br>Camera<br>Camera sau: 50MP + 8MP + 2MP<br>Camera trc: 16MP<br>H tr quay video 4K 30fps<br>Thit k<br>Kch thc: 162,9 x 67 x 7,9 mm<br>Khi lng: 187 gram</p>\r\n<p><br><strong>Mn hnh</strong><br>V kh nng hin th th Redmi Note 12 Pro c trang b mn hnh OLED kch thc 6.67 inch,  phn gii 1.5K (2.400 * 1.080 pixels). Vi thng s ny, Redmi Note 12 Pro s mang n cho ngi dng tri nghim xem cc ni dung vi  chi tit cao, mu sc sng ng v khng gian tri nghim rng ri.<br>im sng gi nht trn Redmi Note 12 Pro chnh l mn hnh 1 t mu.<br><strong>Pin v sc nhanh</strong><br>Redmi Note 12 Pro c trang b vin pin 5000mAh cng kh nng sc nhanh 67W. Cng ging nh cc mu my gi r khc, Xiaomi vn s tng km c sc cho ngi dng trong hp sn phm m khng cn mua thm bn ngoi.&nbsp;<br><strong>Camera</strong><br>Redmi Note 12 Pro c camera chnh 50MP vi cm bin Sony IMX766 v OIS. Hai cm bin cn li trn c hai in thoi l cm bin siu rng 8MP v cm bin  su 2MP. Cc camera selfie pha trc c  phn gii 16MP.<br><strong>Tc  x l</strong><br>V hiu nng, my c trang b con chip Mediatek Dimensity 1080 c sn xut trn tin trnh 6nm hon ton mi. V mt l thuyt, Dimensity 1080 ch l mt phin bn nng cp nh ca Dimensity 920 5G. Tuy nhin, b vi x l mi  c nng cp  ti u v AI v phn mm cho Redmi Note 12 Pro.</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"RPT38G7\" data-pb-style=\"S7OX9N6\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hn