INSERT INTO `catalog_product_entity_text` VALUES ('181',75,0,'63','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=EAXUYAF],#html-body [data-pb-style=FCFD0PR],#html-body [data-pb-style=KU9KBIH]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=H7WCU4A]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=EPFPSUD]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=NKENLLN],#html-body [data-pb-style=S7OX9N6],#html-body [data-pb-style=WI3UI1H]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"H7WCU4A\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"EAXUYAF\"><a href=\"#ESCADXR\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"KU9KBIH\"><a href=\"#RPT38G7\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"FCFD0PR\"><a href=\"#NVRI9NO\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"EPFPSUD\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"ESCADXR\" data-pb-style=\"NKENLLN\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Redmi Note 12 Pro 5G c thit k vung vt thi trang, s hu mn hnh 120Hz bo v mt 1 t mu, pin dung lng ln n 5.000 mah v cng ngh sc nhanh 67w.Thit k Redmi Note 12 Pro 5G<br>Redmi Note 12 Pro c hon thin bng cht liu nha vi phn khung vung vc. Cm camera sau  c thay i vi 3 ng knh xp theo hnh tam gic cng di n flash nm ngang. Phn mt trc ca c hai vn s dng thit k c l cha camera selfie  chnh gia.</p>\r\n<p><br><strong>Thng s, cu hnh Redmi Note 12 Pro 5G</strong><br>Mn hnh<br>6,67 inch OLED, 900 nits, 1 t mu<br> phn gii: 1080 x 2400 pixels<br>Tn s qut: 120Hz<br>Hiu nng<br>Mediatek Dimensity 1080 (6nm)<br>H iu hnh<br>MIUI 13 (da trn Android 12)<br>RAM/ROM<br>6GB / 128GB, 8GB / 128GB<br>8GB / 256GB, 12GB/256GB<br>Dung lng pin<br>5.000mAh Li-Po<br>Sc<br>Sc nhanh 67W<br>Camera<br>Camera sau: 50MP + 8MP + 2MP<br>Camera trc: 16MP<br>H tr quay video 4K 30fps<br>Thit k<br>Kch thc: 162,9 x 67 x 7,9 mm<br>Khi lng: 187 gram</p>\r\n<p><br><strong>Mn hnh</strong><br>V kh nng hin th th Redmi Note 12 Pro c trang b mn hnh OLED kch thc 6.67 inch,  phn gii 1.5K (2.400 * 1.080 pixels). Vi thng s ny, Redmi Note 12 Pro s mang n cho ngi dng tri nghim xem cc ni dung vi  chi tit cao, mu sc sng ng v khng gian tri nghim rng ri.<br>im sng gi nht trn Redmi Note 12 Pro chnh l mn hnh 1 t mu.<br><strong>Pin v sc nhanh</strong><br>Redmi Note 12 Pro c trang b vin pin 5000mAh cng kh nng sc nhanh 67W. Cng ging nh cc mu my gi r khc, Xiaomi vn s tng km c sc cho ngi dng trong hp sn phm m khng cn mua thm bn ngoi.&nbsp;<br><strong>Camera</strong><br>Redmi Note 12 Pro c camera chnh 50MP vi cm bin Sony IMX766 v OIS. Hai cm bin cn li trn c hai in thoi l cm bin siu rng 8MP v cm bin  su 2MP. Cc camera selfie pha trc c  phn gii 16MP.<br><strong>Tc  x l</strong><br>V hiu nng, my c trang b con chip Mediatek Dimensity 1080 c sn xut trn tin trnh 6nm hon ton mi. V mt l thuyt, Dimensity 1080 ch l mt phin bn nng cp nh ca Dimensity 920 5G. Tuy nhin, b vi x l mi  c nng cp  ti u v AI v phn mm cho Redmi Note 12 Pro.</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"RPT38G7\" data-pb-style=\"S7OX9N6\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hng dn mua hng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th mua hng theo mt trong cc cch sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong>1/ Mua hng trc tip:</strong><br>Qu khch c th n trc tip tham quan, tri nghim v mua sm cc sn phm Xiaomi ti tt c cc a ch sau ca MISTORE:</p>\r\n<p>364 Nguyn Tri, Thanh Xun Trung, Thanh Xun, H Ni.<br>Hotline: 03.4567.6666</p>\r\n<p>195, An Dng Vng, Phng 8, Qun 5<br>Hotline: (028)3.888.3456</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>2/ t mua qua website ca Mistore:</strong><br>Bc 1 : Click vo sn phm bn c nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Chn  Thm Vo Gi Hng   thc hin bc tip theo ( lu  bn c th chn nhiu sn phm trong cng 1 gi hng ).</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Kim tra n hng v s lng sau  chn Tin hnh t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 4 : in y  thng tin chnh xc ca qu khch v chn phng thc thanh ton mong mun, sau  kim tra li Ha n mua hng.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu mun thm sn phm khc vo n hng qu khch chn Mua thm.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu Ha n mua hng  chnh xc, qu khch chn t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 5 : Qu khch s nhn c thng bo t hng thnh cng v M n hng t h thng. Thng tin mua hng ca qu khch s c h thng gi qua email ng k, hy lu li m s n hng  tin cho vic theo di n hng ca qu khch.</p>\r\n<p>Chng ti s lin lc vi Qu khch  xc nhn n hng v tin hnh giao hng.</p>\r\n<p>( n hng cha bao gm ph vn chuyn, ph vn chuyn s c bo c th khi nhn vin gi in cht n trc khi giao. n hng ca qu khch s t ng hy nu thng tin t hng khng y  hoc khng r rng m khng cn bo trc. Nu qu khch c nhu cu gi hng ti ca hng vui lng thanh ton trc. )</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>3/ t hng qua in thoi:</strong><br>Bc 1 : in thoi n s in Thoi t Hng ti Hotline:</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Cung cp y  thng tin sn phm , mu sc, chng loi , s lng sn phm m qu khch mong mun.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Cung cp y  thng tin nhn hng ca qu khch mt cch chnh xc nht  Mistore c th giao hng cho qu khch nhanh nht.</p>\r\n<p>Thng tin thanh ton chuyn khon<br>STK: 0461000266789  Vietcombank</p>\r\n<p>Ch TK: Nguyn L Phng</p>\r\n<p>Email: mistore.com.vn@gmail.com</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong> thun tin hn cho qu trnh mua hng, hin ti Mistore.com.vn h tr cc hnh thc thanh ton sau:</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton ti ca hng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tin mt (VND)</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton th ATM</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton bng th tn dng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tr gp. Tm hiu thm ti y</strong><br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton khi nhn hng</strong><br>Hng ho s c vn chuyn qua dch v Chuyn pht nhanh / Shipper n tn nh, thanh ton sau  nhn hng.</p>\r\n<p>(*) Lu : thanh ton khi nhn hng (Cash On Delivery) ch p dng vi n hng c gi tr di 2 triu ng, cha bao gm ph vn chuyn v bo him (nu c), vi n hng ln hn vui lng lin h  c hng dn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton online</strong><br>Chuyn khon qua ti khon cng ty. Xem ti y<br>Thanh ton bng th ATM<br>Thanh ton bng th tn dng<br>Thanh ton tr gp bng th tn dng<br>Th tn dng (Credit Card) l mt loi th ngn hng c tnh nng thanh ton m khng cn tin c sn trong th. Ni cch khc l bn s mn tin ca ngn hng  thanh ton v ti cui k s cn tr li y  cho ngn hng. S tin trong th tn dng c ngn hng cp gi l hn mc th tn dng.<br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Chnh sch bo hnh\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"NVRI9NO\" data-pb-style=\"WI3UI1H\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p id=\"AMAGAE3\">Cng ty TNHH Dami Vit Nam</p>\r\n<p><strong>QUY NH V BO HNH  I MI</strong><br>Chnh sch bo hnh c p dng i vi sn phm: in thoi; My tnh bng (Tablet); My tnh xch tay (Laptop); Linh kin, Ph kin trong h thng ca hng Xiaomi chnh hng MISTORE trn ton quc.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Lu  quan trng:</strong></p>\r\n<p>K t 3/2015, Mistore p dng chnh sch bo hnh in t thng qua S in thoi/ Series number/ iMei thit b. Theo quy nh bo hnh chnh hng, Qu khch vui lng gi li v/hp thit b  c bo hnh.<br>Thi gian tip nhn &amp; tr bo hnh t: 12h00  21h00 (Tr th 7, ch nht v ngy l)<br><strong>I. &nbsp; 