ata-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Chnh sch bo hnh\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"VS6AB9I\" data-pb-style=\"PONNEXG\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p id=\"AMAGAE3\">Cng ty TNHH Dami Vit Nam</p>\r\n<p><strong>QUY NH V BO HNH  I MI</strong><br>Chnh sch bo hnh c p dng i vi sn phm: in thoi; My tnh bng (Tablet); My tnh xch tay (Laptop); Linh kin, Ph kin trong h thng ca hng Xiaomi chnh hng MISTORE trn ton quc.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Lu  quan trng:</strong></p>\r\n<p>K t 3/2015, Mistore p dng chnh sch bo hnh in t thng qua S in thoi/ Series number/ iMei thit b. Theo quy nh bo hnh chnh hng, Qu khch vui lng gi li v/hp thit b  c bo hnh.<br>Thi gian tip nhn &amp; tr bo hnh t: 12h00  21h00 (Tr th 7, ch nht v ngy l)<br><strong>I. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;CHNH SCH BO HNH:</strong><br>Lu : chnh sch bo hnh / i mi ny p dng vi sn phm nhp khu, cc sn phm c phn phi chnh hng bi DGW s c bo hnh / i mi theo chnh sch / quyt nh ca n v tip nhn bo hnh DGW (Dcare)<br>1. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh (tu theo nhm sn phm) v i mi theo chnh sch bo hnh chnh hng ca Xiaomi.</p>\r\n<p>2. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh hoc i mi trong trng hp pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut (tr ngoi hnh).</p>\r\n<p>3. &nbsp; &nbsp;Quy nh v thi gian tip nhn - x l (tnh t thi im tip nhn bo hnh):</p>\r\n<p>Thi gian kim tra: Ti a 48 gi lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Thi gian x l bo hnh: &nbsp;15 - 30 ngy lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Nu c pht sinh vn  khc, CSKH s lin h  thng bo trc t nht 24 gi.</p>\r\n<p>4. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c thay th linh kin hoc sa cha min ph khi b h hng do li k thut t nh sn xut sau thi gian quy nh i mi.</p>\r\n<p>6. &nbsp; &nbsp; Mi loi sn phm c chnh sch bo hnh ring, Qu khch vui lng xem k chnh sch bo hnh theo tng sn phm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>II. &nbsp; &nbsp; IU KIN BO HNH:</strong><br>Sn phm cn trong thi hn bo hnh.<br>Sn phm phi cn nguyn vn, khng sa cha bi cc ni khc ngoi h thng ca hng hoc Mi Store, MiCare v Dcare.<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm phi trng hp vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t v bao b sn phm.<br>Sn phm phi cn hp nguyn vn, khng b rch, khng chp ni, khng b ty xa.<br>III. &nbsp;IU KIN I MI:<br>Sn phm c hng chnh sch 1 i 1 nu pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut.<br>Sn phm i mi l sn phm ngang gi, cng chng loi, cng thng s k thut, cng mu sc. (Trng hp Store khng cn sn phm c cng mu vi sn phm c i mi, chng ti s thay th bng sn phm khc tng ng vi gi tr sn phm ). Nu sn phm khng c li t nh sn xut th s tnh khu tr 30% gi tr sn phm.<br>Thi gian bo hnh v i mi:<br>in thoi, Laptop: Bo hnh 12 Thng phn cng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin | Pin bo hnh 06 thng<br>Xe in, Xe cn bng: Bo hnh 06 Thng phn cng | Pin bo hnh 03 thng<br>Pin d phng: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Tai nghe: Bo hnh 03 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Loa bluetooth: Bo hnh 01 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Camera: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>n trn, n bn: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Sn phm thi trang, ph kin khc: Khng bo hnh, khng i mi.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>IV. &nbsp;TRNG HP T CHI BO HNH (H tr sa cha):</strong><br>Sn phm  ht hn bo hnh.<br>Cc vn  lin quan n ti khon, bo mt (Mt khu, MiCloud)<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm khng trng vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t (hoc ho n mua hng).<br>Sn phm b h hng do thin tai, l lt, st nh, ha hon hay do vn chuyn lm nt, mp, b, try xc, vo nc.<br>Sn phm h hng do s dng khng ng theo hng dn, do ngun in khng ng, khng n nh, do t  cp nht phn mm (up rom) khng ng k thut, Root my dn n h hng thit b.<br>Mn hnh xut hin di 3 im cht, mn hnh b sc, m, bi bn, phn quang hoc cht hn trong qu trnh s dng do tc dng lc, va p, vo nc.<br>Sn phm b r st,  bn do n mn hay do cht lng  vo.<br>Sn phm c du hiu  tho lp, sa cha thay th linh kin  nhng ni khc ngoi h thng Mistore, Micare, Dcare<br>Cc tng phm ph kin km theo sn phm khng phi l sn phm khng c bo hnh. V d: tng phm khuyn mi, mt s ph kin km theo my nh Pin, sc, cable, tai nghe...(nu c)<br>Cc trng hp yu cu v v sinh sn phm, bo tr sn phm khng nm trong hn mc bo hnh.<br>i vi pin tch hp, khng bo hnh cc trng hp ph, chm chy linh kin v cc trng hp chai, hng pin do s dng.<br>i vi loa, tai nghe v cc sn phm c loa, khng bo hnh li r, h.<br>V. Quy nh khc:<br>i vi nhng sn phm nh my tnh, in thoi,  cng lu tr, th nh. Chng ti hon ton khng chu trch nhim v vic mt d liu c nhn ca Qu khch nh: ti liu, danh b, tin nhn  khi thc hin cc yu cu Up Rom, sa cha.<br>Nu qu khch c nhu cu sao lu, backup d liu. Vui lng bo trc  nhn vin k thut thc hin.<br>VI. Chnh sch tr hng<br>Mi Store khng c chnh sch tr hng Qu khch vui lng tm hiu tnh nng hng ha hoc kim tra k sn phm.<br>Mt s trng hp c bit:<br>Qu khch c quyn tr hoc i mi trong trng hp sn phm pht sinh li do nh sn xut khng khc phc c hoc khc phc nhiu ln khng c.<br><strong>GIM C CNG TY</strong></p>\r\n<p> K</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(p dng t 01/01/2023)</p></div></div></div></div>'),('224',76,0,'77','<p> Nhp khu chnh hng Xiaomi (Bc Kinh)</p>\r\n<p> Bo hnh chnh hng 3 thng</p>\r\n<p> Mi 100% Fullbox nguyn seal, i mi trong 7 ngy u tin.</p>'),('225',85,0,'77','Bn l hi nc GT306LW'),('226',75,0,'78','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=DNSU92N],#html-body [data-pb-style=OHEAW21],#html-body [data-pb-style=Q7UPNVQ]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=NEYT8AC]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=RAWUCHV]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=GFL4INO],#html-body [data-pb-style=GX6FX14],#html-body [data-pb-style=RQMK1E1]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"NEYT8AC\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"Q7UPNVQ\"><a href=\"#GAG8KYX\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"DNSU92N\"><a href=\"#QS8QGWC\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"OHEAW21\"><a href=\"#K1P9A16\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"RAWUCHV\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"GAG8KYX\" data-pb-style=\"GFL4INO\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Cc loi my sy tc thng thng tuy lm kh tc nhanh, nhng s khin tc tr nn x ri v h tn. Vi tnh nng b sung ion m cho tc, my sy tc ion Xiaomi H500 s l mt la chn tuyt vi  lm kh cng nh dng m hiu qu, gip tc nhanh kh, ng thi chm sc mi tc ca bn tt hn, khin tc bn lun lun mt m sau mi ln sy.</p>\r\n<p><strong>H tr b sung ION m, gi m v gip mi tc mm mt</strong><br>My sy tc Xiaomi Mijia H500 c gii thiu vi kh nng dng m su cho tc tt hn nhng chic my sy thng thng, nh vo kh nng b sung ion Dihydrate, h tr chm sc su cho mi tc, gip tc ng , mm mt, ch khng gy kh ri nh nhng my sy thng thng. Hng chc triu ion m, s gip ci thin cc lp biu b ca si tc, gim ch ngn, tm bit x ri  cho n mt mi tc chc khe.</p>\r\n<p>So vi th h th nht th my sy tc ion Xiaomi mi s gi  m lu hn cho tc. Thit b tch hp b ngng t, lm ngng t hi m trong khng kh v ngay lp tc chuyn ha thnh cc ion m cc nh bng hai ng c hnh kim, c vn chuyn trc tip n chn tc v da u thng qua cc knh kh lnh c lp m khng cn gim nhit , m bo dng m hiu qu cho mi tc ca bn. Theo , khi s dng my sy tc Mijia H500, tc bn s mm mt v sng bng hn, vi  m tng 26.47%,  bng tng 9.12% v  mt tng 11.86%.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tc  gi 20m/s, sy kh tc nhanh chng</strong><br>My sy Xiaomi H500 c trang b ng c DC tc  cao 20000 vng/pht vi thit k 7 cnh qut tuabin, c th to ra tc  gi ln ti 20m/s. Gi c p ra thng qua mt ng dn kh nn hnh nn  to ra tc  gi cao gip lm kh tc nhanh chng m khng lm tn thng mi tc.</p>\r\n<p>Mi cnh qut hnh lng v s iu chnh cn bng ng chuyn nghip  c th chm gi tinh vi hn. Kt hp vi thit k ti u ca ng gi  gim lc cn lung gi, gip gi thi m i, t ting n, cho bn tri nghim s dng thoi mi hn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Kim sot nhit  thng minh, gim thiu h tn tc</strong><br>Cm bin nhit dng ht thy tinh c s dng trn my sy tc 2 chiu nng lnh H500  pht hin chnh xc nhit  ca ca gi 60 ln mi giy v iu chnh nhit  khng kh trong thi gian thc  ngn tc v da u khng b h tn do qu nng. Ngoi ra, ch  khng kh tun hon nng v lnh c ci tin gip kh nng lm kh nhanh chng, to kiu bng kh lnh, hn ch nhit  cao ln b mt tc, gi m cho ngn tc v chm sc hiu qu da u mng manh.</p>\r\n<p>Trong trng hp nhit  mi trng &lt; 22C th thit b s lun phin thi khng kh nng 7 giy v thi khng kh mt 5 giy. V nu nhit  mi trng  20C th my sy s thi lun phin khng kh nng trong 5 giy v 7 giy cho khng kh mt.</p>\r\n<p>Chip NTC c trang b cho php my t ng iu chnh thi gian thi khng kh nng v lnh, qua  gip n nh nhit , to cm gic thoi mi cho da u v duy tr  m cn thit cho tc. c bit, my cn c th t ng tt ngun v thc hin bo v cu ch trong cc trng hp khn cp, khi thy nhit  qu nng.</p>\r\n<p>Vi thit k tch hp u phun t tnh chng ng cn kp c kh nng xoay t do 360, c th to ra lung gi tc  cao theo hng ty chn, gip lm kh tc nhanh chng, p ng mi nhu cu to kiu. ng thi, vt liu cch nhit c s dng cn c th lm gim nhit  ca u phun, trnh hiu qu tnh trng b bng do nhit  cao.</p>\r\n<p><strong>3 mc nhit NNG - LNH - lun phin, cng 2 tc  gi</strong><br>My sy tc gi r Xiaomi Mijia H500 c trang b 3 ch  gi nhit. Trong , gi nng v lnh c th c chuyn i linh hot, kt hp vi 2 la chn tc  gi thi theo  mun  ngi dng c th s dng thoi mi ty vo nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p>n LED 2 mu c tch hp  bn thun tin theo di s thay i ca nhit  gi. Bn cnh , tnh nng ci t nhit  cng s c t ng ghi nh li  s dng cho ln k tip.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thit k nh gn, di ng</strong><br>V ngoi hnh, my c thit k kh nh gn, va lng bn tay vi trng lng nh ch 550g, d dng cm nm v s dng lu m khng b mi tay. Bn cnh , thit k ny cn gip bn thun tin hn khi b my vo hnh l  mang theo khi i cng tc, du lch.</p>\r\n<p>Phn tay cm ca my sy tc mini H500 c ph mt lp sn BabyskinUV cho bn cm gic cm nm v cng thn thin, mn mng nh da em b. Ngoi ra, quy trnh phun sn 2 lp cn gip chng  mu v chng try xc cho my, d dng lu vn lun trng sng nh mi.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thng s k thut</strong><br>Model &nbsp; &nbsp;CMJ03LX&nbsp;<br>Kch thc &nbsp; &nbsp;144 x 79 x 237mm (bao gm vi phun)&nbsp;<br>Khi lng tnh &nbsp; &nbsp;595g&nbsp;<br>Vt liu &nbsp; &nbsp;Nha - Kim loi&nbsp;<br>Chc nng &nbsp; &nbsp;Lm kh &amp; B sung ION m&nbsp;<br>in p/ Tn s nh mc &nbsp; &nbsp;220V~ 50Hz&nbsp;<br>Cng sut nh mc &nbsp; &nbsp;1800W&nbsp;<br>Chiu di dy ngun &nbsp; &nbsp;1.7m&nbsp;<br>Ch  s dng &nbsp; &nbsp;Gi Nng - Lnh, 2 tc  gi</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"QS8QGWC\" data-pb-style=\"GX6FX14\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hng dn mua hng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th mua hng theo mt trong cc cch sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong>1/ Mua hng trc tip:</strong><br>Qu khch c th n trc tip tham quan, tri nghim v mua sm cc sn phm Xiaomi ti tt c cc a ch sau ca MISTORE:</p>\r\n<p>364 Nguyn Tri, Thanh Xun Trung, Thanh Xun, H Ni.<br>Hotline: 03.4567.6666</p>\r\n<p>195, An Dng Vng, Phng 8, Qun 5<br>Hotline: (028)3.888.3456</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>2/ t mua qua website ca Mistore:</strong><br>Bc 1 : Click vo sn phm bn c nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Chn  Thm Vo Gi Hng   thc hin bc tip theo ( lu  bn c th chn nhiu sn phm trong cng 1 gi hng ).</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Kim tra n hng v s lng sau  chn Tin hnh t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 4 : in y  thng tin chnh xc ca qu khch v chn phng thc thanh ton mong mun, sau  kim tra li Ha n mua hng.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu mun thm sn phm khc vo n hng qu khch chn Mua thm.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu Ha n mua hng  chnh xc, qu khch chn t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 5 : Qu khch s nhn c thng bo t hng thnh cng v M n hng t h thng. Thng tin mua hng ca qu khch s c h thng gi qua email ng k, hy lu li m s n hng  tin cho vic theo di n hng ca qu khch.</p>\r\n<p>Chng ti s lin lc vi Qu khch  xc nhn n hng v tin hnh giao hng.</p>\r\n<p>( n hng cha bao gm ph vn chuyn, ph vn chuyn s c bo c th khi nhn vin gi in cht n trc khi giao. n hng ca qu khch s t ng hy nu thng tin t hng khng y  hoc khng r rng m khng cn bo trc. Nu qu khch c nhu cu gi hng ti ca hng vui lng thanh ton trc. )</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>3/ t hng qua in thoi:</strong><br>Bc 1 : in thoi n s in Thoi t Hng ti Hotline:</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Cung cp y  thng tin sn phm , mu sc, chng loi , s lng sn phm m qu khch mong mun.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Cung cp y  thng tin nhn hng ca qu khch mt cch chnh xc nht  Mistore c th giao hng cho qu khch nhanh nht.</p>\r\n<p>Thng tin thanh ton chuyn khon<br>STK: 0461000266789  Vietcombank</p>\r\n<p>Ch TK: Nguyn L Phng</p>\r\n<p>Email: mistore.com.vn@gmail.com</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong> thun tin hn cho qu trnh mua hng, hin ti Mistore.com.vn h tr cc hnh thc thanh ton sau:</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton ti ca hng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tin mt (VND)</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton th ATM</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton bng th tn dng</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton tr gp. Tm hiu thm ti y</strong><br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Thanh ton khi nhn hng</strong><br>Hng ho s c vn chuyn qua dch v Chuyn pht nhanh / Shipper n tn nh, thanh ton sau  nhn hng.</p>\r\n<p>(*) Lu : thanh ton khi nhn hng (Cash On Delivery) ch p dng vi n hng c gi tr di 2 triu ng, cha bao gm ph vn chuyn v bo him (nu c), vi n hng ln hn vui lng lin h  c hng dn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong><br><strong>Thanh ton online</strong><br>Chuyn khon qua ti khon cng ty. Xem ti y<br>Thanh ton bng th ATM<br>Thanh ton bng th tn dng<br>Thanh ton tr gp bng th tn dng<br>Th tn dng (Credit Card) l mt loi th ngn hng c tnh nng thanh ton m khng cn tin c sn trong th. Ni cch khc l bn s mn tin ca ngn hng  thanh ton v ti cui k s cn tr li y  cho ngn hng. S tin trong th tn dng c ngn hng cp gi l hn mc th tn dng.<br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Chnh sch bo hnh\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"K1P9A16\" data-pb-style=\"RQMK1E1\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p id=\"AMAGAE3\">Cng ty TNHH Dami Vit Nam</p>\r\n<p><strong>QUY NH V BO HNH  I MI</strong><br>Chnh sch bo hnh c p dng i vi sn phm: in thoi; My tnh bng (Tablet); My tnh xch tay (Laptop); Linh kin, Ph kin trong h thng ca hng Xiaomi chnh hng MISTORE trn ton quc.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Lu  quan trng:</strong></p>\r\n<p>K t 3/2015, Mistore p dng chnh sch bo hnh in t thng qua S in thoi/ Series number/ iMei thit b. Theo quy nh bo hnh chnh hng, Qu khch vui lng gi li v/hp thit b  c bo hnh.<br>Thi gian tip nhn &amp; tr bo hnh t: 12h00  21h00 (Tr th 7, ch nht v ngy l)<br><strong>I. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;CHNH SCH BO HNH:</strong><br>Lu : chnh sch bo hnh / i mi ny p dng vi sn phm nhp khu, cc sn phm c phn phi chnh hng bi DGW s c bo hnh / i mi theo chnh sch / quyt nh ca n v tip nhn bo hnh DGW (Dcare)<br>1. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh (tu theo nhm sn phm) v i mi theo chnh sch bo hnh chnh hng ca Xiaomi.</p>\r\n<p>2. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh hoc i mi trong trng hp pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut (tr ngoi hnh).</p>\r\n<p>3. &nbsp; &nbsp;Quy nh v thi gian tip nhn - x l (tnh t thi im tip nhn bo hnh):</p>\r\n<p>Thi gian kim tra: Ti a 48 gi lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Thi gian x l bo hnh: &nbsp;15 - 30 ngy lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Nu c pht sinh vn  khc, CSKH s lin h  thng bo trc t nht 24 gi.</p>\r\n<p>4. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c thay th linh kin hoc sa cha min ph khi b h hng do li k thut t nh sn xut sau thi gian quy nh i mi.</p>\r\n<p>6. &nbsp; &nbsp; Mi loi sn phm c chnh sch bo hnh ring, Qu khch vui lng xem k chnh sch bo hnh theo tng sn phm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>II. &nbsp; &nbsp; IU KIN BO HNH:</strong><br>Sn phm cn trong thi hn bo hnh.<br>Sn phm phi cn nguyn vn, khng sa cha bi cc ni khc ngoi h thng ca hng hoc Mi Store, MiCare v Dcare.<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm phi trng hp vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t v bao b sn phm.<br>Sn phm phi cn hp nguyn vn, khng b rch, khng chp ni, khng b ty xa.<br>III. &nbsp;IU KIN I MI:<br>Sn phm c hng chnh sch 1 i 1 nu pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut.<br>Sn phm i mi l sn phm ngang gi, cng chng loi, cng thng s k thut, cng mu sc. (Trng hp Store khng cn sn phm c cng mu vi sn phm c i mi, chng ti s thay th bng sn phm khc tng ng vi gi tr sn phm ). Nu sn phm khng c li t nh sn xut th s tnh khu tr 30% gi tr sn phm.<br>Thi gian bo hnh v i mi:<br>in thoi, Laptop: Bo hnh 12 Thng phn cng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin | Pin bo hnh 06 thng<br>Xe in, Xe cn bng: Bo hnh 06 Thng phn cng | Pin bo hnh 03 thng<br>Pin d phng: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Tai nghe: Bo hnh 03 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Loa bluetooth: Bo hnh 01 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Camera: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>n trn, n bn: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Sn phm thi trang, ph kin khc: Khng bo hnh, khng i mi.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>IV. &nbsp;TRNG HP T CHI BO HNH (H tr sa cha):</strong><br>Sn phm  ht hn bo hnh.<br>Cc vn  lin quan n ti khon, bo mt (Mt khu, MiCloud)<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm khng trng vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t (hoc ho n mua hng).<br>Sn phm b h hng do thin tai, l lt, st nh, ha hon hay do vn chuyn lm nt, mp, b, try xc, vo nc.<br>Sn phm h hng do s dng khng ng theo hng dn, do ngun in khng ng, khng n nh, do t  cp nht phn mm (up rom) khng ng k thut, Root my dn n h hng thit b.<br>Mn hnh xut hin di 3 im cht, mn hnh b sc, m, bi bn, phn quang hoc cht hn trong qu trnh s dng do tc dng lc, va p, vo nc.<br>Sn phm b r st,  bn do n mn hay do cht lng  vo.<br>Sn phm c du hiu  tho lp, sa cha thay th linh kin  nhng ni khc ngoi h thng Mistore, Micare, Dcare<br>Cc tng phm ph kin km theo sn phm khng phi l sn phm khng c bo hnh. V d: tng phm khuyn mi, mt s ph kin km theo my nh Pin, sc, cable, tai nghe...(nu c)<br>Cc trng hp yu cu v v sinh sn phm, bo tr sn phm khng nm trong hn mc bo hnh.<br>i vi pin tch hp, khng bo hnh cc trng hp ph, chm chy linh kin v cc trng hp chai, hng pin do s dng.<br>i vi loa, tai nghe v cc sn phm c loa, khng bo hnh li r, h.<br>V. Quy nh khc:<br>i vi nhng sn phm nh my tnh, in thoi,  cng lu tr, th nh. Chng ti hon ton khng chu trch nhim v vic mt d liu c nhn ca Qu khch nh: ti liu, danh b, tin nhn  khi thc hin cc yu cu Up Rom, sa cha.<br>Nu qu khch c nhu cu sao lu, backup d liu. Vui lng bo trc  nhn vin k thut thc hin.<br>VI. Chnh sch tr hng<br>Mi Store khng c chnh sch tr hng Qu khch vui lng tm hiu tnh nng hng ha hoc kim tra k sn phm.<br>Mt s trng hp c bit:<br>Qu khch c quyn tr hoc i mi trong trng hp sn phm pht sinh li do nh sn xut khng khc phc c hoc khc phc nhiu ln khng c.<br><strong>GIM C CNG TY</strong></p>\r\n<p> K</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(p dng t 01/01/2023)</p></div></div></div></div>'),('227',76,0,'78','<p> Nhp khu chnh hng Xiaomi (Bc Kinh)</p>\r\n<p> Bo hnh chnh hng 6 thng, i mi trong 7 ngy u tin.</p>\r\n<p> Mi 100% Fullbox nguyn seal</p>'),('228',85,0,'78','My sy tc Ion Xiaomi Mijia H500');
INSERT INTO `catalog_product_entity_text` VALUES ('229',75,0,'79','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=OS0TF8V],#html-body [data-pb-style=S7WTAS2],#html-body [data-pb-style=YG3RCLU]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=KWTGSAT]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=TCI458I]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=G780K3M],#html-body [data-pb-style=URA4GLT],#html-body [data-pb-style=WIC4UBE]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"KWTGSAT\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"YG3RCLU\"><a href=\"#VY1714C\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"OS0TF8V\"><a href=\"#UYRFSE5\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"S7WTAS2\"><a href=\"#TMFTH78\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"TCI458I\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"VY1714C\" data-pb-style=\"URA4GLT\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Thit k my sy c o, tinh t</strong><br>My sy kh mi giy Deerma DEM-HX10 s hu thit k nh gn cng trng lng nh, kh thun tin  lu tr  bt k gc no trong nh m khng chim nhiu din tch. Ngoi ra my sy Deerma c thit k ca thot kh hnh ch U c o, cho kh nng lm kh 2 i giy cng 1 lc, gii quyt nhu cu sy giy vo nhng ngy ma.Bn cnh kh nng sy kh giy trc tip bng ng sy ng, my cn h tr ng dn kh c th ko di ti 27cm gip my sy c th xm nhp vo su trong giy v sy kh  mi ngc ngch. Ngoi ra i vi nhng i giy boot th my h tr np n pha sau  a my sang ch  nghing, gip vic sy giy thun tin hn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cch thc hot ng</strong><br>Lung kh nng 65C khng i xuyn qua cc lp da trong giy, lc ny my sy s to ra 1 lng kh 03 thm u tng si trong giy  lp tc bt ly cc yu t gy mi v t bo vi khun trong khng kh tiu dit 99.9% vi khun Staphylococcus aureus ph bin trong giy, candida albicans, nhanh chng ly i  m v gi cho giy kh ro. Lng nhit lm kh giy kh ln, ngi dng khng cn phi ch lu. Ch khong 15 giy th lng khng kh s lin tc xut ra. Ca thot kh phn chia lung kh thnh 3 giai on v xoay 360, gip lm kh ton b giy nhanh chng</p>\r\n<p><strong>Nhiu ch  sy, ph hp vi nhiu loi giy</strong><br>H tr nhiu ch  sy, ph hp vi nhiu loi giy khc nhau nh ch  tiu chun dnh cho cc loi giy boot, giy c cao. Ch  giy da dnh cho cc loi giy da, ch  sy nh dnh cho cc loi giy bata hoc giy c thp v cui cng l ch  sy v. Bn cnh  my sy DEM-HX10 cn h tr 4 ch  thi gian sy gm 30 pht, 60 pht, 120 pht v 180 pht cho php ngi dng linh hot la chn ch  v thi gian sy ph hp.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thit k a nng, c tnh ng dng cao</strong><br>Bn cnh tnh nng lm kh giy, ngi dng cn c th s dng my vi nhiu tnh nng khc. C th nh nh lung khng kh nng lin tc c ta ra t ng c DC c th s dng  ht m gip mi trng xung quanh lun kh thong, lm my si m vo ma thu ng hoc  sy kh qun o v chng cc loi vi khun mt cch hiu qu.</p>\r\n<p><strong>3 tnh nng bo v ti u</strong><br>Hot ng vi mc nhit  65C, tuy nhin ngi dng c th s dng b iu chnh nhit  iu chnh nhit  ln mc 90C. Tuy nhin nu qu nhit  trn th my t ng tt ngun, cu ch nhit  cng s t ng ngt  bo v an ton cho sn phm. Ngoi ra sau khi sy kh, l thng hi c tch hp pha sau c chc nng lm mt tc thi, bo m an ton cho thit b v giy ca ngi dng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thng s k thut</strong><br>Model: DEM-HX10&nbsp;<br>in p nh mc: 220V<br>Tn s nh mc: 50Hz<br>Cng sut nh mc: 235W<br>Vt liu: ABS<br>Phng php iu khin: Nt bm<br>Trng lng sn phm/ng gi: 1.2kg/1.8kg<br>Kch thc sn phm: 21.1 x 11.7 x 28cm<br>Kch thc ng gi: 23 x 14 x 30cm</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"UYRFSE5\" data-pb-style=\"G780K3M\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hng dn mua hng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th mua hng theo mt trong cc cch sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong>1/ Mua hng trc tip:</strong><br>Qu khch c th n trc tip tham quan, tri nghim v mua sm cc sn phm Xiaomi ti tt c cc a ch sau ca MISTORE:</p>\r\n<p>364 Nguyn Tri, Thanh Xun Trung, Thanh Xun, H Ni.<br>Hotline: 03.4567.6666</p>\r\n<p>195, An Dng Vng, Phng 8, Qun 5<br>Hotline: (028)3.888.3456</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>2/ t mua qua website ca Mistore:</strong><br>Bc 1 : Click vo sn phm bn c nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Chn  Thm Vo Gi Hng   thc hin bc tip theo ( lu  bn c th chn nhiu sn phm trong cng 1 gi hng ).</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Kim tra n hng v s lng sau  chn Tin hnh t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 4 : in y  thng tin chnh xc ca qu khch v chn phng thc thanh ton mong mun, sau  kim tra li Ha n mua hng.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu mun thm sn phm khc vo n hng qu khch chn Mua thm.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu Ha n mua hng  chnh xc, qu khch chn t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 5 : Qu khch s nhn c thng bo t hng thnh cng v M n hng t h thng. Thng tin mua hng ca qu khch s c h thng gi qua email ng k, hy lu li m s n hng  tin cho vic theo di n hng ca qu khch.</p>\r\n<p>Chng ti s lin lc vi Qu khch  xc nhn n hng v tin hnh giao hng.</p>\r\n<p>( n hng cha bao gm ph vn chuyn, ph vn chuyn s c bo c th khi nhn vin gi in cht n trc khi giao. n hng ca qu khch s t ng hy nu thng tin t hng khng y  hoc khng r rng m khng cn bo trc. Nu qu khch c nhu cu gi hng ti ca hng vui lng thanh ton trc. )</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>3/ t hng qua in thoi:</strong><br>Bc 1 : in thoi n s in Thoi t Hng ti Hotline:</