r gp bng th tn dng<br>Th tn dng (Credit Card) l mt loi th ngn hng c tnh nng thanh ton m khng cn tin c sn trong th. Ni cch khc l bn s mn tin ca ngn hng  thanh ton v ti cui k s cn tr li y  cho ngn hng. S tin trong th tn dng c ngn hng cp gi l hn mc th tn dng.<br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Chnh sch bo hnh\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"IG75RCB\" data-pb-style=\"UOTK2L9\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p id=\"AMAGAE3\">Cng ty TNHH Dami Vit Nam</p>\r\n<p><strong>QUY NH V BO HNH  I MI</strong><br>Chnh sch bo hnh c p dng i vi sn phm: in thoi; My tnh bng (Tablet); My tnh xch tay (Laptop); Linh kin, Ph kin trong h thng ca hng Xiaomi chnh hng MISTORE trn ton quc.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Lu  quan trng:</strong></p>\r\n<p>K t 3/2015, Mistore p dng chnh sch bo hnh in t thng qua S in thoi/ Series number/ iMei thit b. Theo quy nh bo hnh chnh hng, Qu khch vui lng gi li v/hp thit b  c bo hnh.<br>Thi gian tip nhn &amp; tr bo hnh t: 12h00  21h00 (Tr th 7, ch nht v ngy l)<br><strong>I. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;CHNH SCH BO HNH:</strong><br>Lu : chnh sch bo hnh / i mi ny p dng vi sn phm nhp khu, cc sn phm c phn phi chnh hng bi DGW s c bo hnh / i mi theo chnh sch / quyt nh ca n v tip nhn bo hnh DGW (Dcare)<br>1. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh (tu theo nhm sn phm) v i mi theo chnh sch bo hnh chnh hng ca Xiaomi.</p>\r\n<p>2. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh hoc i mi trong trng hp pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut (tr ngoi hnh).</p>\r\n<p>3. &nbsp; &nbsp;Quy nh v thi gian tip nhn - x l (tnh t thi im tip nhn bo hnh):</p>\r\n<p>Thi gian kim tra: Ti a 48 gi lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Thi gian x l bo hnh: &nbsp;15 - 30 ngy lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Nu c pht sinh vn  khc, CSKH s lin h  thng bo trc t nht 24 gi.</p>\r\n<p>4. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c thay th linh kin hoc sa cha min ph khi b h hng do li k thut t nh sn xut sau thi gian quy nh i mi.</p>\r\n<p>6. &nbsp; &nbsp; Mi loi sn phm c chnh sch bo hnh ring, Qu khch vui lng xem k chnh sch bo hnh theo tng sn phm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>II. &nbsp; &nbsp; IU KIN BO HNH:</strong><br>Sn phm cn trong thi hn bo hnh.<br>Sn phm phi cn nguyn vn, khng sa cha bi cc ni khc ngoi h thng ca hng hoc Mi Store, MiCare v Dcare.<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm phi trng hp vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t v bao b sn phm.<br>Sn phm phi cn hp nguyn vn, khng b rch, khng chp ni, khng b ty xa.<br>III. &nbsp;IU KIN I MI:<br>Sn phm c hng chnh sch 1 i 1 nu pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut.<br>Sn phm i mi l sn phm ngang gi, cng chng loi, cng thng s k thut, cng mu sc. (Trng hp Store khng cn sn phm c cng mu vi sn phm c i mi, chng ti s thay th bng sn phm khc tng ng vi gi tr sn phm ). Nu sn phm khng c li t nh sn xut th s tnh khu tr 30% gi tr sn phm.<br>Thi gian bo hnh v i mi:<br>in thoi, Laptop: Bo hnh 12 Thng phn cng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin | Pin bo hnh 06 thng<br>Xe in, Xe cn bng: Bo hnh 06 Thng phn cng | Pin bo hnh 03 thng<br>Pin d phng: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Tai nghe: Bo hnh 03 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Loa bluetooth: Bo hnh 01 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Camera: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>n trn, n bn: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Sn phm thi trang, ph kin khc: Khng bo hnh, khng i mi.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>IV. &nbsp;TRNG HP T CHI BO HNH (H tr sa cha):</strong><br>Sn phm  ht hn bo hnh.<br>Cc vn  lin quan n ti khon, bo mt (Mt khu, MiCloud)<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm khng trng vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t (hoc ho n mua hng).<br>Sn phm b h hng do thin tai, l lt, st nh, ha hon hay do vn chuyn lm nt, mp, b, try xc, vo nc.<br>Sn phm h hng do s dng khng ng theo hng dn, do ngun in khng ng, khng n nh, do t  cp nht phn mm (up rom) khng ng k thut, Root my dn n h hng thit b.<br>Mn hnh xut hin di 3 im cht, mn hnh b sc, m, bi bn, phn quang hoc cht hn trong qu trnh s dng do tc dng lc, va p, vo nc.<br>Sn phm b r st,  bn do n mn hay do cht lng  vo.<br>Sn phm c du hiu  tho lp, sa cha thay th linh kin  nhng ni khc ngoi h thng Mistore, Micare, Dcare<br>Cc tng phm ph kin km theo sn phm khng phi l sn phm khng c bo hnh. V d: tng phm khuyn mi, mt s ph kin km theo my nh Pin, sc, cable, tai nghe...(nu c)<br>Cc trng hp yu cu v v sinh sn phm, bo tr sn phm khng nm trong hn mc bo hnh.<br>i vi pin tch hp, khng bo hnh cc trng hp ph, chm chy linh kin v cc trng hp chai, hng pin do s dng.<br>i vi loa, tai nghe v cc sn phm c loa, khng bo hnh li r, h.<br>V. Quy nh khc:<br>i vi nhng sn phm nh my tnh, in thoi,  cng lu tr, th nh. Chng ti hon ton khng chu trch nhim v vic mt d liu c nhn ca Qu khch nh: ti liu, danh b, tin nhn  khi thc hin cc yu cu Up Rom, sa cha.<br>Nu qu khch c nhu cu sao lu, backup d liu. Vui lng bo trc  nhn vin k thut thc hin.<br>VI. Chnh sch tr hng<br>Mi Store khng c chnh sch tr hng Qu khch vui lng tm hiu tnh nng hng ha hoc kim tra k sn phm.<br>Mt s trng hp c bit:<br>Qu khch c quyn tr hoc i mi trong trng hp sn phm pht sinh li do nh sn xut khng khc phc c hoc khc phc nhiu ln khng c.<br><strong>GIM C CNG TY</strong></p>\r\n<p> K</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(p dng t 01/01/2023)</p></div></div></div></div>'),('233',76,0,'80','<p> Nhp khu chnh hng Xiaomi (Bc Kinh)</p>\r\n<p> Bo hnh chnh hng 6 thng, i mi trong 7 ngy u tin.</p>\r\n<p> Mi 100% Fullbox nguyn seal</p>'),('234',85,0,'80','My lc nc MR624');
INSERT INTO `catalog_product_entity_text` VALUES ('235',75,0,'81','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=DL5XWA9],#html-body [data-pb-style=G87WOJ8],#html-body [data-pb-style=VONIJ7E]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=BATECTR]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=QDL39DP]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=F5SLRDH],#html-body [data-pb-style=NALRVA8],#html-body [data-pb-style=PA9EW90]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"BATECTR\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"DL5XWA9\"><a href=\"#WIDPX26\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"G87WOJ8\"><a href=\"#G28NVRY\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"VONIJ7E\"><a href=\"#QQI9XKG\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"QDL39DP\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"WIDPX26\" data-pb-style=\"F5SLRDH\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>My lc nc Xiaomi H400G MR442-A s hu thit k cc k nh gn i km 2 li lc, cng h thng lc 6 giai on, ng dng cng ngh cao, s l la chn hon ho dnh cho cc gia nh. Gip mang li ngun nc sch cho mi nhu cu s dng ca gia nh t nc tinh khit  ung trc tip n nc sinh hot.</p>\r\n<p>Xiaomi H400G MR442-A l phin bn my lc nc hon ton mi n t Xiaomi vi thit k v cng tit kim khng gian lp t, thng lng lc nc n 400G, i km h thng lc 6 giai on, kt ni App theo di TDS, tui th b lc,...T  cho hiu qu cao trong vic lc su mi, asen, ch, E.coli v cc cht c hi khc, mang n ngun nc sch cho mi nhu cu s dng trong gia nh t n ung, ra rau c n ung trc tip. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>H thng lc 6 giai on</strong><br>My lc nc Xiaomi H400G MR442-A &nbsp;c bit c thit k vi 2 li lc PPC v RO cht lng cao, h tr n 6 giai on lc, gip cho hiu qu cao trong vic lc su, loi b mi v cc cht c hi, mang n ngun nc sch tinh khit cho mi nhu cu s dng.</p>\r\n<p>H thng lc 6 giai on gm bng lc PP s loi b ph sa v r st. Thanh than hot tnh CB1 s hp th mi, mu, clo d v mt s cht hu c. Cht c ch gip ngn nga tc nghn h thng v ko di tui th ca mn thm thu ngc RO. Mn thm thu ngc RO vi  chnh xc lc l thuyt l mt phn nghn micromet gip loi b mi hi, asen, ch, E.coli v cc cht c hi khc. Thanh than hot tnh CB2 c trang b pha sau vi kh nng hp th mnh m, h tr ci thin mi v v cui cng l lp vi khng dt chn bt cacbon  gim nc en.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thng lng ln, t nc thi</strong><br>Thng lng nc ca H400G MR442-A ln n 400G c th  y mt ly nc ch trong 12 giy, p ng tt cho mi nhu cu s dng nc hng ngy ca gia nh. c bit, t l nc tinh khit v nc thi ca my lc l 2:1, t nc thi nn s tit kim nc hn, trong khi tng lng nc rng t n 4000L.</p>\r\n<p>B sn phm cng i km vi thng minh, tch hp chc nng s dng kp gm nc tinh khit v nc sinh hot. C th, vi c thit k vi hai thanh iu khin, mt bn l nc sinh hot dng  ra rau, bt a,...Bn cn li l nc tinh khit c th ung trc tip. Trn vi cn c tch hp n bo nhc nh kh trc quan. Khi n xanh ngha l b lc bnh thng v khi n chuyn cam th bn cn thay li lc.</p>\r\n<p>c bit, My lc nc Xiaomi H400G cn c th c kt ni vi App Mijia  ngi dng c th gim st gi tr TDS ca ngun nc v xem tui th b lc ngay thi gian thc.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thit k nh gn, d lp t v s dng</strong><br>My lc nc Xiaomi H400G MR442-A c thit k tch hp trc tip ng dn nc, khng c bnh cha nh nhng phin bn my lc nc thng thng. T  gip thn my c kt cu v cng nh gn ch 120 x 334mm, nn rt tit kim din tch v c bit l linh hot hn cho qu trnh lp t.</p>\r\n<p>Vic thay th li lc cho my lc nc Xiaomi cng v cng d dng. C th, ngi dng ch cn thao tc vn v ko  thay th li lc ngay ti nh m khng cn phi di chuyn thn my ra vo. Theo khuyn co, li lc s c thi gian s dng ti a l 6 thng, tuy nhin ty vo iu kin ngun nc, my c th bo thay lc sm hn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Thng s k thut</strong><br>Model &nbsp; &nbsp;MR442-A&nbsp;<br>Kch thc sn phm &nbsp; &nbsp;395 x 334 x 120mm&nbsp;<br>Tng lng nc tinh khit nh mc &nbsp; &nbsp;1500L, 4000L&nbsp;<br>Khi lng sn phm &nbsp; &nbsp;7.9kg&nbsp;<br>Cng sut nh mc &nbsp; &nbsp;55W&nbsp;<br>Tn s nh mc &nbsp; &nbsp;50Hz&nbsp;<br>in p nh mc &nbsp; &nbsp;220V&nbsp;<br>Lu lng nc tinh khit &nbsp; &nbsp;2.0L/pht, 1.05L/pht&nbsp;<br>Nhit  nc p dng &nbsp; &nbsp;5C - 38C<br>p sut nc u vo &nbsp; &nbsp;0.1-0.4Mpa</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"G28NVRY\" data-pb-style=\"NALRVA8\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hng dn mua hng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th mua hng theo mt trong cc cch sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong>1/ Mua hng trc tip:</strong><br>Qu khch c th n trc tip tham quan, tri nghim v mua sm cc sn phm Xiaomi ti tt c cc a ch sau ca MISTORE:</p>\r\n<p>364 Nguyn Tri, Thanh Xun Trung, Thanh Xun, H Ni.<br>Hotline: 03.4567.6666</p>\r\n<p>195, An Dng Vng, Phng 8, Qun 5<br>Hotline: (028)3.888.3456</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>2/ t mua qua website ca Mistore:</strong><br>Bc 1 : Click vo sn phm bn c nhu cu.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 2 : Chn  Thm Vo Gi Hng   thc hin bc tip theo ( lu  bn c th chn nhiu sn phm trong cng 1 gi hng ).</p>\r\n<p>Bc 3 : Kim tra n hng v s lng sau  chn Tin hnh t hng.</p>\r\n<p>Bc 4 : in y  thng tin chnh xc ca qu khch v chn phng thc thanh ton mong mun, sau  kim tra li Ha n mua hng.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu mun thm sn phm k