 tr gp bng th tn dng<br>Th tn dng (Credit Card) l mt loi th ngn hng c tnh nng thanh ton m khng cn tin c sn trong th. Ni cch khc l bn s mn tin ca ngn hng  thanh ton v ti cui k s cn tr li y  cho ngn hng. S tin trong th tn dng c ngn hng cp gi l hn mc th tn dng.<br>(*) Mt s th c th pht sinh ph thanh ton</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Chnh sch bo hnh\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"QQI9XKG\" data-pb-style=\"PA9EW90\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p id=\"AMAGAE3\">Cng ty TNHH Dami Vit Nam</p>\r\n<p><strong>QUY NH V BO HNH  I MI</strong><br>Chnh sch bo hnh c p dng i vi sn phm: in thoi; My tnh bng (Tablet); My tnh xch tay (Laptop); Linh kin, Ph kin trong h thng ca hng Xiaomi chnh hng MISTORE trn ton quc.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br><strong>Lu  quan trng:</strong></p>\r\n<p>K t 3/2015, Mistore p dng chnh sch bo hnh in t thng qua S in thoi/ Series number/ iMei thit b. Theo quy nh bo hnh chnh hng, Qu khch vui lng gi li v/hp thit b  c bo hnh.<br>Thi gian tip nhn &amp; tr bo hnh t: 12h00  21h00 (Tr th 7, ch nht v ngy l)<br><strong>I. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;CHNH SCH BO HNH:</strong><br>Lu : chnh sch bo hnh / i mi ny p dng vi sn phm nhp khu, cc sn phm c phn phi chnh hng bi DGW s c bo hnh / i mi theo chnh sch / quyt nh ca n v tip nhn bo hnh DGW (Dcare)<br>1. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh (tu theo nhm sn phm) v i mi theo chnh sch bo hnh chnh hng ca Xiaomi.</p>\r\n<p>2. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c bo hnh hoc i mi trong trng hp pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut (tr ngoi hnh).</p>\r\n<p>3. &nbsp; &nbsp;Quy nh v thi gian tip nhn - x l (tnh t thi im tip nhn bo hnh):</p>\r\n<p>Thi gian kim tra: Ti a 48 gi lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Thi gian x l bo hnh: &nbsp;15 - 30 ngy lm vic (khng tnh th 7, ch nht v ngy l).<br>Nu c pht sinh vn  khc, CSKH s lin h  thng bo trc t nht 24 gi.</p>\r\n<p>4. &nbsp; &nbsp; Sn phm c thay th linh kin hoc sa cha min ph khi b h hng do li k thut t nh sn xut sau thi gian quy nh i mi.</p>\r\n<p>6. &nbsp; &nbsp; Mi loi sn phm c chnh sch bo hnh ring, Qu khch vui lng xem k chnh sch bo hnh theo tng sn phm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>II. &nbsp; &nbsp; IU KIN BO HNH:</strong><br>Sn phm cn trong thi hn bo hnh.<br>Sn phm phi cn nguyn vn, khng sa cha bi cc ni khc ngoi h thng ca hng hoc Mi Store, MiCare v Dcare.<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm phi trng hp vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t v bao b sn phm.<br>Sn phm phi cn hp nguyn vn, khng b rch, khng chp ni, khng b ty xa.<br>III. &nbsp;IU KIN I MI:<br>Sn phm c hng chnh sch 1 i 1 nu pht sinh li k thut khng th khc phc c t nh sn xut.<br>Sn phm i mi l sn phm ngang gi, cng chng loi, cng thng s k thut, cng mu sc. (Trng hp Store khng cn sn phm c cng mu vi sn phm c i mi, chng ti s thay th bng sn phm khc tng ng vi gi tr sn phm ). Nu sn phm khng c li t nh sn xut th s tnh khu tr 30% gi tr sn phm.<br>Thi gian bo hnh v i mi:<br>in thoi, Laptop: Bo hnh 12 Thng phn cng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin | Pin bo hnh 06 thng<br>Xe in, Xe cn bng: Bo hnh 06 Thng phn cng | Pin bo hnh 03 thng<br>Pin d phng: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Tai nghe: Bo hnh 03 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Loa bluetooth: Bo hnh 01 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Camera: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>n trn, n bn: Bo hnh 06 Thng | 1 i 1 trong 07 ngy u tin.<br>Sn phm thi trang, ph kin khc: Khng bo hnh, khng i mi.<br>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>IV. &nbsp;TRNG HP T CHI BO HNH (H tr sa cha):</strong><br>Sn phm  ht hn bo hnh.<br>Cc vn  lin quan n ti khon, bo mt (Mt khu, MiCloud)<br>S S-ri my, kiu my trn sn phm khng trng vi s S-ri my, kiu my trn h thng bo hnh in t (hoc ho n mua hng).<br>Sn phm b h hng do thin tai, l lt, st nh, ha hon hay do vn chuyn lm nt, mp, b, try xc, vo nc.<br>Sn phm h hng do s dng khng ng theo hng dn, do ngun in khng ng, khng n nh, do t  cp nht phn mm (up rom) khng ng k thut, Root my dn n h hng thit b.<br>Mn hnh xut hin di 3 im cht, mn hnh b sc, m, bi bn, phn quang hoc cht hn trong qu trnh s dng do tc dng lc, va p, vo nc.<br>Sn phm b r st,  bn do n mn hay do cht lng  vo.<br>Sn phm c du hiu  tho lp, sa cha thay th linh kin  nhng ni khc ngoi h thng Mistore, Micare, Dcare<br>Cc tng phm ph kin km theo sn phm khng phi l sn phm khng c bo hnh. V d: tng phm khuyn mi, mt s ph kin km theo my nh Pin, sc, cable, tai nghe...(nu c)<br>Cc trng hp yu cu v v sinh sn phm, bo tr sn phm khng nm trong hn mc bo hnh.<br>i vi pin tch hp, khng bo hnh cc trng hp ph, chm chy linh kin v cc trng hp chai, hng pin do s dng.<br>i vi loa, tai nghe v cc sn phm c loa, khng bo hnh li r, h.<br>V. Quy nh khc:<br>i vi nhng sn phm nh my tnh, in thoi,  cng lu tr, th nh. Chng ti hon ton khng chu trch nhim v vic mt d liu c nhn ca Qu khch nh: ti liu, danh b, tin nhn  khi thc hin cc yu cu Up Rom, sa cha.<br>Nu qu khch c nhu cu sao lu, backup d liu. Vui lng bo trc  nhn vin k thut thc hin.<br>VI. Chnh sch tr hng<br>Mi Store khng c chnh sch tr hng Qu khch vui lng tm hiu tnh nng hng ha hoc kim tra k sn phm.<br>Mt s trng hp c bit:<br>Qu khch c quyn tr hoc i mi trong trng hp sn phm pht sinh li do nh sn xut khng khc phc c hoc khc phc nhiu ln khng c.<br><strong>GIM C CNG TY</strong></p>\r\n<p> K</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(p dng t 01/01/2023)</p></div></div></div></div>'),('236',76,0,'81','<p> Nhp khu chnh hng Xiaomi (Bc Kinh)</p>\r\n<p> Bo hnh chnh hng 6 thng, i mi trong 7 ngy u tin.</p>\r\n<p> Mi 100% Fullbox nguyn sea</p>'),('237',85,0,'81','My lc nc Xiaomi H400G MR442-A'),('238',75,0,'82','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=R6RFN4F],#html-body [data-pb-style=TK53854],#html-body [data-pb-style=UMDKP24]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=O6BH04T]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=GU9QBUF]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=IQNCRKJ],#html-body [data-pb-style=IUH0MEG],#html-body [data-pb-style=PPQVMG2]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"O6BH04T\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"UMDKP24\"><a href=\"#NRHEVPP\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"TK53854\"><a href=\"#ISVODOB\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Hng dn mua hng</span></a></li><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"R6RFN4F\"><a href=\"#Q7SAEU3\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"GU9QBUF\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"NRHEVPP\" data-pb-style=\"IUH0MEG\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Xiaomi va chnh thc ra mt Pin sc d phng 10.000mAh 22.5W P15ZM &nbsp; thit k cc nh gn, tch hp sn cp sc nhanh 2 chiu trn vin pin sc v cung cp kh nng sc nhanh 22.5W Max.</p>\r\n<p>L dng sc nh gn, c th \"b ti\" d dng<br>Pin sc d phng 10.000mAh 22.5W P15ZM &nbsp;s hu kt cu kh nh gn. C th, vi kch thc 105.2 x 26.9 x 65.2mm bn c th d dng cm nm vin pin sc d phng trong lng bn tay v cng c th nht vo ti qun  mang theo s dng bt c lc no.</p>\r\n<p>Thn my c lm t cht liu PC, ABS dng nha nh cho  bn cc cao v chng bm bn, bm vn tay cc tt. Hn na, 2 phin bn mu sc xanh v kem, v cng tinh t gip ngi dng c th la chn ty theo s thch ca mnh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>S hu dung lng pin 10000mAh</strong><br>Vi dung lng 10000mAh hon ton c th p ng nhu cu sc hng ngy ca mt thit b sc. C th, sc d phng 10000mAh c th sc cho Mi 13 n 1.7 ln, sc Redmi K60 Pro 1.4 ln. Nh  m ngi dng khng cn phi lo lng v ngun in khi di chuyn. Bn cnh , vic s dng li pin Lithium cn gip tng tui th cho sc d phng cng nh m bo an ton cho thit b v ngi dng trong sut qu trnh sc.</p>\r\n<p><strong>H tr cng sc nhanh 2 chiu 22.5W</strong><br>Pin sc d phng 10.000mAh 22.5W P15ZM &nbsp;cn c th cung cp dng sc ti a 22.5W cho cc thit b sc. C th sc nhanh cho cc dng in thoi Xiaomi 13 ln 100% ch trong 1.2 gi, sc nhanh cho Redmi K60 Pro ln 100% ch trong 1.3 gi. Qu trnh t sc y ca vin pin sc d phng cng ch mt 4.5 gi.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Trang b sn cp sc type-C trn thn Pin</strong><br>Pin c trang b 3 cng sc gm 1 dy sc Type-C gn sn trn thn pin, 1 cng Type-C v 1 USB-A. Gip ngi dng c th sc ngay cho thit b di ng bng cng type-C i km m khng cn cm thm cp sc. Tt c cc cng sc u h tr cng sut u ra 1 cng l 22.5W Max, sc cng lc 3 thit b cc nhanh chng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tng thch vi mi thit b, c th sc cho c tai nghe bluetooth</strong><br>Pin sc d phng 10.000mAh 22.5W P15ZM &nbsp;cn c tch hp chip nhn dng thng minh  c th t ng khp vi dng in m cc thit b khc nhau yu cu t in thoi, my tnh bng, tai nghe n smartband,...Bn ch cn bm p vo nt ngun  c th chuyn sang ch  sc dng in thp cho cc thit b tai nghe, smartband,...</p>\r\n<p><br><strong>Thng s k thut</strong><br>Model: P15ZM<br>Dung lng pin: 10000mAh 37Wh 3.7V<br>Dung lng nh mc: 5500mAh (5V/3A)<br>Giao din u vo: Type-C/ Type-C (ngun)<br>Giao din u ra: USB-A/ Type-C/ Type-C (ngun)<br>u vo: &nbsp; Type-C: 5V-3A, 9V-2.5A<br>&nbsp; Type-C (ngun): &nbsp;5V-3A, 9V-2.5A<br>u ra: 22.5W MAX &nbsp;3 cng cng lc: 5V-3A<br>&nbsp; USB-A: 5V-3A, 9V-2.23A, 12V-1.67A, 10V-2.25A MAX<br>&nbsp; Type-C: 5V-3A, 9V-2.23A, 12V-1.67A, 10V-2.25A MAX<br>&nbsp; Type-C (ngun): 5V-3A, 9V-2.23A, 12V-1.67A, 10V-2.25A MAX<br>Kch thc sn phm: 105.2 x 65.2 x 26.9mm<br>Tiu chun iu hnh: Q/MI 50-2023</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"ma