phng 10.000mAh 22.5W P15ZM &nbsp;cn c th cung cp dng sc ti a 22.5W cho cc thit b sc. C th sc nhanh cho cc dng in thoi Xiaomi 13 ln 100% ch trong 1.2 gi, sc nhanh cho Redmi K60 Pro ln 100% ch trong 1.3 gi. Qu trnh t sc y ca vin pin sc d phng cng ch mt 4.5 gi.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Trang b sn cp sc type-C trn thn Pin</strong><br>Pin c trang b 3 cng sc gm 1 dy sc Type-C gn sn trn thn pin, 1 cng Type-C v 1 USB-A. Gip ngi dng c th sc ngay cho thit b di ng bng cng type-C i km m khng cn cm thm cp sc. Tt c cc cng sc u h tr cng sut u ra 1 cng l 22.5W Max, sc cng lc 3 thit b cc nhanh chng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tng thch vi mi thit b, c th sc cho c tai nghe bluetooth</strong><br>Pin sc d phng 10.000mAh 22.5W P15ZM &nbsp;cn c tch hp chip nhn dng thng minh  c th t ng khp vi dng in m cc thit b khc nhau yu cu t in thoi, my tnh bng, tai nghe n smartband,...Bn ch cn bm p vo nt ngun  c th chuyn sang ch  sc dng in thp cho cc thit b tai nghe, smartband,...</p>\r\n<p><br><strong>Thng s k thut</strong><br>Model: P15ZM<br>Dung lng pin: 10000mAh 37Wh 3.7V<br>Dung lng nh mc: 5500mAh (5V/3A)<br>Giao din u vo: Type-C/ Type-C (ngun)<br>Giao din u ra: USB-A/ Type-C/ Type-C (ngun)<br>u vo: &nbsp; Type-C: 5V-3A, 9V-2.5A<br>&nbsp; Type-C (ngun): &nbsp;5V-3A, 9V-2.5A<br>u ra: 22.5W MAX &nbsp;3 cng cng lc: 5V-3A<br>&nbsp; USB-A: 5V-3A, 9V-2.23A, 12V-1.67A, 10V-2.25A MAX<br>&nbsp; Type-C: 5V-3A, 9V-2.23A, 12V-1.67A, 10V-2.25A MAX<br>&nbsp; Type-C (ngun): 5V-3A, 9V-2.23A, 12V-1.67A, 10V-2.25A MAX<br>Kch thc sn phm: 105.2 x 65.2 x 26.9mm<br>Tiu chun iu hnh: Q/MI 50-2023</p></div></div><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"Hng dn mua hng\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"ISVODOB\" data-pb-style=\"PPQVMG2\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p><strong>Hng dn mua hng</strong></p>\r\n<p>Qu khch c th mua hng theo mt trong cc cch sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong>1/ Mua hng trc tip:</strong><br>Qu khch c th 