ng hn, em li tri nghim hnh nh th v cho ngi xem.</p>\n<p>B x l cht lng cao gip thao tc mt m<br>Nh c trang b GPU Mali G52 cng b x l li t CPU A55 mang n cho tivi Xiaomi 65A Pro 65 inch mt hiu nng cc nh v thut ton tr ln linh hot hn. Bn cnh  b nh ln 2GB + 16GB cho php ngi dng thoi mi ti xung mi ng dng yu thch m khng lo v d liu hay gy git lag, tn hng nhng pht giy th gin vi thao tc mt m nht. Cng ngh Wi-Fi bng tn kp v Bluetooth 5.0 cng m bo thit b truyn d liu nhanh v n nh hn.</p></div></div></div></div>','any','2023-12-05 03:11:38','2023-12-05 03:11:38'),('2','M t','.template-managermt656e95f5352bc.jpg','<style>#html-body [data-pb-style=IOGR1K1]{border-width:1px}#html-body [data-pb-style=ITXGF1W]{text-align:left}#html-body [data-pb-style=C8DNJCA]{border-width:1px;min-height:300px}#html-body [data-pb-style=O7SJT9F]{justify-content:flex-start;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background-position:left top;background-size:cover;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:scroll}</style><div class=\"tab-align-left\" data-content-type=\"tabs\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-active-tab=\"\" data-element=\"main\"><ul role=\"tablist\" class=\"tabs-navigation\" data-element=\"navigation\" data-pb-style=\"ITXGF1W\"><li role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-header\" data-element=\"headers\" data-pb-style=\"IOGR1K1\"><a href=\"#SMAJ1QC\" class=\"tab-title\"><span class=\"tab-title\">M t</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"tabs-content\" data-element=\"content\" data-pb-style=\"C8DNJCA\"><div data-content-type=\"tab-item\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-tab-name=\"M t\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-element=\"main\" id=\"SMAJ1QC\" data-pb-style=\"O7SJT9F\"><div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\"><p>Tivi thng minh Xiaomi A Pro 65 inch &nbsp;ni bt vi thit k hin i, khung kim loi cao cp thit k khng vin sang trng cho tri nghim hnh nh khng gii hn. Mn hnh 4K UHD di mu rng cng Dolby Vision mang n  sc nt cc cao, m thanh sng ng nh s h tr ca Dolby Audio, DT